Isehlakalo sokwanda okusheshayo kwesifo se-coronavirus (I-COVID-19) ku-European Union/European Economic Area nase-United Kingdom, ngo-1 January ukuya ku-15 March 2020
Isehlakalo esandayo sezimo zesifo se-coronavirus (i-COVID-19) sibonisa amathrendi afanayo emazweni e-European Union/European Economic Area kanye nase-United Kingdom okuqinisekisa ukuthi, nakuba isezigabeni ezihlukene kuye ngezwe, ubhubhane lwe-COVID-19 luqhubekela phambili ngokushesha kuwo wonke amazwe.
Ngokusekelwe kokuhlangenwe nakho kwase-Italy, amazwe, izibhedlela namayunithi okunakekela abasesimweni esibucayi kufanele andise ukulungela ukwamukela iziguli eziningi eziphethwe i-COVID-19 ezizodinga ukunakekelwa kwezempilo, futhi ikakhulukazi ukunakekela abanesimo esibucayi.
Ngo-31 December 2019, iqembu labantu abanezimo zenyumoniya ene-aetiology engaziwa labikwa e-Wuhan, e-Hubei Province, e-China.
Ngo-9 January 2020, i-China Center for Disease Control and Prevention yabika ukuthi i-ejenti eyimbangela i-coronavirus entsha manje ebizwa ngokuthi i-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kusukela ngaleso sikhathi, ukugula okuwumphumela wesifo se-SARS-CoV-2 kuye kwaqanjwa ngesifo se-coronavirus (I-COVID-19).
Ubufakazi obukhona kuze kube manje bubonisa ukuthi u-80% wabantu abaphethwe i-COVID-19 baphethwe isifo esingasho lutho, okungukuthi isifo somgudu wokuphefumula esihambisana noma esingahambisani nenyumoniya, futhi iningi laba bantu liyalulama.
Ezimweni ezingu-14%, i-COVID-19 iyathuthuka ibe isifo esibucayi kakhulu esidinga ukuthi ulaliswe esibhedlela kuyilapho u-6% wezimo ezisele ubhekana nesifo esibucayi esidinga ukunakekelwa kwesimo esibucayi.
Ukufa kweziguli ezilaliswe ngenxa ye-COVID-19 kungu-4%.
Kulolu cwaningo, sihlola amathrendi esehlakalo esandayo se-COVID-19 ezweni ngalinye le-European Union/European Economic Area (EU/EEA) kanye ne-United Kingdom (UK) futhi siwaqhathanise nalawo ase-Hubei Province, e-China.
Siphinde futhi siqhathanise inani lamanje labantu abane-COVID-19 emazweni ase-EU/EEA nase-UK nalelo lase-Italy phakathi no-31 January–15 March 2020.
Izimo ze-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK
Ngemva kwe-China, i-COVID-19 yasakazeka kabanzi ngokwezindawo futhi ukushintsha kobhubhane lwe-COVID-19 emhlabeni wonke okwamanje kulandela lokho okwenzeka kuleli zwe.
Ngo-11 March 2020, Umqondisi Jikelele we-World Health Organization (I-WHO) wamemezela ukuthi i-COVID-19 iwubhubhane.
Ijenali yango-5 March ye-Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. yabika ngabantu bokuqala abaqinisekisiwe abane-COVID-19 e-Europe ezivumelana nencazelo ye-WHO.
E-EU/EEA, abantu bokuqala abaqinisekisiwe babikwa yi-France ngo-24 January 2020 kubantu ababuya e-Wuhan, e-Hubei Province, e-China.
Ngomhla ka-15 March 2020, abantu abane-COVID-19 base betholiwe kuwo wonke amazwe angu-30 e-EU/EEA kanye nase-United Kingdom (UK), okungukuthi phakathi kuka-31 December 2019 nalolo suku, kwase kubikwe abantu abangu-39,768 abanaleli gciwane kanye nabantu abafile abangu-1,727, kulokhu abantu abangu-17,750 abanaleli gciwane kanye nabangu-1,441 abasebefile babengabase-Italy kuphela.
Ukuthola inombolo eyandayo neyesehlakalo esandayo sezimo ze-COVID-19
E-European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control (I-ECDC), izibalo zabantu abane-COVID-19 ezweni ngalinye emhlabeni wonke, ezitholwa ngemithombo esemthethweni kuphela efana Nomnyango Wezempilo wezwe ngalinye, amagunya ezempilo kazwelonke nawesifunda kanye ne-WHO, zibuyekezwa osukwini ngalunye ngo-8:00 a.m.
Le datha yasetshenziswa ekuhlaziyeni amathrendi e-COVID-19 e-EU/EEA nase-UK, futhi aqhathaniswa nalawo ase-Italy.
Njengesimeleli sokuvama kwezimo ze-COVID-19 eziqhubekayo, sibale isehlakalo esandayo esinqanyuliwe sezinsuku ezingu-14 zezimo ze-COVID-19, ngaleyo ndlela sicabangela ukuqhubeka okungokwemvelo kwe-COVID-19, ezweni ngalinye le-EU/EEA nase-UK, phakathi nenkathi ka-1 January–15 March 2020.
Siphinde sathula inombolo eyandayo yezimo ezibikiwe zezwe ngalinye ngo-15 March 2020 8:00 a.m. uma kuqhathaniswa nase-Italy ngenkathi ka-31 January–15 March 2020.
Amathrendi e-COVID-19 emazweni ase-EU/EEA nase-UK
Amathrendi esehlakalo esandayo esinqanyuliwe sezinsuku ezingu-14 zezimo ze-COVID-19 emazweni ase-EU/EEA nase-UK ngokuvamile alandele lawo ase-Hubei Province (China) (Umfanekiso 1).
Sekukonke e-EU/EEA nase-UK, isehlakalo esandayo se-COVID-19 saqala ukunyuka cishe ngo-21 February futhi sanyuka kakhulu ngo-28 February 2020 (Isithasiselo sokufundwayo).
Lokhu kwandiswa kakhulu ukwanda okusheshayo kwenani lwezimo ezibikiwe ezisuka-Italy, kodwa wonke amanye amazwe ase-EU/EEA nase-UK abonisa amathrendi anyukayo afanayo esehlakalo esandayo se-COVID-19 (Isithasiselo sokufundwayo).
Umfanekiso 2 ubonisa inani elandayo lezimo ze-COVID-19, emazweni ase-EU/EEA nase-UK uma kuqhathaniswa nalelo lase-Italy ngenkathi yango-31 January–15 March 2020.
Ligqamisa ukuthi, ngo-15 March 8:00 a.m., amanye amazwe angu-15 ase-EU/EEA kanye ne-UK ayesevele ebike ingqikithi yenani elingaqhathaniswa nalelo lase-Italy emavikini angu-3 ngaphambilini noma kancane.
Imiphumela yethu ibonisa ukuthi inani lezimo ezibikiwe ze-COVID-19 linyuka ngokushesha e-EU/EEA nase-UK.
Amathrendi aphawuliwe kusehlakalo esandayo se-COVID-19 abonisa ukuthi ubhubhane luqhubeka ngejubane elifanayo kuwo wonke amazwe.
Lokhu kwenzeka naphezu kokuthi amazwe esezigabeni ezihlukene, ukuhlukahluka endleleni yokusabela kwezempilo yomphakathi kazwelonke, futhi cishe nezincazelo ezingafani zezimo emazweni kanye namaphrothokholi ahlukene okukhetha iziguli okufanele zihlolwe ukuze kuqinisekiswe i-COVID-19, okuhlanganisa nokuhlola kokulandelela.
Ekuqaleni kuka-March 2020, odokotela ezifundeni ezithintekile zase-Italy bachaza isimo lapho u-10% weziguli eziphethwe i-COVID-19 zidinga ukunakekelwa kwezimo ezibucayi futhi imithombo yezindaba yabika ukuthi izibhedlela kanye namayunithi okunakekelwa okubucayi kulezi zifunda ayesefinyelele umthamo wawo ophakeme.
Idatha yokungeniswa kwabanezimo ze-COVID-19 esibhedlela kanye/noma iyunithi yokunakekelwa okubucayi iyatholakala esigabeni se-EU/EEA ezimweni ezingu-6% no-1% kuphela, ngokulandelana (idatha ayibonisiwe).
Kufanele, nokho, iqoqwe ngendlela ehlelekile ukuze ihambelana nedatha yokuqapha yamanje egxila enanini lezimo ezibikiwe kanye nenani lokufa.
Ucwaningo olwenziwa ngo-2010–11 lwabonisa ukuhluka okukhulu ngokuqondene nokutholakala kwemibhede yokunakekelwa okubucayi kanye neyokunakekelwa okumaphakathi e-Europe, kusuka ku-29.2 e-Germany kuye emibhedeni engu-4.2 emphakathini wabantu abangu-100,000 e-Portugal.
Lokhu kusho ukuthi amazwe kungenzeka ukuthi anezinsiza eziningi noma ezincane kune-Italy (imibhede yokunakekelwa okubucayi engu-12.5 neyokunakekelwa okumaphakathi emphakathini wabantu abangu-100,000 ngo-2010–11).
Ukulingisa izimo ezihlobene nokugcwala komthamo wokunakekelwa kwezempilo, okunikeza isilinganiso sezwe ngalinye lase-EU/EEA nase-UK ngokuqondene nokwanda kwezimo zabalaliswe esibhedlela ngenxa ye-COVID-19 okuhlobene nengozi engu-> 90% yokweqa umthamo wemibhede yokunakekelwa okubucayi, kunikezwa kusibuyekezo sesithupha sokuhlolwa kwengozi esheshayo ye-ECDC ngokuqondene ne-COVID-19.
Njengoba izimo zinqwabelane ezifundeni ezithile emazweni ase-EU/EEA nase-UK, futhi izibhedlela namayunithi okunakekelwa okubucayi ngokuvamile kusiza abantu abathile besifunda, ulwazi olumayelana nezimo kanye nemibhede yokunakekelwa okubucayi kufanele kutholakale ezingeni le-Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (I-NUTS-2).
Okuhlangenwe nakho kwase-Italy kanye namathrendi amanje akwamanye amazwe abonisa ukuthi ubhubhane lwe-COVID-19 lukhula ngokushesha e-EU/EEA nase-UK.
Amazwe, izibhedlela namayunithi okunakekelwa okubucayi kufanele azilungiselele isimo sokuthelelana komphathi okuqhubekayo kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kanye nokwanda kweziguli eziphethwe i-COVID-19 edinga ukunakekelwa kwezokwelashwa, futhi ikakhulukazi ukunakekelwa okubucayi, njengalokho okwenzeka ezifundeni ezithintekile e-Italy.
Njengoba kuboniswe ekuhloleni kwakamuva kwe-ECDC kwengozi esheshayo, indlela esheshayo, enomdlandla neningilizayo ibalulekile ukulibazisa ukusakazeka kwe-SARS-COV-2, ngokwenza ushintsho olusuka endleleni elawulayo luye endleleni enciphisayo, njengoba ukwanda okusheshayo okulindelwe kwenani lezimo kungase kunganikezi abenzi bezinqumo nezibhedlela isikhathi esanele sokuqonda, sokwamukela nokuvumelanisa ukusabela kwabo kube indlela efanele uma kungasetshenzisiwe kusanesikhathi.
Ukuhlola kwengozi esheshayo kuphinde kusho izinyathelo zempilo yomphakathi ukuze kulawulwe umthelela wobhubhane.
Kukhona intuba encane yethuba lapho amazwe engakwazi khona ukuba nethuba lokulawula ngokuqhubekayo imizamo yawo yokulawula ukuze kuncishiswe ukubhebhetheka SARS-CoV-2 futhi kuncishiswe ingcindezi ekunakekelweni kwezempilo.
Ukuhluleka kwalokhu, kungenzeka ukuthi amasistimu ezokwelashwa amanye amazwe ase-EU/EEA azobhekana nenqwaba yeziguli ezidinga ukunakekelwa kwezimo ezibucayi ezinsukwini ezizayo noma emavikini.
Ukubhekuda kwesifo se-Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), okubangelwe yi-severe acute respiratory syndrome (I-SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), okwamanje kubulale abantu abangaphezu kuka-3,000 futhi yaphatha abantu abangaphezu kuka-80,000 e-China nakwezinye izindawo emhlabeni, okuphumelele enhlekeleleni kubantu.
Ngokufana negciwane layo elifanayo, i-SARS-CoV, eyabangela i-SARS ezinkulungwaneni zabantu ngo-2003, i-SARS-CoV-2 ingase futhi idluliswe isuka kumalulwane futhi ibangele izimpawu ezifanayo ngendlela efanayo.
Nokho, i-COVID-19 inobucayi obucayi kanye nezinga lokufa kune-SARS kodwa idluliseka kakhulu futhi iphatha abantu abadala abaningi kunetsha futhi abantu besilisa abaningi kunabantu besifazane.
Njengendlela yokusabela enanini elikhula ngokushesha lokushicilelwe okumayelana nesifo esisafufusa, lesi sihloko sizama ukunikeza isibuyekezo esifike ngesikhathi nesiningilizayo esimayelana nesihloko socwaningo esithuthuka ngokushesha.
Sizodingida izinto eziyisisekelo ezimayelana ne-epidemiology, i-etiology, i-virology, ukuxilongwa, ukwelashwa, imbangela, nokuvinjwa kwesifo.
Nakuba imibuzo eminingi isadinga izimpendulo, sithemba ukuthi lesi sibuyekezo sisiza ekuqondweni nasekuqedweni kwesifo esisongelayo.
I-Spring Festival yango-January 25, 2020 isiphenduke inkumbulo engenakuqhathaniswa futhi engalibaleki kuwo wonke ama-Chinese akhuthazwa ukuthi ahlale ezindlini zawo ngeholide futhi emavikini amaningi ngemva kwalokho ngenxa yokubheduka kwesifo segciwane elisha.
Igciwane lifana kakhulu ne-coronavirus (I-CoV) eyabangela ukubheduka kwe-severe acute respiratory syndrome (SARS) ngo-2003; ngenxa yalokho, laqanjwa ngokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 yi-World Health Organization (WHO) ngo-February 11, 2020, futhi isifo esihlobene sabizwa ngokuthi i-CoV Disease-19 (I-COVID-19).
Umqedazwe waqala e-Wuhan, e-China, futhi wasakazeka ngokushesha ezweni lonke futhi nakwamanye acishe abe ngu-50 emhlabeni wonke.
Ngo-March 2, 2020, igciwane laholela ezimweni eziqinisekisiwe ezingaphezu kuka-80,000 ze-COVID-19, ngeziguli ezingaphezu kuka-40,000 ezakhishwa esibhedlela kanye neziguli ezingaphezu kuka-3,000 ezafa.
I-WHO ixwayisa ngokuthi i-COVID-19 “iyisitha somphakathi esihamba phambili” futhi kungenzeka ukuthi inamandla amakhulu ukwedlula ubuphekula.
Ngokwe-PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), ezinyangeni ezingaphansi kwezimbili, kushicilelwe amaphepha angaphezu kuka-200 mayelana ne-COVID-19 okuhlanganisa i-virology yayo, i-epidemiology, i-etiology, ukuxilongwa, nokwelashwa kusukela kumbiko wokuqala ngo-January 7, 2020 owanquma ukulandelana kwegciwane okuhlukaniswe ezigulini eziningi.
Lesi sibuyekezo sizama ukufinyeza inqubekela-phambili yocwaningo olumayelana nesihloko esisha nesithuthuka ngokushesha.
Noma nini lapho okungenzeka khona, sizozama ukuqhathanisa i-COVID-19 ne-SARS kanye nesinye isifo esibangelwa i-CoV, i-Middle East respiratory syndrome (I-MERS, ukubheduka kwango-2012).
Sizophinde futhi sixoxe ngalokho esikufundile kuze kube manje mayelana nokuvinjwa nembangela yesifo kanye neminye imibuzo esele kodwa ebalulekile.
Ama-CoV ngokuvamile ababhekwa njengama-pathogen angabulali kubantu, ngokuyinhloko abangela u-15% wemikhuhlane evamile 4.
Nokho, kuleli khulu leminyaka, sike sabhekana kabili nama-CoV abantu a-pathogenic kakhulu, okungukuthi, i-SARS-CoV ne- MERS-CoV, eyabangela ubhubhane olwaqala e-China ngo-2003 nase-Saudi Arabia ngo-2012, ngokulandelana, futhi ngokushesha asakazekela kwamanye amazwe okwabangela ukugula okubi nokufa.
Ngakho-ke, i-COVID-19 yamanje iwukubheduka kwesithathu kwe-CoV kumlando obhaliwe wabantu.
Njengoba kuboniswe Kumfa. ​Umfa.1,1, amaqoqo enyumoniya ayenomsuka ongaziwa aqala ukubikwa e-Wuhan ngo-December 31, 2019 ku-China National Health Commission.
Ezinsukwini eziyisikhombisa kamuva ukulandelana kwe-CoV kwakhululwa.
Ngo-January 15, 2020 kwabikwa isigameko sokuqala sokufa e-Wuhan.
Kusanjalo, umqedazwe wasakazekela ngokushesha emadolobheni angomakhelwane, ezifundazweni, nasemazweni.
Ngo-January 20, kwabikwa ukutheleleka kwezisebenzi zezempilo, okwasikisela ukuthi ukuthelelana kwabantu kwakuyinto engenzeka.
