Ngo-January 24 ucwaningo lwezokwelashwa lokuqala lwesifo labika ukuthi, ezigulini ezingu-41 ezinezimo eziqinisekisiwe, zingu-21 kuphela ezaba nokuxhumana okuqondile nemakethe yokudla kwasolwandle yase-Wuhan eyayibhekwa njengendawo okwakuqale kuyona isifo esivela kumthombo oyisilwane esingaziwa.
