Ama-CoV ayingxenye yomndeni wamagciwane amakhulu afihlekile aqukethe umucu owodwa we-RNA yomuzwa.
Angahlukaniswa abe izingxenye ezine, okungukuthi, i-alpha, i-beta, i-gamma, ne-delta, okungukuthi ama-CoV e-alpha ne-beta ayaziwa ukuthi athelela abantu.
I-spike (S) semvilophu ye-glycoprotein sinamathela kuzamukeli zamaseli e-angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (I-ACE2) kanye ne-dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (I-DPP4) ye-SARS-CoV kanye ne-MERS-CoV, ngokulandelana, bese kwenzeka ukuhlanganiswa kolwelwesi.
Isakhi sofuzo se-RNA yegciwane sikhululwa ku-cytoplasm; ngemva kokuphindwa kwesakhi sofuzo segciwane, i-RNA yesakhi sofuzo esihambisana nemvilophu yama-glycoprotein namaphrotheni e-nucleocapsid kwakha ama-vesicle aqukethe i-virion, ezihlanganisa nolwelwesi lwe-plasma ukuze kudedelwe igciwane.
Ukulandelana kwezakhi zofuzo zokuqala ze-SARS-CoV-2 kwabikwa ngo-January 10, 2020.
I-SARS-CoV-2 kwatholwa ukuthi iwuhlobo olusha lwe-beta-CoV enomazisi wezakhi zofuzo ezingu-99.98% phakathi namasampula alandelanayo angu-10 aqoqwe endaweni yokuqala yokubheduka, i-Huanan Seafood Market e-Wuhan.
I-SARS-CoV-2 ngokuvamile ifana kakhudlwana ne-SARS-CoV kune-MERS-CoV.
Kusetshenziswa i-microscopy yokudluliswa kwe-electron, kwatholwa izinhlayiya ze-SARS-CoV-2 ezingxenyeni ezicace kakhulu ku-epithelium yomgudu womoya kubantu.
I-ACE2 yabantu kwatholwa ukuthi iyisisabeli se-SARS-CoV-2 kanye ne-SARS-CoV.
Nokho, iphrotheni ka-S ye-SARS-CoV-2 izihlanganisa ne-ACE2 yomuntu ngokushesha okukhulu kunaleyo ye-SARS-CoV, okuhambelana neqiniso lokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ibangela ukutheleleka okungekho bucayi kakhulu ezigulini kune-SARS-CoV.
I-SARS-CoV-2 ingaphinde futhi yakhe iphrotheni emfushane entsha ekhiqizwa yi-orf3b kanye nephrotheni ekhishwayo ekhiqizwa yi-orf8.
I-orf3b ye-SARS-CoV-2 ingase idlale indima ku-pathogenicity yegciwane futhi ingase ivimbe ukubonakala kwe-IFNβ; nokho, i-orf8 ayiqukethe noma yisiphi isizinda noma i-motif esebenzayo eyaziwayo.
Ngo-February 18, 2020, i-Zhou, et al., yabika isakhiwo se-cryo-EM ye-ACE2 yabantu enobude obugcwele ekucaceni okungu-2.9 Å exhumene nesithuthi se-amino acid esiyi-B0AT1.
Kwatholwa ukuthi lokhu okuxhumene, okunezakhiwo ezivulekile nezivalekile, kwahlanganiswa njenge-dimer futhi okuxhumene kwe-ACE2-B0AT1 kukwazi ukuhlanganisa amaphrotheni ka-S amabili, okunikeza ubufakazi bokubonwa kwe-CoV kanye nokutheleleka.
I-B0AT1 ingase ibe ithagethi yokwelashwa ekuhlungweni kwemithi ukuze kucindezelwe ukutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV-2.
Umsuka kanye nombungazi omaphakathi
Kuyaziwa ukuthi kokubili i-SARS-CoV kanye ne-MERS-CoV kwaqala emalulwaneni futhi yadlulela kubantu ngamakati e-civet kanye namakameli, ngokulandelana.
Ngokuqhathaniswa kwe-phylogenetic ye-SARS-CoV-2 kanye namanye ama-CoV, amalulwane aqashelwa njengombungazi owumsuka we-SARS-CoV-2 njengoba igciwane elisha lifana ngo-96% nama-CoV amabili afana ne-SARS esuka kumalulwane abizwa ngokuthi i-SL-CoVZX45 yelulwane kanye ne-SL-CoVZX21 yelulwane.
Nokho, ukuthi yimuphi umbungazi owangenelela wasiza igciwane ukuthi leqe umngcele okhona phakathi kwezidalwa ukuze likwazi ukuthelela abantu akwaziwa, futhi umzila wokudluliselwa usazocaciswa.
I-Ji, et al., yasikisela ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi izinyoka ziyisithwali segciwane ukusuka kumalulwane kuye kubantu okwahilela ukuhlanganiswa kwabusha kwezici ezifanayo ngaphakathi kwephrotheni ka-S.
Ngokocwaningo, abacwaningi base-Guangzhou, e-China, basikisela ukuthi ama-pangolin - anekhala elide, izilwane ezincelisayo ezidla izintuthane ngokuvamile ezisetshenziswa njengemithi yesintu yase-Chinese - kungenzeka ukuthi angumbungazi omaphakathi we-SARS-CoV-2 ngokusekelwe kuzici zezakhi zofuzo ezingu-99% ku-CoV etholwe kuma-pangolin kanye ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Nokho, umehluko ka-1% osakazeke phakathi kwezakhi zofuzo ezimbili wenza umehluko omkhulu; ngakho-ke, imiphumela eqinisekisiwe yobufazi obuqinile isalindiwe (Umfa. ​(Umfa.33).
Izici ze-physicochemical ye-SARS-CoV-2 ngokwezinga elikhulu azaziwa okwamanje.
I-SARS-CoV kanye ne-MERS-CoV ingakwazi ukuphila ngaphandle kwesidalwa amahora afika ku-48 endaweni eyomile futhi kuze kufike ezinsukwini ezingu-5 ngaphansi komsakama ongu-20 °C no-40%-50%.
I-SARS-CoV-2 ingase ibe nezici ezifanayo.
Kubikwe ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ayizwani nemisebe ye-ultraviolet kanye nokushisa okungu-56 °C imizuzu engu-30; i-ether, u-75% we-ethanol, isibulali-magciwane esine-chlorine, i-peracetic acid, i-chloroform, nezinye izinto ezincibilikisa amafutha, kodwa hhayi i-chlorhexidine, zingenza igciwane lingasebenzi ngempumelelo.
Ngokuvamile bonke abantu bantula izivikeli-mzimba ezimelena ne-SARS-CoV-2 futhi yingakho besengozini yokuthola igciwane elisha.
Okwamanje, alukho ucwaningo oluningiliziwe olubikiwe mayelana nokusabela kwamasosha omzimba ku-SARS-CoV-2.
Ngakho-ke, singakwazi ukubhekisela kuphela kuzingcwaningo ezidlule zamanye ama-CoV, ikakhulukazi i-SARS-CoV kanye ne-MERS-CoV (Umfa. ​(Umfa.4).4).
Ngokuvamile, ngemva kokuthi igciwane lihlasele umzimba, liqale libonwe amasosha omzimba angokwemvelo ombungazi ngama-receptor okubonwa kwephetheni (ama-PRR) okuhlanganisa ama-receptor afana ne-lectin ohlobo C, i-receptor efana ne-Toll (I-TLR), i-receptor efana ne-NOD (I-NLR), kanye ne-receptor efana ne-RIG ka-I (I-RLR).
Ngemizila ehlukene, igciwane libangela ukuboniswa kwezici zokuvuvukala, ukwakheka kwamaseli e-dendritic, kanye nokukhiqizwa kwama-interferon ohlobo I (ama-IFN) akhawula ukusakazeka kwegciwane futhi kusheshise i-macrophage phagocytosis yama-antigen egciwane.
Nokho, iphrotheni ka-N ye-SARS-CoV ingasiza igciwane ukuthi libalekele ukusabela kwamasosha omzimba.
Maduzane, ukusabela kwamasosha omzimba okuvumelana nezimo kujoyina impi yokulwa negciwane.
Ama-T lymphocyte okuhlanganisa amaseli ka-T e-CD4+ ne-CD8+ adlala indima ebalulekile ekuvikeleni.
Amaseli ka-T e-CD4+ akhuthaza amaseli ka-B ukuthi akhiqize izivikeli zomzimba eziqondene negciwane, kanye namaseli ka-T e-CD8+ abulala ngokuqondile amaseli atheleleke ngegciwane.
Amaseli asizayo ka-T akhiqiza ama-proinflammatory cytokine ukusiza amaseli avikelayo.
Nokho, i-CoV ingakwazi ukuvimba ukusebenza kweseli lika-T ngokukhiqiza i-apoptosis yamaseli ka-T.
Ukungatheleleki kwe-humoral kuhlanganise nezinsiza ezifana ne-C3a kanye ne-C5a kanye nezivikeli-mzimba nakho kubalulekile ekulweni nesifo segciwane.
Ngokwesibonelo, izivikeli-mzimba ezithathwe kusiguli esiluleme zenza ukuthi i-MERS-CoV ingasebenzi.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, ukusabela ngokweqile kwamasosha omzimba kwakha inani elikhulu lama-radical endaweni elingakwazi ukubangela umonakalo omkhulu emaphasheni nakwezinye izitho zomzimba, futhi, esimweni esibi kunazo zonke, ukuhluleka kwezitho zomzimba eziningi futhi ngisho nokufa.
Isifo se-SARS-CoV-2, esinesici sokuqala njengeqembu, sinamathuba amaningi okugulisa abantu abadala abaphethwe i-comorbidities kanye nabantu besifazane abakhulelwe.
Kuyinto evamile ukuthi abantu abachayeke enanini elikhulu lamagciwane noma abanokusebenza kwamasosha omzimba afakwe engcupheni, banethuba eliphakeme lokutheleleka kunabanye abantu.
Isilinganiso sembangela yenkathi yokufukanyelwa kwe-SARS-CoV-2 siyizinsuku ezingu-1-14, ezikhathini eziningi izinsuku ezingu-3-7 ngokusekelwe kucwaningo lwabantu bokuqala abangu-425 e-Wuhan.
Nokho, ucwaningo lwabantu abangu-1,099 lubonisa ukuthi inkathi yokufukanyelwa ibiyizinsuku ezingu-3 ngokwesilinganiso futhi ibinobubanzi bezinsuku ezingu-0 ukuya kwezingu-24.
Ucwaningo lwakamuva, njengoba luchazwe ngenhla, lubonise ukuthi inkathi yokufukanyelwa ibiyizinsuku ezingu-4.8 (3.0-7.2) ngokusekelwe kulwazi lwabantu abangu-8,866.
Kubaluleke kakhulu kumagunya ezempilo ukuthi ashintshe isikhathi sokuzivalela ngokusekelwe enkathini yokufukanyelwa enembile, ngaleyo ndleal kuvinjwe abantu abathelelekile kodwa abangenazo izimpawu ukuthi bangadlulisi igciwane kwabanye.
Njengomkhuba ovamile, abantu abachayekile, noma abathelelekile igciwane, kudingeka ukuthi bazivalele izinsuku ezingu-14.
Ingabe isikhathi sokuzivalela kufanele sinwetshwe sibe izinsuku ezingu-24?
Imfiva ngokuvamile iyinkomba enkulu neyokuqala ye-COVID-19, engase ingahambisani nezimpawu noma ezinye izimpawu ezifana nokukhwehlela okungenazo izikhwehlela, ukuphelelwa umoya, ubuhlungu bemisipha, isiyezi, ikhanda elibuhlungu, umphimbo obuhlungu, i-rhinorrhea, ubuhlungu besifuba, isifo sohudo, isicanucanu, nokuhlanza.
Ezinye iziguli zabhekana ne-dyspnea kanye/noma i-hypoxemia evikini elilodwa ngemva kokuqala kwesifo.
Ezimweni ezibucayi, iziguli zathuthuka ngokushesha zaphathwa isifo sokuphefumula esibucayi, i-septic shock, i-metabolic acidosis, kanye ne-coagulopathy.
Iziguli eziphethwe imfiva kanye/noma izimpawu zokuphefumula kanye nemfiva ebucayi, ngisho noma zingekho izinto ezingavamile ezibonwa esithombeni samphaphu, kufanele zihlungelwe igciwane ukuze kube nokuxilongwa okwenziwe ekuqaleni.
Ucwaningo lolwazi lwabantu olwenziwa ekupheleni kuka-December ka-2019 lwabonisa amaphesenti ezimpawu ayethi u-98% owemfiva, u-76% owokukhehlela okungenazo izikhwehlela, u-55% owe-dyspnea, futhi u-3% owesifo sohudo; u-8% wawudinga ukuphefumula ngosizo lomshini.
Ukuthola okufanayo kwabikwa kuzingcwaningo zakamuva ezimbili zeqoqo lomndeni kanye neqoqo elibangelwa ukuthelelelwa umuntu ongenazo izimpawu.
Uma kuqhathaniswa, ucwaningo lolwazi lwabantu ngo-2012 lwabonisa ukuthi iziguli ezine-MERS-CoV nazo zazinemfiva (98%), ukukhwehlela okungenazo izikhwehlela (47%), kanye ne-dyspnea (55%) njengezimpawu zazo eziyinhloko.
Nokho, u-80% wazo wawudinga ukuphefumula ngosizo lomshini, okungaphezu kakhulu kuneziguli ezine-COVID-19 futhi okuvumelana nezinga eliphakeme kakhulu lokubulala kwe-MERS kune-COVID-19.
Isifo sohudo (26%) kanye nomphimbo obuhlungu (21%) nakho kwaphawulwa kuziguli eziphethwe i-MERS.
Ezigulini eziphethwe i-SARS, kwaboniswa ukuthi imfiva (99%-100%), ukukhwehlela okungenazo izikhwehlela (29%-75%), i-dyspnea (40%-42%), isifo sohudo (20-25%), nomphimbo obuhlungu (13-25%) kwakuyizimpawu ezinkulu futhi ukuphefumula ngosizo lomshini kwakudingekile cishe ezigulini ezingu-14%-20%.
Ngo-February 14, ukufa okubangelwa i-COVID-19 kwakungu-2% lapho abantu abagulayo abaqinisekisiwe befinyelela u-66,576 emhlabeni wonke.
Uma kuqhathaniswa, ukufa okubangelwa i-SARS ngo-November 2002 kwangu-10% kwabo bonke abantu abagulayo abaqinisekisiwe abangu-8,096.
Nge-MERS, ngokusekelwe kucwaningo lolwazi lwabantu ngo-June 2012, ukufa kwakungu-37% kubantu abagulayo abaqinisekisiwe abangu-2,494.
Ucwaningo lokuqala lwabika ukuthi u-R0 we-SARS-CoV-2 wawuphakeme ngo-6.47 unesikhewu sokuzethemba (I-CI) esingu-95% kokungu-5.71-7.23, lapho u-R0 we-SARS-CoV wawunobubanzi obusuka ku-2 ukuya ku-4.
Ukuqhathaniswa kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-MERS-CoV kanye ne-SARA-CoV ngokuphathelene nezimpawu zabo, ukufa, kanye no-R0 kumelelwe kokuthi Ithebula Ithebula1.1.
Izinombolo ezingenhla zisikisela ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 inekhono eliphakeme kakhulu lokubhebhetheka kune-MERS-CoV kanye ne-SARS-CoV, kodwa inamandla amancane okubulala kunazo zombili.
Ngakho-ke, kuyinselele kakhulu ukulawula umqedazwe we-SARS-CoV-2 kune-MERS-CoV kanye ne-SARS-CoV.
Ukuqalisa kwamaqoqo kuvame ukwenzeka kumndeni ofanayo noma kumbuthano ofanayo noma into yezokuthutha efana nomkhumbi wokungcebeleka.
Iziguli ngokuvamile zinomlando wokuvakasha noma zihlala e-Wuhan noma ezinye izindawo ezithintekile noma ukuxhumana nabantu abathelelekile noma iziguli emavikini amabili akamuva ngaphambi kokuqala.
Nokho, kuye kwabikwa ukuthi abantu bangakwazi ukuthwala igciwane ngaphandle kwezimpawu isikhathi eside kunamaviki amabili futhi iziguli ezilashiwe ezikhishiwe esibhedlela zingakwazi ukuphinde zithwale igciwane futhi, okukhipha isixwayiso sokunyusa isikhathi sokuzivalela.
Iziguli zinenani elivamile noma elincishisiwe lamaseli amhlophe egazi ayi-peripheral (ikakhulukazi ama-lymphocyte) ezigabeni zokuqala.
Ngokwesibonelo, i-lymphopenia enesibalo samaseli egazi amhlophe esithi < 4×109/L okuhlanganisa isibalo se-lymphocyte esithi < 1×109/L, kanye namazinga aphakeme e-aspartate aminotransferase kanye ne-viremia atholwa kuziguli ezingu-1,099 ezine-COVID-19.
Amazinga ama-enzyme esibindi nomsipha kanye ne-myoglobin ayephakeme egazini lezinye iziguli, futhi iphrotheni eyi-C-reactive kanye ne-erythrocyte sedimentation yayiphakeme egazini leziguli eziningi.
Kuziguli ezinokugula okubucayi, izinga le-D-dimer, umkhiqizo wokuwohloka kwe-fibrin okhona egazini, laliphakeme, futhi isibalo se-lymphocyte lalinciphe ngokuphawulekayo.
Kwatholwa okungajwayelekile ku-radiography yesifuba yeziguli eziningi ezine-COVID-19 futhi okunezici zethunzi elinamapheshi akabili noma i-ground glass opacity emaphasheni.
Iziguli zivame ukuphathwa inyumoniya engavamile, ukulimala kwephaphu okubucayi, kanye ne-acute respiratory distress syndrome (I-ARDS).
Lapho kwenzeka i-ARDS, ukuvuvukala okungalawuliwe, ukukhula koketshezi, kanye ne-fibrosis ethuthukayo kufaka engcupheni ukushintshana kwegesi.
Ukungasebenzi kahle kohlobo-I nohlobo-II lwe-pneumocyte kunciphisa izinga le-surfactant futhi kunyuse ukucindezeleka kwendawo engaphezulu, ngaleyo ndlela kuncishiswe ikhono lamaphaphu lokunwebeka futhi okunyusa ingozi yokuwa kwamaphaphu.
Ngakho-ke, imiphumela emibi kakhulu ye-radiography ivame ukufana nesimo esibucayi kakhulu sesifo.
Ngo-February 18, 2020, ukuhlaziya kokuqala oku-pathological kwe-COVID-19 kwabonisa ukuxebuka kwama-pneumocyte, ukwakheka kolwelwesi lwe-hyaline, kanye nokufinyelelwa kwe-interstitial lymphocyte, kanye namaseli e-multinucleated syncytial emaphasheni esiguli esibulawe isifo, okuhambisana ne-pathology yesifo segciwane kanye ne-ARDS futhi okufana nalokho kweziguli ze-SARS ne-MERS.
Ukutholwa kwe-RNA ye-SARS-CoV-2 kusetshenziswa i-reverse-transcriptase polymerase chain reaction (I-RT-PCR) kwasetshenziswa njengombandela omkhulu wokuxilongwa kwe-COVID-19.
Nokho, ngenxa yenani eliphakeme lenegethivu engeyikho, engase isheshise umqedazwe, ukubonakala kwezokwelashwa kwaqala ukusetshenziswa lapho kuxilongwa (okwakungathembele kuphela ku-RT-PCR) e-China ngo-February 13, 2020.
Kwavela isimo esifanayo lapho kuxilongwa i-SARS.
Ngakho-ke, inhlanganisela yomlando wesifo, ukubonakaliswa kwezokwelashwa, ukuhlolwa kwaselabhorethri, nemiphumela ye-radiological ibalulekile futhi isemqoka ukuze kwenziwe ukuxilongwa okuyimpumelelo.
Ngo-February 14, 2020, iqembu le-Feng Zhang lachaza iphrothokholi yokusebenzisa indlela ka-SHERLOCK esekelwe ku-CRISPR ukuze kutholwe i-SARS-CoV-2, ethola izingxenyana ezingezona ezemvelo ze-RNA ye-SARS-CoV-2 ku-20 × 10-18 mol/L to 200 × 10-18 mol/L (amakhophi angu-10-100 nge-microliter ngayinye yokufakiwe) kusetshenziswa induku yokugcobhoza enkathini engaphansi kwehora ngaphandle kokudinga amathuluzi ayinkimbinkimbi.
Sithemba ukuthi indlela entsha izothuthukisa kakhulu ukuzwela nezinzuzo uma kuqinisekisiwe kumasampula ezokwelashwa.
Ngenxa yokuntula okuhlangenwe nakho nge-CoV entsha, odokotela ngokuyinhloko bangakwazi ukunikeza ukunakekelwa kokusekela kuziguli ze-COVID-19, kuyilapho bezama izinhlobonhlobo zezindlela zokwelapha ezisetshenzisiwe noma eziphakanyisiwe ngaphambilini ukuze kwelashwe amanye ama-CoV afana ne-SARS-CoV kanye ne-MERS-CoV nezinye izifo zamagciwane (Ithebula ​(Ithebula2).2).
Lokhu kwelashwa kuhlanganisa ukwelashwa kwamanje nokungase kube ukwelashwa ngemithi elwa namagciwane, ama-immunosuppressant, ama-steroid, i-plasma evela kuziguli eziluleme, imithi yama-Chinese, kanye nosizo lwezengqondo.
Kwenziwa ngisho nesiphakamiso sokusebenzisa i-plasma yeziguli eziluleme njengendlela yokwelashwa.
Izinkampani zama-pharmaceutical ziyaqhudelana ukuze zakhe izivikeli-mzimba nemigomo emelene negciwane.
I-SARS-CoV-2 ngokuyinhloko ihlasela amaphaphu ekuqaleni futhi cishe iphinde ihlasele, ngokwezinga elincane, ezinye izitho zomzimba ezibonisa i-ACE2, njengesistimu ye-gastrointestinal kanye nezinso.
Noma kunjalo, ukungasebenzi kahle kanye nokuhluleka kwendlela yokuphefumula kuwusongo olukhulu kuziguli futhi kuyimbangela enkulu yokufa.
Ngakho-ke, ukusekelwa kokuphefumula kubalulekile ukuze kudambiswe izimpawu futhi kusindiswe izimpilo futhi kuhlanganisa ukwelashwa okuvamile ngomoya-mpilo, ukugeleza okuphakeme komoya-mpilo, ukufakwa komoya ngaphandle kwemishini elimaza umzimba, kanye nokufakwa komoya kusetshenziswa imishini elimaza umzimba kuye ngobucayi besifo.
Iziguli ezinezimpawu zokuphefumula ezibucayi kufanele zisekelwe kusetshenziswa i-extracorporeal membrane oxygenation (I-ECMO), indlela elungisiwe yokuhlinzwa ye-cardiopulmonary esetshenziselwa ukwelapha ukwehluleka kokusebenza kwenhliziyo noma kokuphefumula okusongela ukuphila.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ukugcinwa esimweni kwebhalansi ye-electrolyte, ukuvinjwa nokwelashwa kokutheleleka kwesibili kanye ne-septic shock, kanye nokuvikelwa kokusebenza kwezitho zomzimba ezisemqoka nakho kubalulekile kuziguli ezine-SARS-CoV-2.
Kuyaziwa ukuthi isiphepho se-cytokine siwumphumela wokusabela ngokwedlulele kwamasosha omzimba kuziguli ze-SARS ne-MERS.
Isiphepho se-cytokine siyindlela yokusabela yohlelo lokuvuvukala enezici zokukhululwa kochungechunge lwama-cytokine okuhlanganisa i-TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, kanye ne-MCP-1.
Lawa ma-cytokine akhuthaza amasosha omzimba ukuthi akhulule inani elikhulu nama-radical akhululekile ayimbangela eyinhloko ye-ARDS kanye nokuhluleka kwezitho zomzimba eziningi.
Ukucindezelwa kwamasosha omzimba kubalulekile ekwelashweni kweziphepho ze-cytokine, ikakhulukazi kuziguli ezibucayi.
Ama-corticosteroid kanye ne-tocilizumab, isivikeli-mzimba esiyi-anti-IL6 monoclonal, kuye kwasetshenziswa ukuze kwelashwe isiphepho se-cytokine.
Okunye ukwelashwa kokucindezelwa kwamasosha omzimba kwesiphepho se-cytokine kuhlanganisa ukulawulwa kokusabela kwamasosha omzimba okuqondiswe kuseli lika-T; ukuvinjwa kwe-IFN-γ, IL-1, kanye ne-TNF; ukuthiywa kwe-JAK ; i-blinatumomab; umcindezeli wokusetshenziswa kwesiginali ye-cytokine 4; kanye nezivimbi ze-HDAC.
Ama-steroid, njengama-immunosuppressant, asetshenziswa kabanzi ukwelashweni kwe-SARS ukuze kuncishiswe ubucayi komonakalo wokuvuvukala.
Nokho, ama-steroid kusilinganiso esiphakeme awazange azuzise ekulimaleni kwamaphaphu okubucayi ezigulini eziphethwe i-SARS kanye ne-COVID-19.
Kunalokho, kungase kubangele imiphumela engathandeki ebucayi, ikakhulukazi i-avascular osteonecrosis, okuphazamisa ngendlela ephawulekayo i-prognosis.
Noma kunjalo, uhlelo olufushane lwama-corticosteroid ngezilinganiso eziphansi kuye kwezimaphakathi ziye zatuswa ukuthi zisetshenziswe ngokucophelela kuziguli ze-COVID-19 ezigula ngendlela ebucayi.
Ngesikhathi sokubhala, akukho ukwelashwa okusebenzayo okulwa negciwane okwase kuqinisekisiwe.
Nokho, ukufakwa emthanjeni nge-remdesivir, okuyi-nucleotide analog, kwatholwa kusebenza esigulini esiyi-American esine-COVID-19.
I-Remdesivir iwumuthi omusha olwa negciwane owaqala wakhiqizwa yi-Gilead ukuze kwelashwe izifo ezibangelwa amagciwane e-Ebola ne-Marlburg.
Kamuva, i-remdesivir yaphinde yabonisa ukuthi yayingase ivimbele amagciwane e-RNA anomucu owodwa okuhlanganisa amagciwane e-MERS ne-SARS.
Ngokusekelwe kulokhu, i-Gilead inikeze i-China isakhi ukuze iqhube izingcwaningo kubantu abaphethwe i-SARS-CoV-2, futhi imiphumela ibhekwe ngabomvu.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, i-baricitinb, i-interferon-α, i-lopinavir/ritonavir, kanye ne-ribavirin kuye kwaphakanyiswa njengokungase kube ukwelashwa kweziguli ezinezimpawu zokuphefumula ezibucayi.
Isifo sohudo, isicanucanu, ukuhlanza, ukulimala kwesibindi, nokunye ukusabela okubucayi kungase kuvele ngemva kokwelashwa okuyinhlanganisela nge-lopinavir/ritonavir.
Ukusebenzelana kwalokhu kwelashwa neminye imithi esetshenziswe kuziguli kufanele kuqashelwe ngokucophelela.
I-Plasma evela kuziguli eziluleme nokwakhiwa kwezivikeli-mzimba
Ukuqoqwa kwegazi leziguli eziluleme esifweni esithathelanayo ukuze kwelashwe ezinye iziguli eziphethwe isifo esifanayo noma ukuze kuvikelwe abantu abaphile kahle ukuthi bangasitholi isifo kunomlando omude.
Eqinisweni, iziguli eziluleme zivame ukuba nezinga eliphakeme lezivikeli-mzimba ezimelana nesifo esisegazini labo.
Izivikeli-mzimba ziyi-immunoglobulin (Ig) ekhiqizwa ama-B lymphocyte ukuze kuliwe nezifo kanye nezinye izinto ezingadingekile emzimbeni futhi zikwazi ukubona amangqamuzana ahlukile ezifweni futhi awenze angasebenzi ngokuqondile.
Ngokusekelwe kulokhu, i-plasma yaqoqwa egazini leqembu leziguli ezilulame ku-COVID-19 futhi yajovwa kuziguli ezigula ezingu-10 ngendlela ebucayi ezingu-.
Izimpawu zazo zaba ngcono emahoreni angu-24, okwahambisana nokuvuvukala okuncishisiwe kanye nemithamo yegciwane kanye nokugcwala komoya-mpilo okuthuthukile egazini.
Nokho, ukuqinisekiswa kanye nokucaciswa kuyadingeka ukuze kwenziwe isiphakamiso sokuthi indlela isetshenziswe kabanzi ngaphambi kokuthi ukwelashwa okuthile kuthuthukiswe.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, uma kucatshangelwa imiphumela yokwelashwa, okunye okungazuzisi okuhlobene ne-plasma kufanele kucatshangelwe ngokucophelela.
Ngokwesibonelo, izivikeli-mzimba zingakhuthaza ngokwedlulele ukusabela kwamasosha omzimba futhi kubangele isifo sokukhululwa kwe-cytokine, okungase kube ubungozi obusongela ukuphila.
Umthamo wezivikeli-mzimba ezisegazini ngokuvamile uphansi, futhi isidingo se-plasma sikhulu ukuthi kungalashwa iziguli ezigula ngendlela ebucayi.
Kunzima ukwakha nokukhiqiza izivikeli-mzimba ezithile ngokushesha okukhulu ukuze kuliwe nomqedazwe wembulunga yonke.
Ngenxa yalokho, kubaluleke kakhulu futhi kunengqondo ukuhlukanisa amaseli ka-B eziguli eziluleme futhi kuphawulwe amakhodi ezakhi zofuzo anezakhi zofuzo ezisebenzayo noma kuhlungwe izivikeli-mzimba ezisebenzayo ekumeleleni amaphrotheni abalulekile egciwane.
Ngale ndlela, singakwazi ukunyusa ukukhiqizwa kwezivikeli-mzimba.
I-TCM iye yasetshenziswa ukuze kulashwe izinhlobonhlobo zezifo e-China izinkulungwane zeminyaka.
Nokho, imithelela yayo incike kakhulu ekuhlanganisweni kwezingxenye eziningi kufomula ehlukahlukayo kuye ngokuxilongwa kwesifo ngokusekelwe embonweni ye-TCM.
Iningi lezingxenye ezisebenzayo zihlala zingaziwa noma azicacile njengoba kunzima ukumonyula nokuqinisekisa izingxenye ezinjalo noma izinhlanganisela zayo ezisebenza kangcono.
Okwamanje, ngenxa yokuntuleka yokwelashwa okusebenzayo nokuqondile kwe-COVID-19, i-TCM isiphenduke okunye kokwelashwa okukhulu kweziguli ezinezimpawu ezincane kuye kwezimaphakathi kulabo abalulame ezigabeni ezibucayi.
Ngokwesibonelo, amaphilisi e-Shu Feng Jie Du kanye namaphilisi e-Lian Hua Qing Wen kwatholwa ukuthi ayasebenza ekwelashweni kwe-COVID-19.
Izilinganiso eziphakeme zokwelashwa ekwelashweni kweziguli ezine-COVID-19 zaphawulwa ezifundazweni eziningi zase-China ezisebenzise i-TCM ku-87% weziguli zabo, okuhlanganisa i-Gansu (63.7%), i-Ningxia (50%), ne-Hunan (50%), kuyilapho isifundazwe sase-Hubei, esasebenzisa i-TCM cishe ku-30% weziguli zaso ezine-COVID-19, saba nesilinganiso esiphansi kakhulu sokululama (13%).
Nokho, lokhu kuwukuqhathanisa okunganembile njengoba ezinye izici zomthelela ezifana nenani nobucayi beziguli kufanele zifakwe ekuhlaziyweni.
Ngo-February 18, 2020, u-Boli Zhang nozakwabo bashicilela ucwaningo lokuqhathanisa ukwelashwa ngemithi yasentshonalanga (WM) yodwa kanye nokwelashwa okuyinhlanganisela kwe-WM ne-TCM.
Bathola ukuthi izikhathi ezidingekayo ukuze izinga lokushisa komzimba lilulame, kuphele izimpawu, kanye nokulaliswa esibhedlela kwakukufushane eqenjini le-WM+TCM kuneqembu le-WM kuphela.
Okuhlaba umxhwele kakhulu, ukuthi izinga lokuba libi kwezimpawu (ukusuka kwezincane kuye kwezibucayi) laliphansi ngokuphawulekayo eqenjini le-WM+TCM kuneqembu le-WM kuphela (u-7.4% oqhathaniswa no-46.2%) futhi ukufa kwakuphansi kakhudlwana eqenjini le-WM+TCM kuneqembu le-WM kuphela (u-8.8% oqhathaniswa no-39%).
Noma kunjalo, ukusebenza nokuphepha kwe-TCM kusalinde izingcwaningo ezilawulwe kahle emazingeni amakhulu nasezikhungweni eziningi.
Kungaphinde futhi kuhlabe umxhwele ukuthi kuphawulwe indlela yezenzo futhi kucaciswe ukuthi izingxenye ezisebenzayo zokwelashwa kwe-TCM noma izinhlanganisela zayo uma kunokwenzeka.
Iziguli okunezinsolo noma eziqinisekisiwe ukuthi ziphethwe i-COVID-19 ngokuvamile ziyasisaba kakhulu isifo esithelelena kakhulu futhi esibulalayo, futhi abantu abazivalele baphinde babhoreke, babe nesizungu, kanye nolaka.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, izimpawu zokutheleleka ezifana nemfiva, i-hypoxia, nokukhwehlela kanye nemiphumela ebucayi yokwelashwa efana nokuqwasha ebangelwa ama-corticosteroid ingaholela ekubeni nexhala okwengeziwe nokucindezeleka ngokomqondo.
Esigabeni sokuqala sokubheduka kwe-SARS, izifo eziningi ezihlobene nengqondo okuhlanganisa ukucindezeleka okuphikelelayo, ixhala, ukushaywa uvalo, ukuphazamiseka kwekhono lengqondo lokunyakazisa umzimba, izimpawu zokusangana, ukuhanjelwa ingqondo, ngisho nokufuna ukuzibulala kwabikwa.
Ukulandelelwa kokuxhumana okuyimpoqo nokuzivalela, njengengxenye yokusabela kwezempilo yomphakathi ekubhedukeni kwe-COVID-19, kungase kwenze abantu abaningi babe nexhala futhi bazizwe benecala mayelana nemiphumela yokuthelelana, ukuzivalela, kanye nesigcwagcwa emndenini nakubangane babo.
Ngenxa yalokho, ukunakekelwa kwempilo yengqondo kufanele kunikezwe iziguli ze-COVID-19, abantu okusolwa ukuthi banayo, nabantu abaxhumana nabo kanye nomphakathi ovamile oludingayo.
Usizo lwezengqondo kufanele luhlanganise ukusungulwa kwamathimba ezempilo yengqondo yemikhakha eminingi, ukuxhumana okucacile okunezibuyekezo zezikhathi zonke nezinembile ezimayelana nokubheduka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kanye nezinhlelo zokwelashwa kanye nokusetshenziswa kwamadivayisi ezokwelashwa kagesi kanye nezinhlelo zokugwema ukusondelana ngokuseduze nabanye.
Imigomo esebenzayo ibalulekile ukuze kugqashulwe iketanga lokuthelelana ukusuka ezilwaneni nabantu abathelelekile kuye kubabungazi abangase bachayeke futhi ngokuvamile iyahambelana nokwelashwa okulwa namagciwane ekulawulweni kwemiqedazwe ebangelwa amagciwane amasha.
Kwenziwe imizamo yokwenza imigomo esekelwe kuphrotheni ka-S ukuze kwenziwe izivikeli-mzimba zesikhathi eside nezinamandla okubulala kanye/noma ukuvikeleka kokungayitholi i-SARS-CoV.
Imigomo ebukhoma encishiwe amandla iye yahlolwa ezilwaneni ngokuqondene ne-SARS.
Nokho, ukusebenza ezintweni eziphilayo kwalawa makhandidethi omgomo kubantu abadala kanye namamodeli enselele ebulalayo kanye nokuvikeleka kwawo ekungenweni igciwane elisuka ezilwaneni liye kubantu kusazotholwa ngaphambi kokuthi kuqaliswe ucwaningo lwezokwelashwa.
Lokhu kungenxa yokuthi i-SARS yathula eminyakeni engu-17 edlule futhi akukho ukugula kwayo okusha okuye kwabikwa kusukela ngaleso sikhathi.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, izimo eziyimvela kancane kanye namaqoqo e-MERS ayaqhubeka evela e-Middle East futhi asakazeka nakwezinye izifunda ngenxa yokuphikelela kwemithombo yamagciwane asuka ezilwaneni aye kubantu ezindaweni ezinesifo.
Amasu okugoma aye enzelwa i-MERS ngokuthi kusetshenziswe igciwane elingasebenzi, ama-plasmid e-DNA, ama-vector egciwane, ama-nanoparticle, izinhlayiya ezifana negciwane kanye namayunithi angaphansi ephrotheni eyinhlanganisela futhi amanye aye ahlolwa kumamodeli ezilwane.
Ukwakhiwa komgomo ophephile nosebenzayo omelene ne-SARS-CoV-2 kubantu abathelelekayo kuwumsebenzi ophuthumayo nobalulekile ekulawuleni umqedazwe oqhubekayo.
Nokho, kuyinselele ukumelana nobunzima ngenxa yenkathi ende (isilinganiso sezinyanga ezingu-18) edingekayo ukuze kwakhiwe umgomo kanye nezinhlobo ezishintshayo zama-CoV.
Njengesifo esisha, i-COVID-19 isanda kuqala ukubonisa uhlelo lwayo lwezokwelashwa olugcwele ezigulini eziyizinkulungwane.
Ezimweni eziningi, iziguli zingakwazi ukululama kancane ngaphandle kwemiphumela yesifo sangaphambilini.
Nokho, ngokufana ne-SARS ne-MERS, i-COVID-19 iphinde ihlotshaniswe nezinga eliphakeme lokugula nokufa ezigulini ezinokugula okubucayi.
Ngakho-ke, ukwakha imodeli yembangela yesifo kubalulekile kuma-ejensi okunakekelwa kwezempilo ukuze kubekwe ekuqaleni amasevisi awo, ikakhulukazi ezindaweni ezinezinsiza ezincane.
Ngokusekelwe kuzingcwaningo zokwelashwa ezibikwe kuze kube manje, izici ezilandelayo zingase zithinte noma zihlotshaniswe nembangela yeziguli ze-COVID-19 (Ithebula ​(Ithebula33):
Ubudala: Ubudala babuyisici esibaluleke kakhulu sembangela ye-SARS, okuyiqiniso futhi nge-COVID-19.
I-COVID-19 yavela ngokuyinhloko kubudala obungu-30-65 futhi u-47.7% walezo ziguli zazingaphezu kuka-50 kucwaningo lweziguli ezingu-8,866 njengoba kuchazwe ngenhla.
Iziguli ezazidinga ukunakekelwa kwezimo ezibucayi zazinethuba eliphakeme lokuphathwa ezinye izifo nezinkimbinkimbi futhi zazindala ngokuphawulekayo kunalezo ezingenazo (ubudala ongu-66 buqhathaniswa no-51), okusikisela ukuthi ubudala buyisici esiyimbangela kumphumela kuziguli eziphethwe i-COVID-19.
Ubulili: I-SARS-CoV-2 igulise abantu besilisa abaningi kunabantu besifazane (u-0.31/100,000 oqhathaniswa no-0.27/100,000), njengoba kuchazwe ngenhla.
Izifo ezikhona kakade nezinkimbinkimbi: Iziguli eziphethwe i-COVID-19 ezidinga ukunakekelwa okubucayi zinethuba eliphakeme lokuphathwa ukulimala kwenhliziyo okubucayi kanye ne-arrhythmia.
Izehlakalo ezihlobene nenhliziyo zaphinde zaba isizathu esiyinhloko sokufa kweziguli ezine-SARS.
Kuphindwe kwabikwa ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 iyakwazi futhi ukunamathela kuma-ACE2-positive cholangiocyte, okungase kuholele ekungasebenzini kahle kwesibindi kuziguli eziphethwe i-COVID-19.
Kuhle ukuphawula ukuthi ubudala kanye nesifo esikhona kakade kuhlobene nokuqinile futhi kungase kuphazamisane.
Imiphumela yaselabhorethri engavamile: Izinga lephrotheni ye-C-reactive (CRP) egazini ibonisa ubucayi bokuvuvukala noma ukulimala kwesicubu futhi kuye kwaphakanyiswa ukuthi kuyisici esingase sibe imbangela yesifo, ukusabela ekwelashweni, kanye nokululama okuphelele.
Kuphinde kwenziwa ukuhlobana kwezinga le-CRP nobucayi nembangela ye-COVID-19.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, i-lactate dehydrogenase (LDH) ephakeme, i-aspartate aminotransferase (AST), i-alanine aminotransferase (ALT), kanye ne-creatine kinase (CK) ingase futhi isize ukubikezela umphumela.
Lawa ma-enzyme aboniswa kabanzi ezithweni eziningi, ikakhulukazi enhliziyweni nakusibindi, futhi kukhululwa phakathi nokulimala kwesicubu.
Ngenxa yalokho, ziyizinkomba ezivamile zokungasebenzi kahle kwenhliziyo noma isibindi.
Izimpawu zokwelashwa ezinkulu: I-radiography yesifuba nokuqhubeka kwesikhashana kwezimpawu zokwelashwa kufanele zicatshangelwe ndawonye nezinye izinkinga zokubikezelwa kwemiphumela nezinkimbinkimbi ze-COVID-19.
Ukusetshenziswa kwama-steroid: Njengoba kuchazwe ngenhla, ama-steroid angama-immunosuppressant ngokuvamile asetshenziswa njengokwelashwa kokwenezela kwezifo ezithelelanayo ukuze kuncishiswe ubucayi komonakalo wokuvuvukala.
Njengoba kusetshenziswe kabanzi inani eliphakeme lama-corticosteroid kuziguli ezine-SARS ebucayi, iningi labantu abasinda babephethwe i-avascular osteonecrosis benokukhubazeka kokuphila kwabo konke nezinga lokuphila elingelihle.
Ngenxa yalokho, uma edingekile, ama-steroid kufanele asetshenziswe ngesilinganiso esiphansi futhi isikhathi esifushane kuziguli ze-COVID-19.
Ukucindezeleka komqondo: Njengoba kuchazwe ngenhla, phakathi nokubheduka kwe-COVID-19 iziguli eziningi zaphathwa ukucindezeleka okukhulu njengoba kwakufanele zibekezelele izinkathi ezide zokuzivalela nokungaqiniseki okukhulu futhi zibona ukufa kwamalungu omndeni aseduze kanye neziguli ezikanye nazo.
Kusemqoka ukuthi kunikezwe ukwelulekwa komqondo nokusekelwa kwesikhathi eside ukuze kusizwe lezi ziguli zilulame ekucindezelekeni futhi zibuyele empilweni evamile.
Ngokuvumelana nezingcwaningo zolwazi lwabantu kuze kube manje, i-COVID-19 ibonakala inezici ze-epidemiological ezihlukile ku-SARS.
Ngaphezu kokuphindeka kumgudu wokuphefumula ongezansi, i-SARS-CoV-2 iyakwazi ukuphindeka kalula kumgudu wokuphefumula ongenhla futhi ibangele izimpawu ezincane noma ingazibangeli esigabeni sokuqala sokutheleleka, ngendlela efanayo nama-CoV abangela imikhuhlane evamile.
Ngakho-ke, iziguli ezithelelekile esigabeni sokuqala noma enkathini yokufukanyelwa zingakhiqiza inani elikhulu legciwane phakathi nemisebenzi yansuku zonke, okubangela ubunzima obukhulu bokulawulwa komqedazwe.
Nokho, ukutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV kwakucatshangwa ukuthi kwenzeka lapho iziguli zazigula kakhulu, kuyilapho ukutheleleka okuningi kungazange kwenzeke esigabeni sokuqala.
Ngenxa yalokho, ukubheduka kwe-COVID-19 kubucayi kakhulu futhi kunzima ukukulawula kunokubheduka kwe-SARS.
Kunemizamo eminingi eqhubekayo njengamanje e-China okuhlanganisa ukuvalwa thaqa kwe-Wuhan namadolobha azungezile nokuzivalela okuqhubekayo kwaso sonke isibalo sabantu ngethemba lokuphazamisa ukudluliswa kwe-SARS-CoV-2.
Nakuba lezi zinyathelo ziwulimaze kakhulu umnotho neminye imikhakha yezwe, inani leziguli ezintsha liyancipha, okubonisa ukuncipha kwejubane lomqedazwe.
Isilinganiso esithembisa kakhulu esokuthi ukubheduka kuzophela ngo-March futhi isigaba sokuncipha sizoqhubeka izinyanga ezingu-3-4.
Nokho, ezinye izazi azinalo lelo themba.
