Iqembu lase-Canada labika ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 yatholwa kuwo womabili amaswabhu e-mid-turbinate kanye nawomphimbo eziguli ezalulama futhi zaphuma esibhedlela emavikini amabili ngaphambilini, okubonisa ukuthi igciwane elisanda kutholwa kungenzeka ukuthi libe isiqephu esiphindayo esifana nemfuluwenza.
Nokho, izimpawu ezithembisayo zivele e-China ngokusekelwe enanini elehlayo labantu abasha abagulayo, okubonisa ukuthi amasu amanje kungenzeka ukuthi ayasebenza.
Ekuqaleni kwakubikezelwe ukuthi i-Ebola yayizophatha abantu abayisigidi futhi kufe ingxenye yesigidi sabantu.
Nokho, ngenxa yokuzivalela nokuzihlukanisa okuqinile, isifo sigcine silawuliwe.
Kungenzeka, njenge-SARS-CoV, ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ingase ibe buthaka ingabi namandla futhi ekugcineni iphele noma ibe igciwane elingagulisi kakhulu elikwazi ukuphilisana nabantu.
Ukuqhathaniswa komqedazwe we-COVID-19 nalowo we-SARS kanye ne-MERS kunikezwa ngezansi (Umfa. ​(Umfa.55).
I-SARS-CoV-2 ithelelana kakhulu ngokukhwehlela noma ukuthimula, futhi kungenzeka ukuthi ngokuthintana okuqondile nezinto ezinegciwane.
Igciwane laphinde futhi latholwa endleni, okuveza ithuba elisha lokudluliselwa okusuka endleni kuye emlonyeni.
Ucwaningo lwakamuva lweziguli ezingu-138 lwabika ukuthi u-41% weziguli kungenzeka ukuthi zatheleleka ezibhedlela, okuhlanganisa iziguli ezingu-17 ezazivele ziphethwe ezinye izifo ngaphambilini kanye nabanakekeli bezempilo abangu-40.
Ngenxa yalokho, kufanele kusetshenziswe ukuqapha okukhulu ukuze kuvikelwe abantu, ikakhulukazi abahlinzeki bokunakekelwa kwezempilo, osonhlalakahle, amalungu omndeni, ozakwabo, ngisho nabantu abame eduze kweziguli noma abantu abathelelekile.
Umugqa wokuqala wokuvikeleka ongase usetshenziswe ukuze kwehliswe ubungozi bokutheleleka uwukugqoka amamaski obuso; kokubili ukusetshenziswa kwemaski yokuhlinzwa kanye namamaski e-N95 respirator (uchungechunge # 1860s) kusiza ukulawula ukubhebhetheka kwamagciwane.
Amamaski obuso okuhlinza avimba amaconsana awuketshezi avela kumuntu okungenzeka ukuthi uthelelekile ukuthi angahambi ngomoya futhi anamathele ebusweni bezinto, lapho engadluliselwa khona kwabanye abantu.
Nokho, amamaski e-N95 (uchungechunge # 1860s) kuphela angakwazi ukukuvikela ekuhogeleni ama-virion amancane ngo-10 kuye ku-80 nm, kuyilapho u-5% kuphela wama-virion okwazi ukudlula ngokuphelele; i-SARS-CoV-2 inosayizi ofanayo nowe-SARS-CoV kokubili kucishe kube ngu-85 nm.
Njengoba izinhlayiya zikwazi ukudlula kumamaski okuhlinza amahlanu ahlanganisiwe, abahlinzeki bezempilo abasebenza ngokuqondile neziguli kumelwe bagqoke amamaski e-N95 (uchungechunge # 1860s) hhayi amamaski okuhlinza.
Ngaphezu kwamamaski, abahlinzeki bokunakekelwa kwezempilo kufanele bagqoke amagawuni okuzivikela abalingana kahle ukuze kuncishiswe ngokwengeziwe ukuthintana namagciwane.
Amagciwane angakwazi ukungena kumuntu ngamehlo.
Ngo-January 22, 2020, udokotela watheleleka nge-SARS-CoV-2 nakuba ayegqoke imaski ye-N95; igciwane kungenzeka ukuthi langena emzimbeni wakhe ngokuthi lingene emehlweni akhe avuvukele.
Ngenxa yalokho, abahlinzeki bokunakekelwa kwezempilo kufanele futhi bagqoke izivikeli zobuso ezingakwazi ukukubonisa noma izibuko ngenkathi besebenza ngeziguli.
Kumphakathi ovamile ezindaweni ezithintekile noma okungenzeka ukuthi zithintekile, kutuswa kakhulu ukuthi wonke umuntu ageze izandla zakhe ngensipho ekhucululayo izikhathi eziningi kunokuvamile, azame ukuhlala endlini ukuze azivalele futhi akhawule ukuxhumana nabantu okungenzeka ukuthi bathelelekile.
Ibanga elingamagxathu amathathu libhekwa njengebanga elifanele lokuthi abantu baqele kude neziguli.
Lezi zinyathelo ziyizindlela ezisebenzayo zokunciphisa ingozi yokungenwa isifo kanye nokuvimba ukusakazeka kwegciwane.
Nakuba i-SARS-CoV-2 yafika njengegciwane elisha emhlabeni wabantu, ukuba kwayo nesakhiwo esifanayo ne-SARS-CoV njengoba kwabikwa ngo-7 January 2020 kwakufanele kube isixwayiso e-China ngenxa yokuthi yayisakukhumbula ukubheduka kwe-SARS ngo-2003.
Nokho, kwaze kwaba u-19 January 2020 umqondisi we-Center of Disease Control e-Wuhan eqinisekisa izakhamuzi ukuthi igciwane elisha linokuthathelana okuncane futhi linokukhiqizeka kabusha okuncane lapho lisuka komunye umuntu liye komunye nokuthi akuyona inkinga ukuvimba nokulawula isifo.
Lo myalezo wenza umphakathi ukuthi ungaxwayi, ikakhulukazi lapho lonke izwe lalilungiselela i-Spring Festival, futhi baphuthelwa isikhathi esibucayi sokulawula igciwane ngenkathi lingakabhebhetheki lisase-Wuhan.
Ama-ejensi okulawula isifo ase-China angase afunde kulesi sifundo esibucayi futhi enze intuthuko ebalulekile esikhathini esizayo.
Ngokwesibonelo, lawa ma-ejensi kufanele (1) acophelele kakhudlwana lapho enza izimemezelo zomphakathi njengoba igama ngalinye libalulekile kuzakhamuzi futhi lingashintsha izimo zawo zengqondo kanye nezinqumo; (2) azwele futhi asabele kakhudlwana kulwazi olungajwayelekile oluvela emtholampilo kunokuba alinde imibiko egunyaziwe evela kodokotela noma izikhulu; (3) avimbe kakhudlwana ukuze alawule okungase kube umqedazwe ngenkathi kusasesigabeni sako sokuqala kunokuba bazame ukududuza umphakathi; futhi (4) enze kaningi amadrili aqondiswayo nasebenzayo ukuze kuthuthukiswe ukuqapha komphakathi mayelana nezifo ezingumqedazwe futhi kuhlolwe futhi kuthuthukiswe isistimu yokusabela komphakathi nezikhathi ezithile.
Ukubheduka kwe-COVID-19 okubangelwe igciwane elisha le-SARS-CoV-2 ekupheleni kuka-December 2019.
Ezinyangeni ezingaphansi kwezimbili, selisakazekele kulo lonke elase-China kanye nakwamanye amazwe acishe abe ngu-50 emhlabeni wonke ngesikhathi kubhalwa lokhu.
Njengoba igciwane lifana kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV futhi nezimpawu ziyafana futhi phakathi kwe-COVID-19 ne-SARS, ukubheduka kwe-COVID-19 kudale umuzwa wokuthi i-SARS iyaphinda.
Nokho, kukhona ukuhluka okuphawulekayo phakathi kwe-COVID-19 ne-SARS, okubalulekile ukuze kulawulwe umqedazwe kanye nokwelashwa kweziguli.
I-COVID-19 ithinta abantu adala abaningi kunetsha kanye nabantu besilisa abaningi kunabantu besifazane, futhi ubucayi nezinga lokufa liphinde libe phezulu kubantu abadala kunasentsheni.
I-SARS inezinga lokufa eliphakeme kune-COVID-19 (u-10.91% uqhathaniswa no-1.44%).
Iziguli ze-COVID-19 zidlulisa igciwane ngisho nalapho zingenazo izimpawu kuyilapho iziguli eziphethwe i-SARS zilidlulisela uma sezigula kakhulu, okubangela inkinga enkulu nakakhulu yokulawula ukubhebhetheka kwe-COVID-19 kune-SARS.
Lokhu kuchaza ngokwengxenye isizathu esenza ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ibhebhetheke ngokushesha kakhulu nakabanzi kune-SARS-CoV.
Ukuhlaziywa okuvamile kwe-RNA ye-SARS-CoV-2 kungase kube negethivu kwezinye iziguli ze-COVID-19.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, iziguli ezilashiwe zingase ziphinde zibe phozithivu lapho kuhlolwa igciwane.
Lokhu okutholiwe kunyusa kakhulu ubungozi bokubhebhetheka kwegciwane.
Njengoba kunenqubekela-phambili esheshayo kucwaningo lwe-COVID-19, kusele izinkinga ezimbalwa ezibucayi okudingeka ukuthi zixazululwe, ezihlanganisa ukuthi:
Iqhamuka kuphi i-SARS-CoV-2?
Nakuba kwathola ukuthi kunokufana okungu-96% kwesakhiwo sezakhi zofuzo phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kanye nama-CoV amabili amalulwane afana ne-SARS, asikwazi ukuphetha ngokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 iqhamuka emalulwaneni.
Yisiphi isilwane esasimaphakathi nendawo esadlulisela igciwane ukusuka kumbungazi wokuqala, ake sithi amalulwane, ukuya kubantu?
Uma singazazi izimpendulo zika-#1 no-2, asikwazi ukunqamula ngempumelelo ukudluliswa, futhi ukubheduka kungaba kubi nakakhulu nganoma yisiphi isikhathi.
Nakuba amamodeli amangqamuzana kanye nokuhlaziywa kwe-biochemical kubonise ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 inamathela ku-ACE2, igciwane lingena kanjani ngempela kumaseli omgudu wokuphefumula futhi libangele izinguquko ezibangela ukugula okuwumphumela?
Ingabe igciwane liphinde linamathele kumaseli abonisa i-ACE2 kwezinye izitho zomzimba?
Ngaphandle kwezimpendulo ezicacile zale mibuzo, asikwazi ukufinyelela ukuxilongwa okusheshayo nokunembile kanye nokwelashwa okusebenzayo.
Umqedazwe uzoqhubeka isikhathi eside kangakanani?
Izakhi zofuzo zegciwane zishintsha kanjani phakathi nokuthelelana phakathi kwabantu?
Ingabe lizoba ubhubhane lomhlaba wonke, ingabe lizophela njenge-SARS noma lizoba libi nakakhulu ngezikhathi ezithile njengomkhuhlane?
Kubalulekile kodwa kungase kuthathe isikhathi esithile ukucinga izimpendulo zemibuzo engenhla kanye neminye imibuzo eminingi.
Nokho, kungakhathaliseki ukuthi kuzodingeka izindleko ezingakanani, asinakho okunye ukukhetha ngaphandle kokuvimba umqedazwe ngokushesha ngokunokwenzeka futhi sibuyisele izimpilo zethu esimweni esivamile.
Imisuka yegciwane elisuka ezilwaneni liye kubantu yama-coronavirus abantu
Ushintsho nokuvumelana nesimo kukhuthaze i-co-evolution yama-coronavirus (ama-CoV) kanye nombungazi wawo, okuhlanganisa abantu, izinkulungwane zeminyaka.
Ngaphambi kuka-2003, ama-CoV amabili wabantu (ama-HCoV) waye aziwa njengebangela ukugula okuncane, njengomkhuhlane ovamile.
Ukubheduka kwe-severe acute respiratory syndrome (I-SARS) kanye ne-Middle East respiratory syndrome (I-MERS) kushintshe isimo ukuze kubonise ukuthi isifo se-HCoV singabangela umonakalo omkhulu futhi sisongele ukuphila kakhulu kangakanani.
Ukuvela kwe-SARS-CoV-2 e-China emaphakathi ekupheleni kuka-2019 kuphinde kwabeka ama-CoV eshashalazini futhi yasimangaza ngokutheleleka okuphakeme kodwa nge-pathogenicity encishisiwe uma iqhathaniswa nodadewabo i-SARS-CoV.
Isifo se-HCoV siyi-zoonosis futhi ukuqonda imisuka ye-zoonotic yama-HCoV kungasisiza.
Ama-HCoV amaningi aqhamuka kumalulwane futhi awakubangeli ukugula kuwona.
Ababungazi abamaphakathi bamanye ama-HCoV nabo bayaziwa.
Ukuhlonza ababungazi abayizilwane kunemiphumela eqondile ekuvinjweni kwezifo zabantu.
Ukucwaninga ukusebenzelana kombungazi we-CoV ezilwaneni kungase kuveze ukuqonda okubalulekile mayelana nokwakheka kwe-CoV kubantu.
Kulesi sibuyekezo, sethula isifinyezo solwazi olukhona kakade mayelana nama-HCoV ayisikhombisa, futhi sizogxila emlandweni wokutholwa kwawo kanye nomsuka wawo we-zoonotic kanye nokuthelelana kwezidalwa ezihlukahlukene.
Okubaluleke nakakhulu, siqhathanisa futhi sihlukanise ama-HCoV ahlukene ngokombono wokushintsha kwegciwane kanye nokuhlanganiswa kwezakhi zofuzo.
Umqedazwe wamanje wesifo se-CoV ka-2019 (I-COVID-19) kuxoxwa ngawo kulo mongo.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, izimfuneko zokushintsha kombungazi ngempumelelo kanye nemiphumela yokushintsha kwegciwane ekubeni bucayi kwesifo nayo iyagqanyiswa.
Ama-Coronavirus (ama-CoV) ayingxenye yomndeni we-Coronaviridae, owakhiwa iqembu lamagciwane elivalelekile, elinomuzwa-ophozithivu, elinomucu-owodwa we-RNA.
Lawa magciwane aqukethe i-genome enkulu kunawo wonke engu-26 kuye ku-32 kilobases phakathi kwamagciwane e-RNA abizwa ngokuthi “ama-CoV” ngenxa ye-morphology yawo efana nomqhele ngaphansi kwe-microscope ye-electron.
Ngokwesakhiwo, ama-CoV anama-genome angenazo izingxenye anokuhleleka okufanayo.
Cishe izingxenye ezintathu ze-genome zinamafreyimu okufunda avulekile amabili amakhulu agibelene (ORF1a ne-ORF1b), ahunyushwe ukuze abe ama-replicase polyprotein e-pp1a ne-pp1ab.
Ama-polyprotein acutshungulwa ngokwengeziwe ukuze akhe amaphrotheni engeziwe angu-16 angenaso isakhiwo, abizwa ngokuthi i-nsp1~16.
Ingxenye esele ye-genome iqukethe ama-ORF amaphrotheni esakhiwo, okuhlanganisa i-spike (S), imvilophu (E), i-membrane (M) ne-nucleoprotein (N).
Inani lamaphrotheni ezinsiza eziqondene nohlu nalo linekhodi yezinhlu ezihlukahlukene zama-CoV.
Ngokusekelwe kumehluko wokulandelana kwamaphrotheni, ama-CoV afakwa ngokwezigaba zemikhakha emine (i-alpha-CoV, i-beta-CoV, i-gamma-CoV ne-delta-CoV), lapho umkhakha we-beta-CoV uqukethe iningi lama-HCoV futhi uhlukaniswe waba izinhlu ezine (A, B, C no-D).
Ubufakazi be-phylogenetic bubonise ukuthi amalulwane namagundane awumthombo wezakhi zofuzo zama-alpha-CoV kanye nama-beta-CoV, kuyilapho izinyoni ziwumthombo wama-gamma-CoV nama-delta-CoV.
Sekunezinkulungwane zeminyaka, ama-CoV eqa ngokuqhubekayo imingcele yezidalwa futhi iningi lawo liphenduke ama-pathogen abalulekile kubantu.
Kuze kube manje, kwaziwa ama-CoV abantu (HCoVs) ayisikhombisa.
Phakathi kwawo i-HCoV-229E ne-HCoV-NL63 angama-alpha-CoV.
Amanye ama-beta-CoV ayisihlanu abandakanya i-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-HKU1, i-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus (SARS-CoV), i-Middle East respiratory syndrome coronavirus (MERS-CoV) ne-SARS-CoV-2.
I-HCoV-229E, i-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-HKU1 ne-HCoV-NL63 ngokuvamile kubangela izimpawu ezincane, njengomkhuhlane ovamile kanye/noma isifo sohudo.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, i-SARS-CoV, i-MERS-CoV kanye ne-SARS-CoV-2 esanda kutholwa kubangela ukugula okukhulu, okubangela isifo esibucayi somgudu ongezansi wokuphefumula ezigulini eziningi kakhulu okubangela ithuba eliphakeme lokwakheka kwe-acute respiratory distress syndrome (ARDS) nezinye izifo ezenzeka ngaphandle kwamaphaphu.
Uhlobo lokuqala lwe-HCoV-229E, i-B814, lwahlukaniswa kokwakuphuma emakhaleni eziguli ezinomkhuhlane ovamile maphakathi nawo-1960.
Kusukela ngaleso sikhathi, kwatholwa ulwazi olwengeziwe ngezincwaningo eziningiliziwe ze-HCoV-229E kanye ne-HCoV-OC43, kokubili okubangela izimpawu ezizikhawulayo.
Empeleni, kwakwamukelwe umbono wokuthi ukuphathwa ama-HCoV ngokuvamile akunabo ubungozi kwaze kwaba yilapho kubheduka i-SARS.
Ukubheduka kwe-SARS okwenzeka ngo-2003 kungokunye okudabukisa kakhulu emlandweni wamanje, yagulisa abantu abangaphezu kuka-8,000 futhi yayinezinga lokufa elicishe libe ngu-10%.
Eminyakeni eyishumi kamuva, ukubheduka kwe-Middle East respiratory syndrome (I-MERS) kwaphumela kumqedazwe oqhubekayo e-Arabian Peninsula okunokubhebhetheka okwenzeka ngezikhathi ezithile kwezinye izingxenye zomhlaba.
I-HCoV entsha ka-2019 (2019-nCoV), kamuva eqanjwe ngokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2, iyi-ejenti eyimbangela yomqedazwe oqhubekayo wesifo se-coronavirus ka-2019 (COVID-19), esibulale abantu abangaphezu kuka-3,120 futhi yathelela abantu abangaphezu kuka-91,000 ngo-March 3, 2020.
I-alamu ibilokhu ikhala futhi umhlaba kufanele ulungele ubhubhane oluzayo lwe-SARS-CoV-2.
Wonke ama-HCoV ayisikhombisa anomsuka we-zoonotic osuka kumalulwane, amagundane noma izilwane ezifuywayo.
Ubufakazi obuningi busekela umsuka wokuziphendukela kwawo wonke ama-HCoV ukusuka kumalulwane, lapho amagciwane ezivumelanise khona kahle nesimo futhi engakubangeli ukugula kodwa ebonisa ukuhlukahluka kwezakhi zofuzo okuningi.
Umqedazwe we-COVID-19 ubeke izinselele ezinkulu zokwelashwa, zesayensi, zomphakathi nezezimilo e-China nasemhlabeni.
Ukulandelela imisuka ye-zoonotic yama-HCoV kunikeza uhlaka lokuqonda umlando ongokwemvelo, amandla ashukumisayo nezici zokukhawula zokugxuma kwezidalwa.
Lokhu kungaphinde futhi kuqondise noma kusize ekucingeni imbangela, okumaphakathi kanye nokwenziwa kwamakhophi esilwane esingumbungazi(ezingumbungazi) se-SARS-CoV-2, okuzoba nemithelela ebalulekile ekuvinjweni kokuyidlulisela esikhathini esizayo.
Kulesi sibuyekezo sethula isifinyezo semisuka ye-zoonotic, ukuthelelana kwezidalwa ezihlukene kanye ne-pathogenesis yama-HCoV.
Ikakhulukazi, sigqamisa futhi sixoxe ngetimu efanayo yokuthi amagciwane angumzali wama-HCoV ngokuvamile awakubangeli ukugula kumbungazi wawo ongokwemvelo kodwa abangela ukugula ngemva kokuthi kuthelelane izidalwa ezihlukahlukene nombungazi omusha.
Siphinde futhi sibuyekeze ithrendi yokuziphendukela kwe-HCoV lapho ukwanda kokuthelelana kuvame ukufika nokwehla kwe-pathogenicity.
Imiphumela yokubheduka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 eqhubekayo kuphinde kuxoxwe ngayo kulo mongo.
Ama-CoV ezilwane abelokhu aziwa kusukela ekupheleni kwawo-1930.
Ngaphambi kokuhlukaniswa kokuqala kohlobo lwe-HCoV-229E oluthi B814 kulokho okwaphuma emakhaleni eziguli ezazithole umkhuhlane ovamile, ama-CoV ahlukene ayehlukanisiwe kuzilwane ezithelelekile ezinhlobonhlobo, okuhlanganisa igalikuni, igundane, inkomo, ingulube, ikati nenja.
Emashumini eminyaka edlule, kutholwe ama-HCoV ayisikhombisa.
Isifinyezo esifushane somlando wokutholwa kwama-HCoV ngokulandelana kwawo (Ithebula ​1) ungase uzuzise futhi ufundise.
Uhlobo lokuqala lwe-HCoV-229E lwahlukaniswa kumgudu wokuphefumula weziguli ezinesifo sokuphefumula somgudu ongenhla ngonyaka ka-1966, futhi lwamukelwa ukuze lukhule emigqeni yamaseli amaphaphu e-WI-38.
Iziguli eziphethwe i-HCoV-229E zazinezimpawu zomkhuhlane ovamile, okubandakanya ikhanda elibuhlungu, ukuthimula, i-malaise nomphimbo obuhlungu, futhi imfiva nokukhwehlela kwabonwa kuzigameko ezingu-10~20%.
Kamuva ngo-1967, i-HCoV-OC43 yahlukanisa esithweni sesicubu kanye nomgudu wochungechunge olulandelayo ebuchosheni bamagundane ancelayo.
Izici zokwelashwa zesifo se-HCoV-OC43 zibonakala zifana nalezo ezibangelwa yi-HCoV-229E, eyayingahlukaniseki ngokwezimpawu ekuthelelekeni ngezinye izifo zomgudu wokuphefumula ezifana namagciwane emfuluwenza A kanye nama-rhinoviruse.
Kokubili i-HCoV-229E kanye ne-HCoV-OC43 kusakazeke embulungeni yonke, futhi kuvame ukuthelelana phakathi nenkathi yasebusika esimweni sezulu esikahle.
Ngokuvamile, isikhathi sokufukanyelwa salawa magciwane amabili singaphansi kweviki elilodwa, kulandele cishe amaviki angu-2 okugula.
Ngokocwaningo lwamavolontiya angabantu, abantu abaphile kahle abaphethwe i-HCoV-229E babhekana nomkhuhlane omncane ovamile.
Iziguli ezimbalwa kuphela ezinamasosha omzimba acindezelekile ezabonisa ukuba nesifo esibucayi somgudu wokuphefumula ongezansi.
I-SARS, ephinde yaziwe ngokuthi “inyumoniya engavamile”, yaba ubhubhane lokuqala olubangelwa i-HCoV oluqoshiwe emlandweni wabantu futhi iyi-ejenti eyimbangela ye-SARS-CoV, i-HCoV yesithathu etholiwe.
Ukugula kokuqala okubangelwa yi-SARS kungakwazi ukulandelelwa kufike ekupheleni kuka-2002 e-Guangdong Province yase-China.
Umqedazwe we-SARS waholela embikweni wabantu abagulayo abangu-8,096 nabantu abangu-774 abafile, abasakazeke emazweni nasemazwekazini amaningi.
Ngaphandle kwababhebhethekisi abakhulu, kwalinganiselwa ukuthi isigameko ngasinye sasingabangela ezinye izigameko ezingaba zimbili, ngenkathi yokufukanyelwa yezinsuku ezingu-4 ukuya ku-7 futhi ukuphakama komthamo wegciwane kwavela osukwini lwe-10 lokugula.
Iziguli ezitheleleke nge-SARS-CoV ekuqaleni zazibonakala ziphethwe i-myalgia, ikhanda elibuhlungu, imfiva, i-malaise kanye nomkhuhlane, olandelwa yi-dyspnea, ukukhwehlela kanye nengcindezi yokuphefumula njengezimpawu zakamuva.
