Lo mbungazi omaphakathi angase abe umthombo oyi-zoonotic yokutheleleka kwabantu futhi adlale indima yokukhulisa umbungazi okuvumela igciwane ukuthi liphindeke isikhashana futhi lidluliselwe kubantu ukuze kukhuliswe izinga lokutheleleka kwabantu.
