I-angiotensin converting enzyme 2 (I-ACE2) yabantu yaziwa njengesisabeli se-SARS-CoV.
I-WIV1 ethathwe kusampula lendle yamalulwane kwaboniswa ukuthi isebenzisa ilulwane, i-civet kanye ne-ACE2 yabantu njengesisabeli sokungena kuseli.
