Ngakolunye uhlangothi, izingcwaningo e-Middle East ziye zabonisa ukuthi amakamela e-dromedary a-seropositive kuzivikeli-mzimba ezibulala i-MERS-CoV ngokuqondile, ngokufana namakamela adabuka e-Middle East emazweni amaningi ase-Afrika.
