Kuyaphawuleka futhi ukuthi ngokuvamile kwabonwa izimpawu ezincane kodwa ukukhishwa okukhulu kwegciwane kumakamela athelelekile nge-MERS-CoV ngokocwaningo.
Kuyaphawuleka, ukuthi amakamela athelelekile awagcinanga ukukhipha amagciwane ngomgudu wokuphefumula kuphela kodwa futhi nangomgudu wendle-womlomo, okuphinde kube umzila oyinhloko wokukhishwa kwegciwane elivela kumalulwane.
