Lokho kusho ukuthi, amalulwane kungenzeka ukuthi awayena umbungazi owumthombo oseduze we-SARS-CoV-2 ngaphandle kwalapho kutholwa ama-CoV elulwane acishe afane esikhathini esizayo.
Kucatshangelwa ukuthi, ababungazi besilwane esimaphakathi se-SARS-CoV-2 kufanele babe phakathi kwezilwane zasendle ezidayiswa futhi zibulawe e-Huanan Seafood Wholesale Market, iningi lazo lalihlobene nokugula kokuqala kwe-COVID-19, okubonisa ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi kwaba nesenzakalo sokuthelelana okusuka kuzilwane kuye kubantu.
Izingcwaningo zakamuva ezimbalwa ezisekelwe ekulandelaneni kwe-metagenomic ziye zasikisela ukuthi iqembu lezilwane ezincane ezincelisayo ezaziwa ngokuthi ama-pangolin (i-Manis javanica) kungenzeka ukuthi zifukamele ama-beta-CoV amadala ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Lawa ma-genome amasha e-pangolin CoV abelana ngo-85-92% we-homology yokulandelana kwe-nucleotide ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Nokho, ahlobene ngokuseduze ngokulinganayo ne-RaTG13 ngomazisi ocishe ube ngu-90% ezingeni lokulandelana kwe-nucleotide.
Ahlangana abe yizinhlu ezingaphansi ezimbili zamagciwane acishe afane ne-SARS-CoV-2 esihlahleni esi-phylogenetic, esinye sazo sabelana ngesizinda sokunamathisela sesisabeli esifana kakhulu (i-RBD) ne-SARS-CoV-2, nokufana kokulandelana kwe-amino acid okungu-97.4%.
Ngokungafani okukhulu, ama-RBD e-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 ahlukene kakhulu, nakuba kunezinga eliphakeme le-genome ebanzi yokulandelana kwe-homology.
Ucwaningo lwangaphambilini lwama-pangolin agulayo lwabika ukutholwa kwama-contig egciwane kumasampula amaphaphu, okubonakala ehlobene ngokufanayo ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Lolu cwaningo lwasebenzisa izindlela zokwakhiwa ezihlukahlukene kanye nokuhlelwa okwenziwa ngesandla ukuze kwakhiwe ukulandelana kwe-genome eyingxenye eyakhiwa cishe u-86.3% wobude obuphelele be-genome yegciwane.
Asikwazi ukubekela eceleni ithuba lokuthi i-pangolin ingesinye sezilwane ezingababungazi abaseduze be-SARS-CoV-2.
Nokho, okwamanje abukho ubufakazi obusekela ukuthi i-pangolin ingumsuka oqondile we-SARS-CoV-2 ngenxa yokuhlukahluka kokulandelana phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kanye ne-SARS-CoV-2 ye-pangolin ehlobene nama-beta-CoV.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ibanga eliphakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kanye ne-RaTG13 lifushane nakakhulu phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kanye ne-SARS-CoV-2 ye-pangolini ehlobene nama-beta-CoV.
Umgudu wokuziphendukela we-SARS-CoV-2 kumalulwane, ama-pangolin nezinye izilwane ezincelisayo usazotholwa.
Nakuba i-homology yokulandelana okuphakeme itholiwe kuma-RBD phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-pangolin, i-SARS-CoV-2 ehlobene nama-beta-CoV, i-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 kwabelana nge-homology ephakeme yokulandelana kwe-genome ebanzi.
Kunezinsolo eziphakeme zokuthi izinga eliphakeme lokufana phakathi kwama-RBD e-SARS-CoV-2 ye-pangolini ehlobene nama-beta-CoV kanye ne-SARS-CoV-2 kuqhutshwa ukuziphendukela kokuhlangana okuxhumana ngokukhethwa.
Esinye isiphakamiso sincoma ukuhlanganiswa kabusha okuphakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ye-pangolini ehlobene ne-beta-CoV kanye ne-RaTG13 kusilwane sesithathu sasendle.
Njengamandla aqhuba ukuziphendukela, ukuhlanganiswa kabusha kusakazekile phakathi kwama-beta-CoV.
Isiphetho asikafinyelelwa ngokuqondene nomsuka we-zoonotic eseduze ye-SARS-CoV-2.
Ngaphandle kwama-HCoV a-pathogenic kakhulu, umsuka we-zoonotic ye-HCoV-229E, i-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-NL63 kanye ne-HCoV-HKU1 nawo ucwaningiwe.
Ubufakazi be-phylogenetic bubonise ukuthi kokubili i-HCoV-NL63 kanye ne-HCoV-229E kungenzeka ukuthi kwaqala kuma-CoV elulwane, kuyilapho amagciwane angumzali e-HCoV-OC43 kanye ne-HCoV-HKU1 etholwe kumagundane.
Kubikwe ukuthi i-CoV yelulwane ebizwa ngokuthi i-ARCoV.2 (i-Appalachian Ridge CoV) etholwe elulwaneni elinemibala emithathu laseNyakatho Melika yabonisa ubudlelwano obuseduze ne-HCoV-NL63.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, i-HCoV-229E yayihlobene ngokwezakhi zofuzo nenye i-CoV yelulwane, ebizwa ngokuthi i-Hipposideros/GhanaKwam/19/2008, eyatholwa e-Ghana, kuyilapho ama-camelid aye asolwa ngokuba umbungazi wayo oseduze.
Ukuze sicacise, ulwazi lwamanje oluphathelene nemisuka eyizilwane yama-HCoV aziwayo lufinyezwe Kumfanekiso ​1 kanye Nethebula 2.
Ukuhlaziywa kwe-phylogenetic kunikeze ubufakazi bezigameko zokuthelelana kwezidalwa zama-HCoV emlandweni.
Ngenkathi i-HCoV-OC43 isuka kwesinye isilwane ukuze idluliselwe kubantu yasuka ezilwaneni ezifuywayo cishe ngo-1890, kwaqoshwa ubhubhane lwesifo sokuphefumula .
Umlando wokuthelelana kwezidalwa ezihlukahlukene we-HCoV-229E awucacile kakhulu.
Kutholwe ama-alpha-CoV elulwane ahlobenene-HCoV-229E.
Phakathi kwawo kukhona i-alpha-CoV ye-alpaca.
Ubufakazi obumbalwa busekela ukudluliswa kwegciwane lisuka emalulwaneni liye kubantu ngokuqondile.
Okokuqala, abantu hhayi ama-alpaca kungenzeka ukuthi baxhumane namalulwane endaweni ezungezile efanayo.
Kunalokho, abantu abasondelana ngokuseduze nama-alpaca.
Okwesibili, ama-alpha-CoV elulwane ahlobene ne-HCoV-229E ahlukahlukene futhi awakubangeli ukugula kumalulwane, kuyilapho i-alpha-CoV ye-alpaca yabangela ukubheduka kwesifo sokuphefumula kuzilwane ezithelelekile.
Okugcina, i-alpha-CoV ye-alpaca ayikatholwa kuzilwane zasendle.
Ngenxa yalokho, ngeke silishalazele ithuba lokuthi ama-alpaca athola i-alpha-CoV ehlobene ne-HCoV-229E kubantu.
Eqinisweni, amalulwane awumthombo oqondile wamagciwane abangela ukugula kwabantu okuhlanganisa igciwane lamarabi, igciwane le-Ebola, igciwane le-Nipah kanye negciwane le-Hendra.
Ngakho akumangalisi ukuthi amalulwane kungenzeka adlulisele i-HCoV-229E kubantu ngokuqondile.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, lapho ama-alpha-CoV elulwane esebenza njengeqoqo lezakhi zofuzo ze-HCoV-229E, ama-alpaca kanye namakamela e-dromedary kungenzeka ukuthi angumbungazi omaphakathi odlulisela igciwane kubantu, njengoba kunjalo nge-MERS-CoV.
I-MERS-CoV iyisibonelo esihle sokuthelelana kwezidalwa ezingafani kusukela kumalulwane kuye kumakamela e-dromedary kuye kubantu.
Umsuka wokuziphendukela kwe-MERS-CoV evela kumalulwane uyaziwa ekuhlonzweni kwayo kokuqala futhi uqiniswe ngokutholiwe okulandelayo.
Kusobala ukuthi amalulwane anikeza izinhlobonhlobo zamagciwane ithuba lokuthi kube nokushintshana kwezingxenye zezakhi zofuzo phakathi kwezilwane ezihlukene kanye nokuthelelana kwezilwane ezihlukene.
Impilo ende, amakoloni aminyene, ukusondelana komphakathi okuseduze kanye nekhono elinamandla lokundiza konke kuyizimo ezikahle zokuthi amalulwane abe 'umbhebhethekisi wegciwane' okahle.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, sekungamakhulu eminyaka i-MERS-CoV yethulwe kumakamela e-dromedary.
Ivumelaniseke kahle kulawa makamela aphenduke ekubeni umbungazi omaphakathi aba umbungazi ozinzile nongumthombo ongokwemvelo.
I-MERS-CoV ibangela ukugula okuncane futhi inezinga lokushintsha eliphansi kulezi zilwane.
Ukutheleleka kwayo kubantu kuyiphutha futhi abantu bahlala bengumbungazi wokugcina we-MERS-CoV njengoba ukudluliswa kwayo kungakwazi ukulondolozwa.
Ngokungafani nendima yamakamela ekudlulisweni kwe-MERS-CoV, indima yama-pangolin, uma ikhona, ekudlulisweni kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ihlukile.
Ngokukhethekile, ama-beta-CoV e-pangolin abangela ukugula kakhulu kuma-pangolin.
Angase abe umbungazi wokugcina wama-beta-CoV ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2, ngokufana nama-civet esimweni se-SARS-CoV.
Amathuba ambalwa okuthelelana kwezidalwa ezingafani nge-SARS-CoV-2 kusukela ezilwaneni kuye kubantu kufanele zicatshangelwe noma zingacatshangelwa kuzingcwaningo zesikhathi esizayo.
Okokuqala, amalulwane kungenzeka abe umbungazi ongumthombo wegciwane elihlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2 elicishe lifane ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Abantu bangase badlale indima efanayo namalulwane ngokuhlinza izilwane noma ukumbiwa kwamalahle.
Okwesibili, ama-pangolin angase abe umbungazi okhulisayo omaphakathi lapho igciwane elihlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2 lisanda kwethulwa khona.
Abantu batheleleka ngegciwane ngokuhlinza nokudla inyama ezingelwayo.
Kungenzeka ukuthi izilwane eziningi ezincelayo okuhlanganisa nezilwane ezifuywayo zingachayeka ku-SARS-CoV-2.
Kudingeka inhlolovo yezivikeli-mzimba zezilwane ezifuywayo nezasendle.
Okwesithathu, njengoba kushiwo ngenhla, ukuhlanganiswa kabusha nokuvunyelaniswa nesimo kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kungenzeka kwenzeke esilwaneni sesithathu esixhumene nakho kokubili amalulwane nama-pangolin.
Ukucingwa kwesilwane esiwumsuka we-SARS-CoV-2 kusaqhubeka.
Ngaphandle kwezinhlobo ezihlukahlukene zababungazi abayizilwane, kunezici ezintathu ezinkulu ohlangothini lwegciwane ezibalulekile ekwenzeni ama-CoV eqe umngcele wezidalwa.
Okokuqala, inani lawo eliphakeme loshintsho ekuphindweni kwe-RNA.
Uma kuqhathaniswa namanye amagciwane e-RNA anomucu owodwa, isilinganiso samanani oshintsho lwama-CoV singase sibhekwe “njengesincane” kuye “kwesiphakeme” ngokwesilinganiso soshintsho esingu ~10-4 unyaka ngamunye ngesikhungo ngasinye sesi-2, kuye ngesigaba sokuvumelanisa kwe-CoV kubabungazi abasha.
Ama-CoV ane-exoribonuclease yokufuna amaphutha, ukususwa kwayo kuphumela ekushintsheni okuphakeme kakhulu nasekwehleni kwamandla noma ukungakwazi ukukhula ngendlela efanele.
Ngokuthakazelisayo, i-nucleotide analogue Remdesivir iyaziwa ukuthi icindezela ukuphindeka kwe-CoV ngokuvinjwa kwale exoribonuclease kanye ne-RNA polymerase encike ku-RNA.
I-Remdesivir ingenye yama-ejenti athembisa kakhulu alwa ne-SARS-CoV-2 ezohlolwa kuzingcwaningo zokwelashwa.
Noma kunjalo, amanani oshintsho lwama-CoV aphakeme cishe ngesigidi kunalawo ababungazi.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, inani loshintsho livame ukuba phezulu uma ama-CoV engavumelanisiwe kahle nombungazi.
Uma kuqhathaniswa ne-SARS-CoV enenani loshintsho eliphakeme, inani loshintsho le-SARS-CoV-2 libonakala liphansi, okusikisela izinga eliphezulu lokuvunyelaniswa nabantu.
Kucatshangelwa ukuthi, kungenzeka selivunyelanisiwe kakade nomunye umbungazi osondelene nabantu.
Ngaphezu kwe-SARS-CoV-2, lokhu kuphinde kusebenze ku-MERS-CoV, evumelana kahle namakamela e-dromedary.
Kucatshangelwa ukuthi cishe akunakwenzeka ukuthi ushintsho lwezakhi zofuzo lungabangela imigomo nemishanguzo yamagciwane emelene ne-SARS-CoV-2 ukuthi ingasebenzi ngokushesha.
Okwesibili, i-genome enkulu ye-RNA kuma-CoV isebenzisa ukuthamba okwengeziwe ekushintshweni kwe-genome kushintsho nokuhlanganiswa kabusha, ngaleyo ndlela kunyuswe ithuba le-co-evolution yezidalwa ezihlukahlukene, elizuzisayo ekuveleni kwama-CoV amasha lapho izimo zifaneleka.
Lokhu kusekelwa amafreyimu ahlukile amaningi okufunda avulekile nokusebenza kwephrotheni akhiqizelwa isiphetho esingu-3′ se-genome.
Okwesithathu, ama-CoV ahlalal ashintsha amathempulethi ngokungahleliwe phakathi nokuphindwa kwe-RNA ngendlela ehlukile “yokukhetha-kokukopisha”.
Kumbungazi osebenza njengesitsha sokuxuba, ukushintsha kohlobo kwenzeka njalo phakathi ne-transcription ye-CoV RNA.
Ama-RNA a-homologous kakhulu anobude obugcwele kanye na-subgenomic angase ahlangane kabusha ukuze akhe ama-CoV amasha.
Ubufakazi obuyi-phylogenetic bokuhlanganiswa kabusha okungokwemvelo butholwe kukho kokubili i-HCoV-HKU1, i-HCoV-OC43, kanye nama-CoV esilwane njenge-SL-CoV yelulwane kanye ne-batCoV-HKU9.
Ukusebenzisana kwegciwane nombungazi ngokuqondene nokutheleleka
Ngaphandle kwezici ezintathu zegciwane ezishiwo ngenhla, ukusebenzisana kwegciwane nesisabeli sombungazi kungesinye isici esiyinhloko esinethonya ekuthelelaneni kwezidalwa ezingafani.
Lapha, ukuhlanganiswa kabusha kwe-SARS-CoV kubhekwa njengesibonelo esivamile, esabonisa ubufakazi bokukhethwa okuphozithivu phakathi nezehlakalo zokuthelelana kwezidalwa ezihlukene.
Ngokusekelwe ekuhlaziyweni okuqhathanisayo phakathi kwabantu abahlukanisiwe kanye nama-SARS-CoV e-civet, kucatshangelwa ukuthi i-SARS-CoV ibhekana nokuvumelana nesimo okusheshayo kubabungazi abahlukene, ikakhulukazi ngoshintsho ku-RBD yephrotheni ka-S.
Ngokuvamile, i-RBD kuphrotheni ka-S ye-CoV isebenzisana nesisabeli seseli futhi ikhethwa ngokuqinile ukusabela kwesivikeli-mzimba sombungazi.
Ku-SARS-CoV, i-RBD ikuma-amino acid esi-318 kuye kweyesi-510 engxenyeni ye-S1, enamathela ku-ACE2 yomuntu kanye nama-coreceptor ayo ukuze kungene igciwane.
I-RBD ye-SARS-CoV iyakwazi ukubona izisabeli ze-ACE2 yezilwane ezihlukene, okuhlanganisa ilulwane, i-civet, igundane nenja ye-raccoon, okuvumela ukuthelelana ngegciwane kwezidalwa ezihlukene.
Eqinisweni, izinsalela ezingu-6 kuphela ze-amino acid okwaphawulwa ukuthi zihlukile kokuhlukanisiwe kwegciwane labantu kanye ne-civet ku-RBD okungu-4 kukho kutholakala ku-motif enamathela kusisabeli ukuze isebenzelane nesisabeli se-ACE2.
I-SARS-CoV ye-civet inoshintsho lwe-K479N kanye ne-S487T ku-RBD yayo, okungase kunyuse izinga lokuhlangana lokusebenzelana kwephrotheni ye-spike nesisabeli se-ACE2 yomuntu.
Ngamanye amazwi, lolu shintsho lwama-amino acid amabili lungase lubaluleke ekuvumelanisweni kwegciwane kubantu.
Kuyaphawuleka ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 inesisabeli esifanayo seseli ne-SARS-CoV.
Umehluko ka-30% phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-SARS-CoV kuyunithi ye-S1 yephrotheni ka-S usho ukuthi izinga lokuhlangana lephrotheni lika-S ne-ACE2 yabantu kungenzeka ukuthi lishintshile.
Empeleni, ucwaningo lwe-cryo-EM libonisa izinga eliphakeme lokugoqa okungu-10- ukuya ku-20- lalokhu kugoqa kunalokho okuphakathi kwe-ACE2 yabantu nephrotheni ka-S ye-SARS-CoV.
Kuzophinde futhi kuthakazelise ukunquma ukuthi ingabe iyadingeka yini enye i-coreceptor ekuthelelekeni kwe-SARS-CoV-2.
Ngokuthakazelisayo, i-HCoV-NL63 iphinde inamathele ku-ACE2 kodwa ngengxenye ehlukile ka-S.
Kukhona ezinye izisabeli ze-HCoV, njengama-aminopeptidase N e-HCoV-229E, kanye ne-9-O-acetylated sialic acid ye-HCoV-OC43.
Angase futhi abhekwe njengesizathu sokuzivumelanisa ngempumelelo kwama-CoV kubantu ngemva kokuthelelana kwezidalwa ezihlukene esuka kubabungazi bawo abayizilwane.
Ngaphezu kwezisabeli ezingamaseli, umphumela wokuthelelana kwezidalwa ezihlukene ngama-HCoV uphinde futhi ulawulwe ukuncika kwesinye isidalwa nezici zomkhawulo.
Ukwehluka kwalawa maphrotheni ombungazi phakathi kwabantu nababungazi abawumthombo ongokwemvelo wama-HCoV njengamalulwane, amakamela e-dromedary kanye namagundane kungase kubangele umngcele wokuthelelana kwezidalwa ezihlukene.
Ama-HCoV kufanele athathe izici zokuncika kumnikazi futhi aphazamise izici zokuvimvela kombungazi ukuze kube nokuthelelana kwezidalwa okuyimpumelelo.
Ngokuqondene nalokhu, izinqumi ezingamangqamuzana kule ndawo ebalulekile yokusebenzelana nombungazi wegciwane zisazobonwa futhi ziphawulwe.
Ukuhlungwa okubanzi kwe-genome okungachemile kokuncika kombungazi kanye nezici zokukhawulwa ze-SARS-CoV-2 ngokusebenzisa ubuchwepheshe besimanje be-CRISPR kungase kuzuzise.
Ukuqhamuka kwama-HCoV amasha: ukubuyela ekuqaleni
Ukwehlukahluka kwama-CoV elulwane kunikeza amathuba amaningi okuvela kwama-HCoV amasha.
Ngalo mqondo, ama-CoV elulwane asebenza njengeqoqo lezakhi zofuzo zama-HCoV.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ushintsho olusheshayo kanye nokuhlanganiswa kabusha kwezakhi zofuzo kuphinde kuqhube ukuziphendukela kwe-HCoV futhi kusebenza njengezinyathelo ezimbili ezibalulekile kule nqubo.
Ngokwesibonelo, ukutholwa noma ukulahleka kwezakhi zofuzo ezenza ikhodi yephrotheni entsha kunamandla okuwashintsha kakhulu ama-phenotype egciwane.
Phakathi kwamaphrotheni ayinsiza e-SARS-CoV, i-ORF8 kucatshangwa ukuthi ibalulekile ekuzivumelaniseni nabantu, njengoba amagciwane elulwane ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV ahlukaniswa kodwa atholwa ekhiqiza amaphrotheni e-ORF8 ahlukile.
Isici sokususwa kwe-29-nucleotide sama-SARS-CoV sitholwe ezinhlotsheni ezihlukanisiwe ekuqaleni komqedazwe wabantu.
Lokhu kususwa kuhlukanisa i-ORF8 ibe i-ORF8a kanye ne-ORF8b futhi kucatshangwa ukuthi iwushintsho oluzivumelanisayo olukhuthaza ukushintshwa kwababungazi.
Ngaphandle kwalokho, i-SARS-CoV ingase ibe nomlando wokuhlanganiswa kabusha nezinhlu zama-CoV e-alpha kanye ne-gamma, lapho kwatholwa khona inani elikhulu lezindawo zokuhlanganiswe kabusha okuncane ku-RNA polymerase encike ku-RNA.
Izindawo zokuhlanganiswa kabusha zatholwa futhi ku-nsp9, engxenyeni enkulu ye-nsp10, nasezingxenyeni ze-nsp14.
Ngokufanayo, kuye kwaboniswa ukuthi umqedazwe i-MERS-CoV yabhekana nezehlakalo zokuhlanganiswa kabusha phakathi kwezinhlu ezihlukene, okwenzeka kumakamela e-dromedary e-Saudi Arabia.
Ngaphandle kwe-SARS-CoV kanye ne-MERS-CoV, izehlakalo zokuhlanganiswa kabusha ziye zaphawulwa kwamanye ama-HCoV, lapho ama-HCoVs ehlangana kabusha namanye ama-CoV esilwane kuzakhi zawo zofuzo ezingenaso isakhiwo.
Kufanele futhi kuqashelwe ukuthi ukukhethwa kokwenziwa kungase kube nesandla ezinguqukweni ezingahlosiwe kuma-genome egciwane, okungase kube umphumela wokukhulula amagciwane ezingcindezeni zokukhetha ezisetshenzisiwe, njengalezo zamasosha omzimba zombungazi.
Isibonelo sale miphumela siwukulahleka kwe-ORF4 enobude obuphelele kuhlobo lwephrothothayiphu ethi HCoV-229E, ngenxa yokususwa kwe-nucleotide ekabili.
Nakuba i-ORF4 ephelele yabonwa kumagciwane elulwane nekamela ahlobene ne-HCoV-229E, i-alpha-CoV ye-alpaca ibonisa ukufakwa kwe-nucleotide eyodwa, okuholela ekushintsheni kwefreyimu.
Okokugcina kodwa okubalulekile, ukuziphendukela kwama-HCoV amasha kuphinde kuqhutshwe ingcindezi yokukhethwa kubabungazi bayo abawumthombo.
Zazingekho izimpawu noma kwakunezimpawu ezincane kuphela ezitholiwe lapho amalulwane etheleleka ngama-CoV, okubonisa ukuvumelaniswa okufanayo phakathi kwama-CoV namalulwane.
Kubonakala sengathi amalulwane avumelaniswe kahle nama-CoV ngokwesakhiwo nendlela yokusebenza.
Ngokwesibonelo, ukuphazamiseka kokusetshenziswa kokusabela okukhuthaza ukuvuvukala kumalulwane kuyinciphisa kalula i-pathology eqaliswa ama-CoV.
Ngaphandle kwalokho, umsebenzi weseli elingumbulali ongokwemvelo kumalulwane uyacindezelwa ngenxa yokwenyuka kokusabela kwesivimbi sesisabeli seseli elingumbulali ongokwemvelo elithi NKG2/CD94 kanye nezinga lokuboniswa eliphansi lamangqamuzana esigaba I esiyinkimbinkimbi se-histocompatibility.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, izinga eliphakeme lezidalwa ezisabela kumoya-mpilo (i-ROS) ezakhiwe ngomsebenzi wokugaywa kokudla okuphakeme kwamalulwane kungase kuthinte kokubili ukucindezelwa kokuphindwa kwe-CoV futhi kuthinte ukuhlolwa kwamaphutha nge-exoribonuclease, ngaleyo ndlela kunikeza ingcindezi yokukhethwa yokwakhiwa kwezinhlobo zegciwane ezi-pathogenic kakhulu lapho zethulwa kumbungazi omusha.
Izinhlobo ze-CoV ezi-pathogenic kakhulu zingase futhi zishintshe ngokuhlanganiswa kabusha, okuholela ekutholweni kwamaphrotheni amasha noma izici zephrotheni zokuvumelaniswa kombungazi.
Ngenxa yalokho, akuyona nje inhlanhla ukuthi ama-HCoV amasha amathathu avele emashumini amabili eminyaka edlule.
Ama-CoV awagulisani noma abangele izimpawu ezincane kubabungazi bawo abayinhloko njengamalulwane namakamela.
Aphindeka ngokushesha ngaphandle kokukhuthaza ukusabela okuqinile kwamasosha omzimba.
Lapha kunezimfihlo zokuthi kungani izithwali ezingenazo izimpawu zibonwa nokuthi yini ebangela izimo ezibucayi ekuguleni kwabantu.
Izimpawu ezibucayi ngokuyinhloko zibangelwa ukusebenza kakhulu kwamasosha omzimba kanye nesiphepho se-cytokine lapho kunokusabela kwamasosha omzimba okuqinile, umonakalo wamaphaphu uba mkhulu kakhulu.
Ngokuhlukile, kulabo abangazibonisi izimpawu zokugula, ukusabela kwamasosha omzimba kuye kwahlukaniswa kabili ekuphindweni kwe-CoV.
Isu elifanayo lokuhlukanisa ukusabela kwamasosha omzimba lingase libe nemiphumela ezuzisayo ekwelashweni okumelene ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Ukusabela kwe-interferon kuqine ngokukhethekile kumalulwane.
Ngenxa yalokho, ukusetshenziswa kohlobo I lwe-interferon okungenani ezigabeni zokuqala zokutheleleka nge-SARS-CoV-2 kubantu kufanele kuzuzise.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ukusetshenziswa kwe-NLRP3 inflammasome kumalulwane akusebenzi.
Ngokwalokhu kucabanga, ukuvinjwa kwe-NLRP3 inflammasome nge-MCC950 kungase kube usizo ekwelashweni kwe-COVID-19.
Ukuvela kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kulandela itimu evamile yokuvela kwe-SARS-CoV kanye ne-MERS-CoV.
Nakuba kutholwe i-beta-CoV yelulwane eyabelana ngo-95% we-nucleotide homology ne-SARS-CoV, kukhona futhi i-CoV yelulwane eyabelana ngo-96% we-nucleotide homology ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Nakuba ama-civet nezinye izilwane ezimakethe kutholwe ukuthi zifukamela amagciwane afana ne-SARS-CoV, ababungazi abamaphakathi abaseduze be-SARS-CoV-2 abakatholwa.
Kutholwe ama-beta-CoV e-pangolin anesakhiwo esifanayo ne-SARS-CoV-2, okubonisa ukuthi ama-pangolin kungenzeka ukuthi angabanye ababungazi abamaphakathi noma ama-beta-CoV ama-pangolin angase abe nesandla ezingxenyeni zezakhi zofuzo enguqulweni yokugcina ye-SARS-CoV-2.
Yize imibuzo isamile, abukho ubufakazi bokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 yakhiwe umuntu ngenhloso noma ngephutha.
Ama-CoV abuyele eshashalazini ngenxa yokubheduka kwakamuva kwe-SARS-CoV-2.
Ukucwaningwa kwama-CoV emalulwaneni nezinye izilwane kuwushintshe kakhulu umbono wethu wokubaluleka kwemisuka ye-zoonotic nemithombo eyizilwane yama-HCoV ekuthelelaneni kwabantu.
Ubufakazi obusakazekile bubonisa ukuthi i-SARS-CoV, i-MERS-CoV kanye ne-SARS-CoV-2 inomsuka oyilulwane futhi idluliselwa kubantu ngababungazi abamaphakathi.
Njengoba ukutheleleka nge-SARS-CoV kusuka ekuthintaneni okuphakathi kwabantu nama-civet ezimakethe, ukuvala izimakethe zezilwane eziphilayo nokubulala ama-civet kwakungase kuqede umqedazwe we-SARS.
Ngokucabanga okufanayo, ama-pangolin kufanele akhishwe ezimakethe ezidayisa izinto eziphilayo ukuze kuvinjelwe ukutheleleka oku-zoonotic, kucatshangelwa ukutholwa kwezinhlu eziningi zama-beta-CoV e-pangolin ahlobene ngokuseduze ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Nokho, ukuthi iyadluliselwa yini nokuthi idluliselwa kanjani i-SARS-CoV-2 kubantu ngama-pangolin nezinye izilwane ezincelisayo kusazocaciswa ezingcwaningweni zesikhathi esizayo.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, i-MERS-CoV ibilokhu ikhona kumakamela e-dromedary isikhathi eside.
Lawa makamela ayithuluzi elibalulekile lezokuthutha kanye nomthombo oyinhloko wenyama, ubusi, isikhumba nemikhiqizo kavolo kubantu basendaweni.
Asakazeke kabanzi e-Middle East nase-Africa.
Ngakho kuyinto engenakwenzeka ukuthi kubulawe wonke amakamela ukuze kulawulwe i-MERS, njengoba kwenzeka ezimakethe zezilwane zasendle e-China ukuze kuvinjwe ukusakazeka kwe-SARS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Ukuze kuvinjwe ukubheduka okuphindayo kwe-MERS, kufanele kusetshenziswe indlela eningilizayo ukuze kwakhiwe imigomo esebenzayo emelene ne-MERS-CoV yamakamela, ehambisana nezinye izinyathelo zokulawula isifo.
Njengoba singakwazi ukuqeda lawa magciwane, ama-genotype amasha angase avele ukuze abangele ukubheduka.
Izinhlobonhlobo zama-CoV a-zoonotic ziyajikeleza ehlane.
Ngokukhethekile, ama-CoV elulwane anamandla e-zoonotic ahlukahlukene kakhulu.
Kukhona amathuba amaningi okuthi lawa ma-CoV e-zoonotic ashintshe futhi ahlangane kabusha, okuzophumela kuma-CoV amasha akwazi ukuthelelana kakhulu kanye/noma abulale abantu esikhathini esizayo.
Isiko lokudla izilwane zasendle kwezinye izindawo zase-China kufanele liyekwe ukuze kuncishiswe ukuxhumana okungadingekile phakathi kwabantu nezilwane.
Ngezigameko ze-SARS, i-MERS kanye ne-COVID-19, kufanele kube khona uhlelo lokulungela nokusabela olungcono kakhulu.
Empeleni, amagciwane amaningi anesikhathi eside ekhona emhlabeni.
Ahlala ezindaweni zawo ezingokwemvelo kuze kube yilapho ethola ithuba lokuphuma.
Nakuba amalulwane enezici eziningi ezikhuthaza ukusakazwa kwamagciwane, ithuba lokuthi abantu baxhumane namalulwane nezinye izilwane zasendle angacishiswa uma abantu befundiswa ukuthi baqhele kuzona.
Ukugadwa okuqhubekayo kwezilwane ezincelisayo kuyadingeka ukuze kuqondwe kangcono i-ecology yama-CoV nababungazi bawo abangokwemvelo, okuzoba usizo ekuvimbeni ukutheleleka okusuka ezilwaneni kuye kubantu kanye nokubheduka kwesikhathi esizayo.
Uma sesiphetha, indlela engcono kakhulu yokuvimba i-zoonosis yamagciwane iwukuba abantu baqhele endaweni ezungezile eyimithombo engokwemvelo yamagciwane a-zoonotic.
Izingxenye ezimbalwa ze-puzzle yomsuka we-zoonotic ye-SARS-CoV-2 azikatholakali.
Okokuqala, uma amalulwane edlulisa igciwane eliwukhokho we-SARS-CoV-2 kuma-pangolin, kuzozuzisa ukubona ukuthi kungaphansi kwaziphi izimo amalulwane nama-pangolin engakwazi ukwabelana ngokufana kwendawo ezungezile.
Okwesibili, uma amalulwane edlala indima eqonde kakhulu ekuthelelekeni kwabantu, kufanele kutholwe ukuthi abantu baxhumana kanjani namalulwane.
Okwesithathu, uma isilwane esincelisayo sisebenza njengombungazi wangempela omaphakathi, indlela esisebenzelana ngayo nezidalwa ezihlukahlukene okuhlanganisa abantu, amalulwane nama-pangolin kufanele icaciswe.
Okokugcina, njengoba izilwane eziningi ezincelisayo kuhlanganise nezilwane ezifuywayo zingase zichayeke ku-SARS-CoV-2, kokubili ukugadwa nokutheleleka kokucwaninga kufanele kwenziwe.
Uma kungase kube ilulwane, i-pangolin noma esinye isilwane esincelisayo, kulindelwe ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 noma amagciwane ayo angumzali acishe afane azotholwa kumbungazi wawo ongokwemvelo esikhathini esizayo.
Ukucwaningwa okuqhubekayo kule ndawo kuzochaza umzila wokuziphendukela kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ezilwaneni, nemiphumela ebalulekile ekuvinjweni naskulawulweni kwe-COVID-19 kubantu.
Ukubuyekezwa kombandela wokuxilongwa kwalabo “abasolwa” futhi “abaqinisekisiwe” ukuthi baphethwe i-COVID-19 kuyadinga
Ngo-6 February 2020, ithimba lethu lalishicilele umhlahlandlela weseluleko esisheshayo sokuxilongwa nokwelashwa kokutheleleka kwe-coronavirus entsha ka-2019 (2019-nCoV), futhi lo mhlahlandlela wanikeza okuhlangenwe nakho kwethu kanye nokwenza ireferensi efanele yokulwa lolu bhubhane lomhlaba wonke.
Nokho, isifo se-coronavirus sika-2019 (I-COVID-19) isifo esisha, ukuqapha nokuqonda kwethu kuyanyuka ngokusekelwe kucwaningo oluqhubekayo nokuhlangenwe nakho kwezinqubo zokwelashwa; yingakho, amasu okuxilongwa nokwelashwa eqhubeka ebuyekezwa njalo.
Kule ncwadi, siphendule ukuphawula okukodwa okumayelana nomhlahlandlela wethu futhi sanikeza umbandela wokuhlonzwa omusha walabo “abasolwa” futhi “okuqinisekisiwe” ukuthi bayagula ngokuvumelana ne-Diagnosis and Treatment Guidelines for COVID-19 (uhlelo lwesikhombisa) olukhishwa yi-National Health Committee of the People’s Republic of China.
Ngo-December 2019, i-coronavirus entsha ka-2019 (2019-nCoV) yayibangele ukubheduka, manje okubizwa ngokusemthethweni ngokuthi i-coronavirus disease 2019 (I-COVID-19) futhi igciwane liqanjwe ngokuthi i-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ngo-11 March 2020, i-WHO yabhekisela ku-COVID-19 njengobhubhane.
Ukuze kuliwe nokutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV-2, ithimba lethu lisungule umhlahlandlela wokusabela okusheshayo futhi ushicilelwe ku-inthanethi ku-Military Medical Research ngo-06 February 2020.
Ithole ukunakwa okukhulu kusukela yashicilelwa.
Qaphela nokho ukuthi i-COVID-19 iyisifo esisha, ukuqapha kanye nolwazi ngayo luya ngokuya lwanda ngokusekelwe kulokho okutholwa kucwaningo kanye nokuhlangenwe nakho kwezokwelashwa; yingakho, amasu okuxilongwa nokwelashwa eqhubeka ebuyekezwa.
Ngokwesibonelo i-Diagnosis and Treatment Guidelines for COVID-19 eyakhishwa yi-National Health Committee of the People’s Republic of China (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), phakathi kuka-16 January 2020 kuya ku-3 March 2020, iye yakhipha imiqulu eyisikhombisa lapho ezinye izinto zishintshwe ngokuphawulekayo.
Umhlahlandlela wethu wathola ukuphawula okuvela ku-Zhou et al., bethula isiphakamiso esilula samaphuzu ngokusekelwe kokuhlangenwe nakho kwabo.
Umsebenzi wabo wengeza ubufakazi obusha womhlahlandlela wethu futhi wenza ukubhekisela okubalulekile kwalolu bhubhane emhlabeni kabanzi.
Siyawutusa umsebenzi wabo obalulekile futhi sidlulisa ukubonga kwethu.
Nokho, umebenzi wabo udinga ukubuyekezwa ngokuvumelana ne-Diagnosis and Treatment Guidelines for COVID-19 (Uhlelo lwesikhombisa locwaningo) yakamuva nezingcwaningo zakamuva.
Ngokohlelo lwesikhombisa (3 March 2020), ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukugulwa okusolwayo kudingeka ukuthi kuhlangniswe noma iyiphi into eyodwa yezici zomlando we-epidemiological nezinto ezimbili zokuboniswa kwezokwelshwa ukuze kwenziwe ukuhlaziywa okubanzi, noma idinga ukuhlangabezana nezinto ezintathu zokuboniswa kwezokwelashwa ezingenawo umlando ocacile we-epidemiological:
Umlando we-epidemiological: (1) umlando wokuvakashela noma wokuhlala edolobheni lase-Wuhan nezindawo ezizungezile, noma eminye imiphakathi lapho okubikwe khona ukugula kwe-COVID-19 ezinsukwini ezingu-14 ezidlule ngaphambi kokuqala kwezimpawu; (2) umlando wokuxhumana nabantu abatheleleke nge-SARS-CoV-2 (ngokuhlola kwe-nucleic acid okuphozithivu); (3) umlando wokuxhumana neziguli eziphethwe imfiva noma izimpawu zokuphefumula edolobheni lase-Wuhan nezindawo ezizungezile, noma eminye imiphakathi lapho kubikwe khona i-COVID-19 ezinsukwini ezingu-14 ngaphambi kokuqala kwezimpawu; (4) umlando wokuhlangana neziguli eziningi eziqinisekisiwe (iziguli ≥ ezingu-2 ezinemfiva kanye/noma izimpawu zokuphefumula ezivele phakathi namaviki angu-2 ezindaweni ezincane, njengasekhaya, ehhovisi, ekilasini lasesikoleni, njll).
Ukubonakala kwezokwelashwa: (1) imfiva kanye/ noma izimpawu zokuphefumula; (2) ezinezici zomfanekiso wokutheleleka kwe-COVID-19; (3) ingqikithi yesibalo samaseli egazi amhlophe abonisa isibalo se-lymphocyte esivamile, esehlile, noma esinciphile esigabeni sokuqala.
Ukuxilongwa kokugula okuqinisekisiwe kufanele kusekelwe ekuguleni okusolwayo okunento eyodwa yobufakazi obulandelayo be-pathogenic noma be-serological: (1) ukuhlola okuphozithivu kwe-PCR yesikhathi sangempela se-SARS-CoV-2; (2) ukulandelana kwe-genome ephelele yegciwane okubonisa i-homogeneity ephakeme kumagciwane aziwayo e-coronavirus entsha; (3) ukuba phozithivu ngokuba nesivikeli-mzimba esiqondile se-IgM kanye nesivikeli-mzimba se-IgG ye-SARS-CoV-2 ekuhloleni kwe-serum; noma ushintsho lwesivikeli-mzimba esiqondile se-IgG ye-SARS-CoV-2 esisuka kuphozithivu siye kunegethivu, noma i-titer ekhula izikhathi ezingu-≥4 esigabeni sokululama esingaphezu kwaleso sesigaba esibucayi.
Siyabona ukuthi ukuhlola kwesikhathi sangempela kwe-PCR ye-nucleic acid kumgudu wokuphefumula noma kumasampula egazi sengezwe ezinhlelweni zesibili (18 January 2020) nezesithathu (22 January 2020).
Ukutholwa oku-pathogenic kwesampula legazi kwengezwe ezinhlelweni zesine (27 January 2020) nezesihlanu (8 February 2020); futhi ubufakazi be-serological bufakwe ohlelweni lwesikhombisa.
Lezi zinguquko ezisekelwe kumsebenzi oqhubekayo wabacwaningi wokucinga ikhithi yokutholwa kwe-nucleic acid ephakeme yokuxilongwa okusheshayo, kanye namasampula omgudu wokuphefumula okuhlanganisa isampula legazi, okunyuse ukutholakala kwezicubu ezihlukene, futhi kwasekela ukulethwa komphumela ophozithivu wesivikeli-mzimba esithile kumbandela oqinisekisiwe.
Ngaphandle kwalokho, kukhona ubufakazi obengeziwe obusikhumbuza ukuthi siqaphe ngeziguli ezinezimpawu ezingavamile nalezo ezingenazo izimpawu.
Yingakho, ishadi lokugeleza le-Zhou et al. kufanele libuyekezwe, njengoba libhekisela kumuntu ongenazo izimpawu zokwelashwa “njengosengozini ephansi”.
Inqubo yamaphuzu nayo idinga ukuqinisekiswa emsebenzini nasezifundweni zokwelapha eziqhubekahyo.
Ekuphetheni, sithemba ukuthi kunobufakazi obengeziwe obuzayo futhi sicela ukuthi abafundi baphawule.
Ukuze kwenziwe ukuxilongwa “kokugula okusolwayo” kanye “nokugula okuqinisekisiwe”, situsa ukuthi kulandelelwe futhi kulalelwe imihlahlandlela emisha yamazwe ekhaya labo.
Ithimba lethu lizophinde futhi libuyekeze umhlahlandlela wethu ukuze sinikeze usizo.
I-Bangladesh ibike ukufa okusha okuyisihlanu okubangelwe i-COVID-19, inani eliphakeme kakhulu losuku
Izolo, i-Bangladesh iqinisekise ukufa okusha okuyisihlanu okubangelwe i-COVID-19 ngalolo suku.
Leli inani eliphakeme kunawo wonke losuku elibangelwe igciwane.
Kusukela izolo, i-Bangladesh's Institute of Epidemiology, i-Disease Control and Research (IEDCR) ibike ukuthi inani elibikiwe labantu abagulayo lingu-114 kanye nabangu-33 abaluleme abahlezi ekhaya.
Kurekhodwe ingqikithi yabantu abangu-17 abafile.
Esithangameni sezindaba ze-inthanethi, umqondisi we-IEDCR, uDkt. Meerjady Sabrina Flora, uthe abantu abashonile bahlanganisa abantu besilisa abane kanye nowesifazane oyedwa.
Ngokusho kukaDkt. Meerjady, ababili bebeneminyaka engaphezu kuka-60, ababili bebephakathi kuka-51 no-60, futhi oyedwa ubephakathi kuka-41-50.
Uphinde wathi ababili bebeqhamuka e-Dhaka.
I-World Health Organization (WHO) imemezele ukuthi i-COVID-19 iwubhubhane ngo-March 11.
Isikhulu sasesibhedlela sitshele i-Anadolu Agency, umthombo wezindaba wasendaweni, ukuthi omunye wabashonile bekungu-Jalal Saifur Rahman, umqondisi we-Bengali Anti-Corruption Commission, owanakekelwa e-Kuwait Maitree Hospital.
NgoMgqibelo, kusimemezelo sevidiyo ye-inthanethi, Ungqongqoshe wase-Bangladesh Wezokuthutha Zomgwaqo u-Obaidul Quader uthe ezokuthutha zomphakathi zizovalwa isikhathi eside kunaleso esihleliwe, kuze kube yilo Mgqibelo ozayo.
Lokhu kuvalwa kwezithuthi zomphakathi kwakuqale ngo-March 26 futhi bekuhlelwe ukuthi kuzophela ngoMgqibelo, April 4.
Ukuthuthwa kwezimpahla ezibalulekile -- ezokwelashwa, uphethiloli nokudla -- kusavunyelwe.
Izigameko zokuqala ezirekhodiwe zesifo se-COVID-19 e-Bangladesh zaba ngo-March 8, kubantu ababili ababuya bevela e-Italy kanye nonkosikazi womunye wabo.
Ngo-March 19, laba abathathu basebeluleme kakade.
Inani labaphethwe i-SARS-CoV-2 lidlula isigidi esisodwa emhlabeni jikelele
NgoLwesine, ingqikithi yenani labantu abaphethwe i-SARS-CoV-2 coronavirus ladlula isigidi esisodwa emhlabeni jikelele, ngokusho kwedatha ye-Johns Hopkins University.
Okungenani ukufa okuyizinkulungwane ezingu-52 kwahlotshaniswa ne-COVID-19, ukugula okubangelwa i-coronavirus.
Lokhu kwenzeke ngosuku olufanayo lapho i-Malawi iqinisekise ukugula kwayo kokuqala okubangelwe i-coronavirus futhi i-Zambia ibe nokufa kwayo kokuqala okuhlobene ne-coronavirus.
I-North Korea ithe, kusukela ngoLwesine, ingelinye lamazwe ambalwa angenaso isifo se-coronavirus.
Ngayizolo, i-World Health Organization ifake umbiko wokugula okuqinisekisiwe okungu-1,051,635, okuhlanganisa ukugula okungu-79,332 emahoreni angamashumi amabili nane angaphambi kuka-10 a.m. ngokwe-Central European Europe (0800 UTC) ngo-April 4.
E-United States, kurekhodwe ukugula okubangelwa i-coronavirus okungaphezu kwezinkulungwane ezingu-244, okuhlobene nokufa okucishe kube ngu-5,900.
I-CBS News ibike, icaphuna idatha ye-Johns Hopkins University, ukuthi kube khona ukufa okungaphezu kuka-1,000 e-US ngoLwesithathu okubangelwe ukutheleleka kwe-coronavirus.
Emhlabeni jikelele, amazwe amemezele izinyathelo eziqinile zokuvimbela ukubhebhetheka kwesifo.
NgoLwesine, u-Sergei Sobyanin, usodolobha wase-Moscow, unwebe ukuvalwa thaqa kwedolobha kuze kube u-May 1.
Ezweni kabanzi, Umongameli u-Vladimir Putin umemezele ukuthi abantu base-Russia bazoqhubeka beholelwa ngaphandle kokuya emsebenzini kuze kube u-April 30.
Iphalamende lase-Portugal livotele ukunweba isimo esiphuthumayo sikazwelonke ngezinsuku ezingu-15; ivoti liphasiswe amavoti angu-215 abantu abavumile, abayishumi abavotanga, futhi oyedwa ubenevoti elimelene nalokhu.
I-Saudi Arabia inwebe isikhathi sokubuya ekhaya sasemadolobheni angcwele ase-Mecca nase-Medina ukuze siqhubeke usuku lonke; ngaphambilini, isikhathi sokubuyela ekhaya besiphakathi kuka-3 p.m. no-6 a.m.
I-Thailand ihlela ukusebenzisa isikhathi sokubuyela ekhaya esiphakathi kuka-10 p.m. no-4 a.m.
Umbusi wase-Ohio, u-Mike DeWine, umemezele ukuthi isifundazwe silule umthetho waso wokuhlala ekhaya kuze kube u-May 1.
Izitolo e-Australia zinciphise imikhawulo yokuthenga iphepha lasendlini encane ekuthengeni ngakunye
NgeSonto nangoMgqibelo kusihlwa, inxanxathela yezitolo zase-Australia u-Woolworths no-Coles unciphise umkhawulo waso wokuthengwa kwephepha lendlu yangasese ukuze umuntu athenge amabili kanye nephakethe elilodwa ekuthengeni ngakunye esitolo ezweni lonke, ngokulandelana.
U-ALDI uphinde wethula umkhawulo wephakethe elilodwa, ngoMsombuluko.
Le mikhawulo iphostwe njengemiyalezo ekuphumeni, nasemakhasini e-Facebook alesi sitolo.
Abathengi bebeqhubeka bewathenga inqwaba yawo ngenxa yokwesaba i-COVID-19 uma kwenzeka kudingeka ukuthi bazihlukanise.
NgoLwesithathu, u-Woolworths uphinde wakhawula ukuthengwa kwephepha lendlu yangasese kulabo abalethelwa ekhaya ukuze kube iphekhi eyodwa nge-oda ngalinye.
Lezi zinguquko zilandela ezangaphambilini zomkhawulo wamaphekhi amane ekuthengeni ngakunye owethulwe u-Woolworths no-Coles ngo-March 4 no-5.
"U-Coles, kusitatimende sayo sezindaba sango-March 8, yabika ukuthi ngomkhawulo wamaphekhi amane obekiwe, ""izitolo eziningi zisaphelelwa impahla cishe ngemva kwehora lokulethwa kwayo"", futhi ibize isidingo ""esingenakuqhathaniswa"", kuyilapho u-ALDI, kuphosti yayo ye-Facebook ngoLwesibili, ithe ""okungalindelekile""."
"Ukudayiswa ""kunyuke kakhulu"" ngeviki elidlule, ngokusho komkhulumeli wakwa-Woolworths."
Isitolo sakwa-Costco e-Canberra naso siphinde sakhawula inani elivunyelwe ukuze libe amaphekhi amabili ngeviki elidlule.
Ukuze kubhekwane nokushoda, u-Coles u-ode amaphakheji amakhulu kakhulu kubahlinzeki futhi wamemezela nokwanda kokudilivwa, u-Woolworths u-ode isitokwe esengeziwe, kuyilapho u-ALDI enze izitokwe zesipesheli esihleliwe sangoLwesithathu ukuthi sitholakale ngokushesha.
U-Russell Zimmerman, umqondisi ophezulu we-Australian Retailers Association, uthe abadayisi bayazama ukunyusa isitokwe, kodwa imikhawulo yomkhandlu wendawo ephathelene nesikhathi sokudiliva kwamaloli kwenza izinto zibe nzima.
Ulindele ukuthi izindleko zokukhiqiza zinyuke, njengoba abahlinzeki bezama ukuhlangabezana nesidingo, nezipesheli ezimbalwa.
NgoLwesibili, u-ALDI wamemezela ukuthi ngenxa yokukhululwa ngokushesha kwesitokwe, ezinye izitolo azikwazi ukuqhubeka nesipesheli sangoLwesithathu.
Kumbiko we-News.com.au, uDkt. Gary Mortimer, uchwepheshe wezokudayisa wase-Queensland University of Technology, uthe izitolo zigcwalisa isitokwe njalo ngobusuku.
Uphawule wathi iphepha lasendlini encane liyinto enesisindo, okuholela ekutheni kube nenani eliphansi lezitokwe uma kuziwa ngokwezinombolo, futhi, uma seliphelile, lishiya isikhala esikhulu sivulekile, okuqinisa umuzwa wokuthi liyanquleka.
U-Coles no-Woolworths banombono [othi] uma bekukhona izinto eziningi kumashalofu, uma umkhiqizo ofana namaroli ephepha lasendlini encane kanye nesanithayiza kungase [kuthengwe] futhi kukhona ngobuningi, cishe unganciphisa uvalo kusho u-Russell Zimmerman ngokwe-ABC News.
