I-World Health Organization ibiza i-COVID-19 ngobhubhane
Ngolwesithathu, i-World Health Organization (WHO) ibize uqubuko oluqhubekayo lwe-COVID-19 — isifo esibangelwa i-coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 — ubhubhane.
"Yize igama elithi ""ubhubhane"" lubhekisela ezingeni isifo esisaphazeke ngayo, hhayi endleleni izibonelo eziqondile eziyingozi ngayo, u-WHO ubonise ukunakekela isidingo sokuqhuba ohulumeni ekuthatheni isinyathelo:"
Wonke amazwe asangakwazi ukushintsha inqubo yalo bhubhane.
Uma amazwe ephenya, ehlola, elapha, ehlukanisa, elandelela futhi esabela ngokulawula iminyakazo yabantu, kusho u-Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Umqondisi-Ophethe we-WHO.
Sikhathazeke kakhulu ngakho kokubili ukusabalala okusemazingeni athusayo nanzima kanye nokuntuleka komnyakazo okusemazingeni athusayo.
"Ngokusho kuka-Dr. Tom Frieden, obengumqondisi odlule we-United States' Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, ubhubhane ""alunasiqhathaniso sangaphambili."""
"Wathi, ngokuphawula okumenyezelwe ku-CNN ngo-February, ""ngaphandle kwemfuluwenza, alikho elinye igciwane lokuphefumula elilandelelwe kusukela livela kuze kube yilapho libhebhetheka umhlaba wonke."""
"U-Ghebreyesus uveze umbono ofanayo, ethi ""asikaze sibone ngaphambili ubhubhane olususwe inhlansi ye-coronavirus."""
"Uqhubekile, ""futhi askikaze ngaphambili sibone ubhubhane olungalawuleka ngesikhathi esifanayo."""
Isimo esisha sobhubhane silandela isinqumo sika-WHO's sango-January sokubiza uqubuko njengenkathazo yomhlaba wonke yesimo esiphuthumayo sempilo yomphakathi.
"Umqondisi we-United States' National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Disease's, u-Dr. Anthony Fauci, uthe ngokuqubuka, ""okusalayo, kusazoba kubi nakakhulu."""
Kusukela Ngolwesine, i-Associated Press ibike ukuthi kube nezibonelo okungenani ezingu-126,000 ze-COVID-19 umhlaba wonke, okuholele ngaphezu kuka-4,600 wabafile.
Ubhubhane lwe-2019–20 coronavirus lingubhubhane oluqhubekayo lwesifo se-coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), olubangelwa i-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ukuqubuka kwakhonjwa e-Wuhan, China, ngo-December 2019, kwameyezelwa ngokuthi Isimo Esiphuthumayo Sempilo Yomphakathi Emazweni Onke Esikhathazayo ngo-30 January 2020, futhi sabhekwa njengobhubhane ngo-11 March 2020.
Kusukela ngo-10 April 2020, izibonelo ezinembile eziyizigidi ezingu 1.61 ze-COVID-19 ziye zabikwa emazweni nemingcele angu-210, okuholela kwabangu-97,000 abafile ngokuqiniseka.
Abantu abangaba ngu-364,000 balulamile.
Inani lezibonelo zokubhubha liye lalinganiselwa ku-4% e-China, ngesikhathi esifanayo ezembulunga zisuka ku-13.04% e-Algeria kuye ku-.08% e-New Zealand.
Izimpawu ezivamile zihlanganisa ukushisa, ukukhwehlela nokuphelelwa umoya.
Izinkinga zingase zihlanganise i-pneumonia ne-acute respiratory distress syndrome.
Isikhathi sokuchayeka kuya kwesibonisa izimpawu ngokuvamile siba ezinsukwini ezinhlanu, kodwa kungadonsa kusuka kwezimbili kuye kweziyishumi nane.
Alikho ikhambi elaziwayo noma inqubo yokwelapha enganqoba igciwane.
Indlela yokwelapha emqoka ebheka izimpawu nokunakekela okusizayo. Izindlela zokuvikela eziphakanyisiwe zihlanganisa ukuhlanza izandla, ukumboza umlomo lapho ukhwehlela, ukugcina ibanga phakathi kwakho nabanye, nokuqapha nokuzihlukanisa kubantu abasola ukuthi kungenzeka bathelelekile.
Amagunya emhlabeni wonke sebesabele ngokubeka imingcele kwezokuhamba, ukuhlukaniswa, izikhathi zokunyakaza, izinyathelo ezilawula ubungozi ezindaweni zokusebenza, nokuvalwa kwezindawo.
Lolu bhubhane seluholele ekuphazamisekeni okunzima komnotho nenhlalo emhlabeni wonke, ukuhlehliswa noma ukukhanselwa kwezemidlalo, ezenkolo, ezombangazwe nezenzakalo zamasiko, kanye nokuntuleka okusabalele kwezinto eziyisidingo eziqedwe ukuthenga ngamawala.
Izikole kuhlanganise amavasithi zivaliwe izwe lonke noma emazweni angu 193, okuthinta amaphesenti angu-99.4 ngokunembile weningi labafundi umhlaba wonke.
Ulwazi oluyiphutha mayelana negciwane sekusabalele ku-inthanethi, futhi sekube khona nezimo zikucwasa ngobuzwe nokubandlululwa kwabantu base-China, nabanye abantu abavela Empumalanga nabozalo nokubukeka kwasemazweni Enyakatho ye-Asia, nabanye abavela ezindawe ezinezibonelo eziningi zegciwane.
Ngenxa kokuncishiswa kwezinga kwezokuhamba nokuvalwa kwezimboni ezinkulu, kube khona ukuncipha ekungcolisweni komoya nama-carbon emissions.
Amagunya kwezempilo e-Wuhan, China (inhloko-dolobha yesifunda sase-Hubei) ibike uxhaxha lwezibonelo zenyumoniya ezinomsuka ongaziwa ngo-31 December 2019, kanti uphenyo lwavulwa ekuqaleni kuka-January 2020.
Izibonelo eziningi bezihlobene ne-Huanan Seafood Wholesale Market ngakho igciwane licabangelwa ukuba nomsuka ovela ngokuthathelwa esilwaneni.
Igciwane elibangele ukuqubuka laziwa ngokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2, igciwane eliqalayo ukuvela elihlobene eduze nama-coronaviruses elulwane, ama-coronaviruses e-pangolin, ne-SARS-CoV. Umuntu wokuqala owaziwayo owakhombisa izimpawu kwatholakala kamuva ukuthi waqala ukugula ngo-1 December 2019, futhi lowo muntu akazange neze abe nokuhlobana okusobala noxhaxha lwe-wet market.
Kuxhaxha lokuqala lwezibonelo ezabikwa ngo-December 2019, Izingxenye ezintathu zatholakala zixhuma emakethe.
Ngomhlaka-13 March 2020, umbiko ongaqinisekisiwe ovela ku-South China Morning Post waphakamisa ukuthi isibonelo esilandelela emuva ku-17 November 2019, somuntu weminyaka engu-55 ubudala wesifundazwe sase-Hubei, singase sibe esokuqala. Ngomhlaka-26 February 2020, i-WHO yabika ukuthi, njengoba izibonelo ezintsha zibikwa zincipha e-China kodwa zikhula ngamawala e-Italy, e-Iran, nase-South Korea, isibalo sezibonelo ezintsha ezingaphandle kwe-China bese zisedlulile isibalo sezibonelo ezintsha zase-China okokuqala.
Kungenzeka kube nokubika ngaphansi kwezibonelo, ikakhulukazi phakathi kwalabo abanezimpawu ezisivivi.
Ngo-26 February, izibonelo ezincane zase zibikiwe phakathi kwentsha, labo abono-19 nangaphansi bakha u-2.4% wezibonelo umhlaba wonke. Umeluleki oyinhloko wesayensi wase-United Kingdom's, u-Patrick Vallance, walinginasela u-60% womphakathi wase-British uzodinga ukutheleleka ukuze i-effective herd immunity izofinyeleleka.
Izibonelo zibhekisela esibalweni sabantu abahlolelwe i-COVID-19, futhi ukuhlolwa kwabo okuqinisekisa ukuqinisekiswa ngokuhambelana nenqubo yomthetho.
Kusukela ngo-23 March, alikho izwe ebeselihlole ngaphezulu kuka-3% wenani labantu balo, futhi amazwe amaningi ayenemithetho egwema ukuhlolwa kwalabo abanezimpawu ezisivivi nje, njenge-Italy, i-Netherlands, i-Spain, ne-Switzerland.
Ucwaningo olwanyatheliswa ngo-16 March lwathola ukuthi e-China, kuze kube ngu-23 January, isilinganiso esingu-86% sokuthelelana nge-COVID-19 sasingakatholakali, futhi lokhu kuthelelana okungabhaliwe phansi yikona okungumthombo ka-79% wezibonelo ezibhalwe phansi zesifo.
Ukuhlaziya kwezibalo okwanyatheliswa ngo-30 March kwalinganisela ukuthi izinombolo zokutheleleka e-Italy ziphakeme kakhulu kunezibonelo ezibikiwe.
Ukulinganisela kokuqala kwesibalo esilula sokuzala (R0) se-COVID-19 besiku-1.4 kuye ku-2.4.
Ucwaningo olunyatheliswe i-US Center for Disease Control and Prevention luphethe ngokuthi kungase kube ngu-5.7.
Amantu abaningi abane-COVID-19 bayalulama.
Labo abangalulami, isikhathi kusukela ekwakhekeni kwezimpawu kuye ekufeni siphakathi kwezinsuku ezingu-6 nezingu-41, ezivame kakhulu kube izinsuku ezingu-14.
Kusukela ngo-10 April 2020, okungenani ukufa kwabangu-97,000 kwabekwa njengesizathu se-COVID-19.
E-China, kusukela ngo-5 February cishe u-80% wabafile waba yilabo abangaphezulu kuka-60, futhi u-75% uvele unezinkinga ezingokwempilo ezikhona kakade ezihlanganisa izifo zenhliziyo noshukela. Izibalo ezisemthethweni zokufa ngobhubhane lwe-COVID-19 ngokujwayelekile kubhekisela kubantu abafile abahlolwa baqinisekiselwa i-COVID ngokusho kwenqubo yomthetho.
Isibalo sabafile esiyiqiniso se-COVID-19 kungenzeka sikhulu kakhulu, njengoba singahlanganisi wonke umuntu ofa ngaphandle kokuhlola - isib. ekhaya, ekhaya labadala, etc.
Idatha eyingxenye evela e-Italy yathola ukuthi isibalo sokufa okweqile phakathi nobhubhane yeqa izibalo ezisemthethweni zokufa ngenxa ye-COVID ngo-4-5x.
"Ongumkhulumeli we-U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) wavuma ""Siyazi ukuthi[isibalo esikhishiwe sokufa] singaphansi ngokulinganisa"", inkulumo ehambelana nemibiko ye-anecdotal yokubala ngaphansi e-U.S. Ukulinganisa ngaphansi okunjalo kuvamile ukwenzeka uma kunobhubhane, njengomshayabhuqe we-H1N1 swine flu ngo-2009. Ukufa okuqala okwaqinisekiswa kwaba e-Wuhan ngo-9 January 2020."
Ukufa kokuqala okwenzeka ngaphandle kwezwe lase-China uqobo kwenzeka ngo-1 February e-Philippines, futhi ukufa kokuqala okwenzeka ngaphandle kwase-Asia kwenzeka e-France ngo-14 February.
Ngo-28 February, ngaphandle kwezwe lase-China uqobo, ukufa kwabangaphezu kweshumi nambili kwaqoshwa e-Iran, e-South Korea, nase-Italy.
Ngo-13 March, amazwe nezindawo ezingaphezulu kwamashumi amane ayesebike ukufa, kuwowonke amazwekazi ngaphandle kwe-Antarctica. Kunezinyathelo eziningana ngokuvamile ezisebenziselwa ukubala izinga lokufa.
Lezi zinombolo ziyahluka ngendawo nangaphezu kwesikathi, futhi zithonywa ubukhulu bokuhlola, isimo senqubo sokunakekela kwezezempilo, izinhlobo zokulashwa, isikhathi kusukela kuqale ukuqubuka, nezici zomphakathi njengobudala, ubulili, nempilo iyonke. I-death-to-case ratio ibonisa isibalo sabafile ubahlukanise ngenombolo yezibonelo ezihloliwe phakathi negebe elithile lenkathi.
Ngokusekela ngezibalo ze-Johns Hopkins University, i-global death-to-case ratio ngu-6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) kusukela ngo-10 April 2020.
Isibalo siyahluka ngendawo.
E-China, ukulinganisa kwe-death-to-case ratio kwehla kusuka ku-17.3% (kulabo abanezimpawu ezavela ngo-1–10 January 2020) kuye ku-0.7% (kulabo abanezimpawu ezavela ngo-1 February 2020). Ezinye izinyathelo zihlanganisa i-case fatality rate (CFR), yona ebonisa iphesenti yabantu abahloliwe abafayo ngenxa yesifo, ne-infection fatality rate (IFR), yona ebonisa iphesenti yabathelelekile (abahloliwe nabangahloliwe) abafayo ngenxa yesifo.
Lezi zibalo azincikile esikhathini futhi zilandela inani labantu abathile kusuka ekuthelelekeni ngesixazululo sesibonelo.
Inqwaba yezifundiswa ike yazama ukubala lezizinombolo zamanani abantu athile.
I-University of Oxford's Centre for Evidence-Based Medicine ilinganisela ukuthi i-infection fatality rate yobhubhane selulonke iphakathi kuka-0.1% no-0.39%.
Ukulinganisa okuphakeme kwaleli banga kuyahambisana nemiphumela evela ekuhloleni okungahleliwe kwe-COVID-19 e-Germany, futhi ucwaningo lwezibalo ezihlaziya imiphumela yokuhlola okulinganiselwa yi-CFR.
I-WHO iyagomela ukuthi ubhubhane lungalawuleka.
Iqophelo nobude bangempela bokuqubuka akuqinisekisi futhi kungahluka ngendawo.
"U-Maciej Boni we-Penn State University wathi, ""Uma eyekwa engabhekiwe, ukuqubuka okuthelelanayo kuyadamba sdalwa bese kuqala ukuncipha lapho isifo siphelelwa abagcini esingabathola."
"Kodwa kucishe kube okungenakwenzeka ukwenza ukuqagela okusile njengamanje mayelana nokuthi lokho kuzoba nini""."
"Umeluleki omkhulu wezokwelapha kahulumeni wase-China u-Zhong Nanshan wathi ""kungenzeka kube skuphelile ngo-June"" uma wonke amazwe engenza umnyakazo wokulandela izinyathelo ze-advn ye-WHO yokuvimba ukusabalala kwegciwane."
"Ngo-17 March, u-Adam Kucharski we-London School of Hygiene & Tropical Medicine wakhuluma wathi i-SARS-CoV-2 ""izohamba izungeza, ngokunamandla unyaka owodwa noma emibili""."
"Ngokusho kocwaningo lwe-Imperial College eholwa ngu-Neil Ferguson, ukuzihlukanisa ngokomzimba nezinye izinyathelo kuzodingeka ""kuze kube yilapho ikhambi litholakala (ngokuhlambisela izinyanga ezingu-18 noma ezengeziwe)""."
"U-William Schaffner we-Vanderbilt University wathi, ""Ngicabanga ukuthi akunakwenzeka ukuthi le-coronavirus—ngoba idluliselana kalula—izonyamalala unomphela"" ingase futhi ""iphenduke isifo sezinkathi zonyaka, izibuyele njalo ngonyaka""."
Indluzula yokubuya iyoncika ekuvikelekeni okuqinile komhlambi nezinga lokuzishintsha
Izimpawu ze-COVID-19 zingaba ezingaqondile kokunye futhi abantu abathelelekile bangase bangabi nezimpawu.
Izimpawu ezivame kakhulu ezimbili ukushisa (88%) nokukhwehlela okomile (68%).
Izimpawu ezivame kancane zihlanganisa ukukhathala, ukwakheka kwamathe namafinyila esifubeni (phlegm), ukuphelelwa inzwa yokunuka, ukuphelelwa umoya, ubuhlungu bomsipha namalunga, umphimbo obuhlungu, ukunkenketha kwekhanda, amakhaza, ukuhlanza, i-hemoptysis, uhudo, noma i-cyanosis. I-WHO ithe ngokungageji umuntu oyedwa kwabayisithupha ugula kakhulu futhi abe nenkinga yokuphefumula.
I-U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) inohlu olubonisa izimpawu zesimo esiphuthumayo njengobunzima lapho uphefumula, ubuhlungu obuphikelelayo esifubeni noma ukucindezeleka, ukudunyelwa esithubeni, ubunzima uma uvuka, nobuso obuhlaza noma izindebe; ukunakekela okusheshayo kwezokwelapha kuyakhuthazwa uma lezi zimpawu zikhona. Ukuthuthuka kwesifo kulokhu kungaholela kusifo senyumoniya enzima, i-acute respiratory distress syndrome, i-sepsis, i-septic shock nokufa.
Abanye balabo abathelelekile bangase bangabi nazo izimpawu, bangabi nezimpawu zokwelapha kodwa imiphumela yabo yokuhlola iqinisekisa ukutheleleka, ngakho abacwaningi sebekhiphe iseluleko sokuthi labo ababe nokuthintana okuseduze nalabo abaqinisekisiwe kumelwe baqaphwe eduze futhi bazilongwe ukuze kuqinisekwe unkungabikho kwesifo.
Ukulinganisa kwe-China kwabangenazo izimpawu i-ratio range isuka kwabambalwa kuye ku-44%.
Inkathi evamile yokufudumala (inkathi ephakathi kokutheleleka nokuvela kwezimpawu) kunebanga elisuka kolulodwa kuye kwezingu-14 izinsuku; ngokujwayelekile kuba izinsuku ezinhlanu. Ukwenza isibonelo sokungaqiniseki, ukulinganisa ingxenye yabantu abane-COVID-19 abalahlekelwa inzwa yapho yokunuka ekuqaleni yayingu-30% futhi kamuva yehla yaba ku-15%.
Eminye imininingwane yendlela isifo esisabalala ngayo isadingidwa kwayimanje.
Isifo sikholelwa ukuthi sisabalala ngokuyinhloko phakathi nokuthintana okuseduze nangamaconsi amancane akheka lapho ukhwehlela, uthimula, noma ukhuluma; lapho othintana eduze engaba kumitha elingu-1 kuye ku-2 (u-3 kuye ku-6 amagxathi).
Ucwaningo luthole ukuthi ukukhwehlela okungamboziwe kungaholela amaconsi ukuthi ahambe ibanga elingafika kumamitha angu-4.5 (15 amagxathi) kuye kumamitha angu-8.2 metres (27 amagxathi).
Abanye baphakamise ukuthi igciwane lingase lidluliselwe ngamaconsi amancane ahlala isikhathi esijana emoyeni, angaba khona phakathi nokukhuluma. Amaconsana okuphefumula nawo angase akheke phakathi nokukhipha umoya wokuphefumula, kuhlanganise nalapho ukhuluma, yize ngokuvamile igciwane lingahambi ngomoya.
Amaconsi angahlala emilomeni noma emakhaleni abantu abaseduze noma kwenzeke ahogelwe angene emaphashini.
Ezinye izinqubo zokwelapha njenge-intubation ne-cardiopulmonary resuscitation (CPR) angase abangele ukuchicha kokuphefumula ukuba kufutheke bese umphumela ube ukusaphazeka ngomoya.
Ingase isabalale futhi lapho othile ethinta indawo enegciwane, okuhlanganisa isikhumba, bese ezithinta amehlo, ikhala, noma umlomo.
Noma kukhona ukukhathazeka ukuthi ingase yande ngothuvi, ingozi ikholelwa ukuthi iphansi.
Uhulumeni wase-China uliphikile ithuba lokwenzeka kokuthatheleka kwegciwane le-SARS-CoV-2 ngokuthinta umlomo ngemva kokuthintana nendle. Igciwane linengozi yokuthelelana kakhulu phakathi nezinsuku ezintathu zokuqala nje lapho kuvela izimpawu yize ukusabalala kungenzeka ngaphambi kokuvela kwezimpawu futhi nasezigabeni zokugcina zesifo.
Abantu bahlolwe batholakala benalo igciwane izinsuku ezifika kwezintathu ngaphambi kokuvela kwezimpawu okubonisa ukuthi ukudlulisela kungenzeka ngaphambi kokwakheka kwezimpawu ezimqoka.
Imibiko embalwa kuphela yezibonelo ezingenazo izimpawu eziqinisekiswe elebhu ebonisayo, kodwa ukudluliselana ngaphandle kwezimpawu kuye kwakhonjwa amanye amazwe phakathi nophenyo lokulandelela ukuthintana.
I-European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control (ECDC) ibeka ukuthi yize ingacaci kahle indlela isifo esisabalala kalula ngayo, umuntu oyedwa ngokuvamile uthelela abanye ababili noma abathathu. Igciwane liqhubeka liphila amahora kuya ezinsukwini ngaphezulu kwezinto.
Ngokuqondile, igciwane litholakale litholakala kuze kufike ezinsukwini ezintathu kupulastiki (i-polypropylene) no-304 ku-stainless steel, usuku olulodwa kumakhadibhodi, futhu kuze kube amahora amane ethusini.
Lokhu, kodwa, kuyahluka kuncike esimweni sokufudumala nezinga lokushisa nokubanda. Izilwane zasekhaya nezinye izilwane ziye zakholwa zatholakala ngempela zinayo i-COVID-19.
Abukho ubufakazi bokuthi izilwane zingakwazi ukudlulisela igciwane kubantu, yize amaguya e-British eyala ukuthi umuntu azihlanze izandla ngemuva kokuthinta izilwane, njengoba kunjalo ngemva kokuthinta izindawo abantu abanegciwane okungenzeka bazithintile.
I-Severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) igciwane elisha, elaqala ukuhlukaniswa kubantu abathathu ababenesifo senyumoniya bexhumene noxhaxha lwezibonelo sokugula ngokuphefumula e-Wuhan.
