I-ECDC ne-European regional office le-WHO bakhiphe imihlahlandlela yezibhedlela nabanakekeli bempilo abayinloko ngokugudluza izinsiza ngezigaba ezingafani, okuhlanganisa ukugxilisa imisebenzi yamalebhu ekuhloleni i-COVID-19, ukukhansela izinqubo ezikhethwayo lapho kungenzeka, ukuhlunga nokuhlukanisa iziguli ze-COVID-19 eziqinisekisiwe, nokuphakamisa amandla okunakekela okubucayi ngokuqeqsha izisebenzi nokwandisa isibalo sezisizi zokuphefumula nemibhede.
Kunemibono ehlukene mayelana nokuthi isibonelo sokuqala (obizwa ngesiguli seqanda) savela kuphi.
Isibonelo sokuqala esaziwayo se-coronavirus entsha sibuyela emuva ku-1 December 2019 e-Wuhan, e-Hubei, e-China.
Esikhathini esingaba inyanga, isibalo sezibonelo ze-coronavirus e-Hubei saphakama kancane.
Lezi bezixhumene kakhulu ne-Huanan Seafood Wholesale Market, ephinde idayise izilwane eziphilayo, futhi umbono ukuthi igciwane lavela kwesinye sizinhlobo zalezi zilwane; noma, ngamanye amagama, sinomsuka wokuthathelwa esilwaneni. Uxhaxha lwamanyumoniya lwembagela engaziwa lwabhekwa ngo-26 December futhi lalashwa ngudokotela u-Zhang Jixian e-Hubei Provincial Hospital, owabikela i-Wuhan Jianghan CDC ngo-27 December.
"Ngo-30 December, iqembu lodokotela e-Wuhan Central Hospital laxwayisa abanakwabo nge-""coronavirus efana ne-SARS""."
Odokotela abayisishigalombili, abahlanganisa u-Li Wenliang, bayalwa amaphoyisa ngokusakaza amahlebezi ayiphutha, omunye futhi, u-Ai Fen, wathethiswa abaphathi bakhe ngokuhlaba umkhosi.
I-Wuhan Municipal Health Commission kamuva yakhipha isaziso somphakathi ngo-31 December futhi yabikela ne-WHO.
Izibonelo ezanele zenyumoniya engaziwa zase zibikelwe amagunya ezempilo e-Wuhan ukuthi zingasusa uphenyo ekuqaleni kuka-January. Ezigabeni zokuqala zokuqubuka, isibalo sezibonelo saphindeka okungenani njalo ngemuva kwezinsuku eziyisikhombisa nengxenye.
Ekuqaleni naphakathi kuka-January 2020, igciwane lasabalala laya nakwezinye izifunda zase-China, lisizwa ukuthutha ngenxa Yonyaka Omusha Wase-China nokuthi i-Wuhan iyihabhu yezokuthutha nokushintshana kojantshi abakhulu.
Ngo-20 January, i-China yabika cishe izibonelo ezingu-140 ngosuku olulodwa, okuhlanganisa abantu ababili e-Beijing noyedwa e-Shenzhen.
Kamuva idatha esemthethweni yabonisa ukuthi abantu abangu-6,174 bese bebonisa izimpawu ngo-20 January 2020. Kusukela ngo-26 March, i-United States iyidlulile i-China ne-Italy ngibalo esiphakeme sezibonelo eziqinisekisiwe emhlabeni. Kusukela ngo-9 April 2020, izibonelo ezingaphezu kuka-1.61 wesigidi ziye zabikwa umhlaba wonke; abantu abangaphezulu kuka-97,000 bafile futhi abangaphezulu kuka-364,000 balulamile.
Okungenani amazwe nezindawo ezingu-200 zibe naso okungenani isibonelo esisodwa.
Ngenxa yobhubhane e-Europe, amazwe amaningi endaweni yase-Schengen isibeke umngcele wokunyakaza ngenkululeko futhi aphakamisa ukulwulwa komngcele.
Ukusabela kwesizwe kuhlanganise izinyathelo zokugcinwa njengokuvalelwa (okwaziwa ngokuthi iziqondiso zokuhlala ekhaya, iziqondiso zokukhosela lapho ukhona, noma ukuvala phansi) nezikhathi ezimisiwe. Kusukela ngo 2 April, cishe izigidi ezingu-300 zabantu, noma u-90% wenani labantu, bangaphansi kwendlela ethile yokuvala phansi e-United States, abantu abangaphezulu kwezigidi ezingu-50 zabantu ziphansi kokuvala phansi e-Philippines, okungenani izigidi ezingu-59 zabantu ziphansi kokuvala phansi e-South Africa, futhi izinkulungwane zezigidi ezingu-1.3 zabantu ziphansi kokuvala phansi e-India.
Ngo-26 March, izinkulungwa zezigidi ezingu-1.7 zbantu emhlabeni wonke bebengaphansi kohlobo lokuvala phansi, okube sekukhuphuka kwaba izinkulungwane zezigidi ezingu-2.6 zabantu ezinsukwini ezimbili kamuva—okungaba izingxenye ezintathu zenani labantu bomhlaba.
Isibonelo sokuqala eziqinisekisiwe se-COVID-19 silandelelwe emuva ku-1 December 2019 e-Wuhan; umbiko owodwa ongaqinisekisiwe uphakamisa ukuthi isibonelo sokuqala saba ngo-17 November.
Udokotela u-Zhang Jixian wabheka uxhaxha lwezibonelo zenyumoniya yembangela engaziwa ngo-26 December, khona lapho insibhedlela sakhe sabikela i-Wuhan Jianghan CDC ngo-27 December.
Ukuhlola kokuqala kofuzo kwezibonelo zeziguli ngo-27 December 2019 kwabonisa ukuba khona kwe-coronavirus efana ne-SARS.
Isaziso somphakathi sakhishwa yi-Wuhan Municipal Health Commission ngo-31 December.
I-WHO yabikelwa ngosuku olufanayo.
"Njengoba lezi zaziso zivela, odokotela e-Wuhan baxwayiswa amaphoyisa ""ngokusakaza amahlebezi"" aphathelene nokuqubuka."
"I-Chinese National Health Commission yaqala ngokugomela ukuthi ""abukho ubufakazi"" bokudliliselana komuntu nomuntu."
"Ekuphetheni kuka-January, uhulumeni wase-China waqalisa umkhankaso omkhulu kamuva owachazwa unobhala jikelele we-Chinese Communist Party u-Xi Jinping ngokuthi ""impi yabantu"" yokuvalela ukusaphazeka kwegciwane."
"Kulokho okubizwe ngokuthi ""ukuvalelwa okukhulu emlandweni wesintu"", intambo ngenhlanzeko yamenyezelwa ngo-23 January yokuvala ukungena nokuphuma e-Wuhan, eyandiselwa inani lamadolobha angu-15 cities e-Hubei, okuthinta inani lezigi zabantu ezingu-57."
Ukusebenzisa imoto yakho bekuvinjelwe edolobheni.
Ukugubha Unyaka Omusha e-China (25 January) kwakhanselwa ezindaweni eziningi.
Abasemagunyeni baphinda bamemezela ukwakhiwa kwesibhedlela sesikhashana, i-Huoshenshan Hospital, eyaqedwa ezinsukwini ezingu-10.
Esinye isibhedlela sakhiwa kamuva, i-Leishenshan Hospital, ukuze sinakekele iziguli ezengeziwe.
Ngaphezu kokwakha izibhedlela ezintsha, i-China futhi yaguqula izindawo ezingu-14 e-Wuhan, njengezikhungo zemihlangano nezitediyamu, zaba yizibhedlela zesikhashana. Ngo-26 January, uhulumeni waqalisa ezinye izinyathelo zokuvalela ukuqubuka kwe-COVID-19, okuhlanganisa ukukhipha izimemezelo zezempilo zabahambi nokunweba iholidi Lomkhosi weNtwasahlobo.
Amanyuvesi nezikole ezweni nawo avalwa.
Izifunda zase-Hong Kong ne-Macau zaqalisa izinyathelo ezimbalwa, ikakhulukazi ngokuphathelene nezikole namanyuvesi.
Izinyathelo zokusebenza ukude zaqaliswa ezifundeni ezimbalwa zase-China.
Imikhawulo yokuhamba yamiswa ngaphakathi nangaphandle kwe-Hubei.
Ezokuthutha zomphakathi zathuthukiswa, futhi amanyuziyemu kulo lonke elase-China avalwa isikhashana.
"Ukulawula ukunyakaza komphakathi kwafakwa kumadolobha amaningi, futhi kuqhathaniswe ukuthi okungenani izigidi zabantu ezingu-760 (okungaphezulu kwengxenye yenani labantu) zabhekana nohlobo lomkhawulo wangaphandle. Ngemuva kokuthi ukuqubuka kungene esigabeni sakho sembulunga ngo-March, amagunya ase-China athatha izinyathelo eziqinile zokuvikela igciwane ukuthi ""lingangeni"" livela kwamanye amazwe."
Ngokwesibonelo, i-Beijing ibeke ukuvalewa okuyimpoqo kwezinsuku ezingu-14 kubo bonke abahambi bamazwe abafikayo edolobheni. Ngo-23 March, izwe eliyinhloko e-China bekunesibonelo esisodwa kuphela sokudlulisela ngaphakathi ezinsukwini ezinhlanu ngaphambili, kulesi senzakalo ngomhambi obebuyela e-Guangzhou evela e-Istanbul.
On 24 March 2020, uNdunankulu wase-China u-Li Keqiang wabika ukuthi ukusabalala kwezibonelo ezidluliselene ngaphakathi bekuvinjiwe nokuthi ukuqubuka bekulawuliwe e-China.
Ngosuku olufanayo lokwenziwa lula kwemikhawulo yokuhamba e-Hubei, ngaphandle kwe-Wuhan, izinyanga ezimbili ngemva kokuphoqelelwa kokuvala phansi. I-Chinese Ministry of Foreign Affairs yamemezela ngo-26 March 2020 ukuthi ukungena kwabanama-visa noma abanezimvume zokuhlala kuzomiswa kusukela ngo-28 March kuqhubeke, ngaphandle kwemininingwane eqondile yokuthi lenqubomgomo izophela nini.
Labo abafisa ukungena e-China kuzomele bafake isicelo sama-visas kumahhovisi amanxusa ase-China noma kumahhovisi amanxusa e-China.
Uhulumeni wase-China ukhuthaze amabhizinisi nezimboni ukuthi zivule kabusha ngo-30 March, futhi wahlinzekela izinkampani ngogqozi lwezishuqulu zemali. I-State Council imemezele usuku lokuzila oluqala ngemizuzu emithathu yesikhathi sokuthula ezweni lonke ngo-10:00 4 April, okuqondana ne-Qingming Festival, yize uhulumeni omkhulu ucele imikhaya ukuthi ibonise ukwazisa kwayo nge-inthanethi ukuze kuqaphelwe ukuzihlukanisa ngokomzimba bese kugwenywe ukuqubuka kabusha kwe-COVID-19.
I-COVID-19 yaqinisekiswa ukuthi isisabalale yaya e-South Korea ngo-20 January 2020 ivela e-China.
Abemeleli bezezempilo zezwe babike ukuphakama okuqaphelekayo kwezibonelo eziqinisekisiwe ngo-20 February, okubhekwa ngokuyinhloko njengomphumela wombuthwano wase-Daegu weqembu elisha lenkolo elaziwa ngokuthi i-Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Abazinikele ku-Shincheonji bevakashele e-Daegu bevela e-Wuhan basolwa ngokuba ngabasusi bokuqubuka.
Kusukela ngo-22 February, phakathi kwabalandeli abangu-9,336 besonto, u-1,261 noma okungenani u-13% wabika izimpawu. I-South Korea yamemezela isixwayiso sezinga eliphezulu ngo-23 February 2020.
Ngo-28 February, izibonelo eziqinisekisiwe ezidlule ku-2,000 zabikwa e-Korea, zakhuphuka zafika ku-3,150 ngo-29 February.
Zonke izizinda samasosha e-South Korea ziye zavalwa ngemuva kokuthi ukuhlola kuthole amasosha amathathu enesifo ngokuqinisekisiwe..
Amashejuli okundiza nawo athinteka futhi kanjalo ashintshwa. I-South Korea yethule okubhekwe njengohlelo olukhulu futhi oluhlelwe ngobugcweti emhlabeni lokuthi kubhekwe inani labantu ukuthi alinalo yini igciwane, bese kuhlukaniswa noma ubani othelelekile futhi kulandelelwe bese kuvalelwa labo abathintane nabo.
Izindlela zokubuka zihlanganisa ukuzibika wena okuphoqiwe lapho unezimpawu kulabo abavela emazweni angaphandle ngokusebenzisa ujlelo lukamakhal-ekhukhwini, ukuhlola igciwane ngokudlula ngemoto lapho imiphumela itholakala ngosuku olulandelayo, nokukhuphula ukukwazi ukuhlola okuzovumela abantu abangu-20,000 ukuthi bahlolwe usuku nosuku.
Uhlelo lwe-South Korea lubhekwa njengempumelelo programme ekulawuleni ubhubhane yize kungavalwa ngokuphelele amadolobha. Umphakathi wase-South Korea wawuhlukene ngombono ekuqaleni lapho Umongameli u-Moon Jae-in esabela kule nkinga.
Abantu abaningi baseKorea basayine izincwadi zesicelo sokuba kwenziwe uphenyo ngoMoon ngemva kwezinsolo zokuthi uhulumeni akazange asisingathe kahle isimo lapho kuqubuka igciwane, kanti abanye basayine izincwadi zokumncoma ngezinyathelo azithathile.
Ngomhla ka-23 Mashi, kwabikwa ukuthi inani lababetheleleke ngaleli gciwane eSouth Korea lalehle ukwedlula zonke ezinye izinsuku amasontweni amane.
Ngomhla ka-29 Mashi, kwabikwa ukuthi kusukela ngomhla ka-1 Ephreli wonke umuntu owayefika evela kwelinye izwe wayezogcinwa endaweni ehlukanisiwe nabanye abantu ukuze lingasakazeni igciwane kuze kuphela amasonto amabili.
Ngokwemibiko yabezindaba eyakhishwa ngo-1 Ephreli, iSouth Korea yayithole izicelo ezivela emazweni angu-121 ukuba ilekelele ekuhloleni leli gciwane.
Umbiko wokuqala wezibalo zababetholakale benegciwane le-SARS-CoV-2 e-Iran wakhishwa ngo-19 Febhuwari eQom, okuyilapho ngokombiko weMinistry of Health and Medical Education, kwashonela khona abantu ababili kamuva ngalolo suku.
Izinyathelo zokuqala ezathathwa uhulumeni kwaba ukumiswa kwamakhonsathi neminye imikhosi yokugubha amasiko endawo, ezemidlalo nemithandazo eyenziwa njalo ngoLwesihlanu, ukuvalwa kwamanyuvesi nezikhungo zemfundo ephakeme kanye nezikole.
I-Iran yakhipha imali engama-trillion ayisihlanu ama-rial ukuze ikwazi ukulwisana naleli gciwane.
Ngomhla ka-26 Febhuwari 2020, uMongameli uHassan Rouhani wathi zazingekho izinhleko zokuba izindawo okutholakale kuzo leli gciwane zigcinwe zivaliwe kodwa abantu kuphela ababezohlaliswa ezindaweni ezivikelekile ukuze bangalisakazi igciwane kwabanye.
Izinhlelo zokunciphisa ukuhamba kwabantu besuka kwamanye amadolobha beya kwamanye zamenyezelwa ngoMashi, nakuba isiminyaminya sezimoto saqhubeka sikhona ngenxa yokusondela kweholidi lokugujwa konyaka omusha iNowruz.
Amathempeli enkolo yobuShia aseQom aqhubeka evuliwe kwaze kwaba umhla ka-16 Mashi 2020. NgoFebhuwari I-Iran yaba iziko lokubhebhetheka kwaleli gciwane, ilandela iChina.
Izinsolo zokuthi i-Iran iye yanciphisa inani langempela labantu abanalesi sifo ukuze idlulisele isithombe okungesona zenza ukuba amazwe angaphezu kweshumi ayenabantu ababenalesi sifo aphenye ngomsuka waso. Athola ukuthi lesi sifo sase sikhona e-Iran ngoFebhuwari 28, usuku uhulumeni wase-Iran abika ngalo ukuthi babengu-388 kuphela abantu ababenaso, okungase kusho ukuthi inani lalingaphezulu kakhulu kunalokho okwabikwa.
Ngomhla ka-3 Mashi, iPhalamende lase-Iran lavalwa ngemva kokuthola ukuthi amalungu alo angu-23 kwangu-290 ayenaleli gciwane.
Ngomhla ka-12 Mashi, iHuman Rights Watch yanxusa iziphathimandla zamajele ase-Iran ukuba zikhulule ngaphandle kwemibandela labo ababeboshwe bebhikisha ngokuthula belwela amalungelo abantu, nokuba kudedelwe okwesikhashana iziboshwa ezaziziphethe kahle.
Le nhlangano yachaza ukuthi ayemaningi amathuba okusakazeka kwegciwane ezindaweni ezivalelekile, njengasemajele esikhashana angenazo nezinto ezanele zokwelapha.
NgoMashi 15, uhulumeni wase-Iran wabika ukuthi babengu-100 abantu ababeshonile ngosuku olulodwa; okwakuyinani elaliphakeme ukuwedlula wonke kusukela leli gciwane lafika.
NgoMashi 17 kwase kushone osopolitiki base-Iran neziphathimandla zikahulumeni ezingaphezu kuka-12, okuhlanganisa labo ababesebenza esikhathini esingaphambili nalabo abebesasebenza khona namanje.
NgoMashi 23, base bengu-50 abantu ababethola leli gciwane ngehora kanti njalo ngemva kwemizuzu eyishumi kwakufa umuntu oyedwa ngenxa yegciwane le-corona.
Othile osebenzela inhlangano i-WHO, wathi kungenzeka ukuthi amanani angempela ase-Iran aphindwe kasihlanu kunalawo abikwayo.
Waphinde wathi kungenzeka ukuthi izindleko iMelika ezikhokhisa i-Iran zinomthelela endleleni leli zwe elingakwazi ukusingatha ngayo le nkinga ngokwezimali.
