NgoMashi 17, lesi sifo sase sibikwe kuzo zonke izingxenye ezingu-50 zezwe laseMelika kuhlanganise naseColumbia. NgoMashi 23, kwabikwsa ukuthi idolobha laseNew York lalinabantu abangu-10 700 abanegciwane le-corona, okuyinani elingaphezu kwenani labanegciwane sebebonke eSouth Korea.
NgoMashi 25, undunankulu wathi ukugwema ukusondelana kwabantu kwakubonakala kusebenza, ngoba ukulinganisa kokuphindeka kabili kwezibonelo kuye kwanensa ekusukeni ezinsukwini ezingu-2.0 kuye ezinsukwini ezingu-4.7.
Kusukela ngoMashi 28, base bengu-32,308 abantu abanegciwane edolobheni laseNew York, bengu-672 abase bebulawe yileli gciwane. NgoMashi 26, kwabikwa ukuthi inani labanesifo se-corona eMelika lase liwedlula amanani akwamanye amazwe emhlabeni wonke, okuhlanganisa iChina ne-Italy. Kusukela ngo-Ephreli 8, sekubikwe izibonelo ezingu-400,335 e-United States, kanti sekufe abangu-12,841.
Ngombiko okhishwe abezindaba ngomhla ka-30 Mashi, uMongameli waseMelika uTrump unqume ukunweba isikhathi ebesibekiwe ukuze kusiqinisekiswe ukungasondelani kwabantu kuze kube u-Ephreli 30.
Ngololo suku, umkhumbi oyisibhedlela onemibhede engaba ngu-1 000, i-USNS Comfort, wafika eNew York.
Ngo-Ephreli 3, i-U.S. ibe nesibalo esingu-884 sabafile ngenxa ye-coronavirus enkathini yamahora angu-24.
E-New York, inani labantu abanegciwane lase ledlulile ku-100 000 ngo-Ephreli 3. IPhalamende iWhite House igxekiwe ngokulithatha kancane leli gciwane nangokuthonya imibiko ekhishwa abezomnyango wezempilo nososayensi ngokukhipha isiqondiso sokuba iziphathimandla zezempilo zibambisane noSekela-Mongameli uMike Pence ekukhipheni imibiko eya emphakathini ngokuphathelene naleli gciwane.
Ukwamukelwa kwethimba elimiswe uTrump ukuba lihole kulesi simo esibucayi kubonakala kunokuchema futhi kusekelwa abalandeli beqembu lakhe.
Ezinye iziphathimandla zaseMelika nabezindaba ziyigxekile iMelika ngokuncika kakhulu kwezohwebo nezwe laseChina ukuze ithole izinto eziyisidingo ezihlanganisa nezinto ezidingekayo kwezokwelapha.
Ucwaningo lenqubo yokuhamba komoya lasebenziswa ukuze kuhlelwe futhi kuqagelwe inqubo yokusakazeka lase lunyatheliswa nge-The Journal of Travel Medicine maphakathi noJanuwari 2020.
Ngokwalokho okwakukhishwe ngo-2018 yiqembu le-International Air Transport Association, iBangakok, iHong Kong, iTokyo neTapei kwakungamazwe anezivakashi eziningi ezivela eWuhan.
IDubai, iSydney neMelborne nawo ayizindawo ezithandwa kakhulu abantu abavela eWuhan.
Phakathi kwezindawo ezingu-20 ezithandwa kakhulu yizivakashi zakwamanye amazwe, kwabikwa ukuthi iBali yayingakulungele kunazo zonke ukubhekana naleli gciwane, amadolobha ase-Australia ayehamba phambili phakathi kwezindawo ezikulungele kangcono. I-Australia yakhipha izinhlelo zayo zokubhekana naleli gciwane embikweni wayo i-Emergency Response Plan for Novel Coronavirus(COVID-19) ngoFebhuwari 7.
Yabonisa ukuthi kwakukuningi okwakungakaziwa nge-COVID-19, nokuthi enye yezindlela zokubhekana nalesi sifo kwakuwukuqinisa ekuqapheni imingcele yezwe nangokungagodli lutho okumelwe kwaziswe abantu.
NgoMashi 21, i-Australia yakhipha isimemezelo esiphuthumayo sesifo esibulalayo.
Ngemva kokusebenza kwesinyathelo sokuvalwa kwezinto zokuthutha umphakathi eWuhan naseHubei, amazwe amaningi ahlele ukukhipha izakhamuzi zawo nabameleli bamazwe abo kulezi zindawo esebenzisa izindiza eziqashiwe zasemazweni awo ngemvume yeziphathimandla zaseChina.
Amazwe okuqala alanda izisebenzi zawo kwakuyiCanada, iMelika, iJapan, i-India, iSri Lanka, i-Australia, iFrance, i-Argentina, iGermany neThailand.
IPakistan ithe ngeke ibuyise muntu oseChina.
NgoFebhuwari 7, iBrazil yathutha ngokushesha amalungu omndeni waseBrazil angu-34, ngaphezu kwalabo abane basePoland, oyedwa waseChina nomunye wase-India.
Lezi zakhamuzi zasePoland, eChina nase-India zazehle ePoland okuyilapho le ndiza yaseBrazil ayayizoma khona isikhashana ngaphambi kokuqhubeka nomzila wayo oya eBrazil.
Izakhamuzi zaseBrazil ezazikade ziseWuhan zazihlaliswe endaweni yamasosha eseduze kwaseBrasilia njengesinyathelo sokuvimbela ukusabalala kwegciwane.
Ngalolo suku kwalandwa izakhamuzi zaseCanada ezingu-215 eWuhan (ezingu-176 zazisendizeni yokuqala, ezingu-39 zisendizeni yesibili eyayiqashwe uhulumeni waseMelika) zayiswa e-CFB Trenton ukuze zihlale lapho amasonto amabili ukuze kuvinjwe ukusabalala kwegciwane.
Ngo-11 February, elinye ibhanoyi elinabantu abangu-185 base-Canada elivela e-Wuhan lafika e-CFB Trenton.
Amagunya ase-Australia athutha amalungu omphakathi angu-277 ngo-3 no-4 February bayiswa e-Christmas Island Detention Centre, ebilungiswe kabusha ukuze ibe indawo yokuvalelwa, bahlala khona izinsuku ezingu-14.
Indiza yokuthuthwa yase-New Zealand yafika e-Auckland ngo-5 February; abagibeli bayo (kuhlanganisa abathile base-Australia nabase-Pacific) babevalelwe endaweni yemikhumbi yempi e-Whangaparoa, enyakatho ye-Auckland.
Ngo-15 February, i-United States yamemezela ukuthi izothutha abantu base-America ababegibele umkhumbi wokuhamba i-Diamond Princess.
Ngo-21 February, ibhanoyi elithwele abagibeli base-Canada abangu-129 ababethuthwe begibele i-Diamond Princess lafika e-Trenton, e-Ontario.
Ekuqaleni kuka-March, uhulumeni wase-India waqala ukuthutha izakhamuzi zawo zivela e-Iran. Ngo-14 March indiza ye-South African Airways eqashwe Uhulumeni wase-South Africa yabuyisela ezweni izakhamuzi zase-South Africa ezingu-112.
Ukubheka kwezokwelapha bekwenziwa ngaphambi kokuhamba, futhi abane base-South Africa ababebonisa izimpawu ze-coronavirus bashiwa ngemuva ukuze kuncishiswe ingozi.
Izakhamuzi zase-South Africa ezinemiphumela yokuhlola elandulayo kuphela ezabuyiselwa ezweni.
Imiphumela yokuhlola yakhulula bonke abase-South Africa, kuhlanganise abasebenzi bendiza, abashayeli bendiza, izisebenzi zasehhotela, amaphoyisa namasosha ayehlangenyele kulomsebenzi wokusiza abantu okwathi, njengesinyathelo sokuqapha, banke bahlala ngaphansi kokuqashwa nokuvalelwa inkathi yezinsuku ezingu-14 e-The Ranch Resort.
Ngo-20 March, i-United States yaqala ukukhipha kancane amabutho ayo e-Iraq ngenxa yobhubhane.
Ngo-5 February, umnyango wezangaphandle wase-China wabika ukuthi amazwe angu-21 (okuhlanganisa i-Belarus, i-Pakistan, i-Trinidad and Tobago, i-Egypt, ne-Iran) athumele usizo e-China.
Abanye abafundi base-China abakumanyuvesi ase-America bahlangana ndawonye ukuze basize bathumele usizo kulezo zindawo zase-China ezihlaselwe igciwane, beneqembu elikhulu lendawo ebanzi yase-Chicago babika ukwazi ukuthumela amamaski angu-50,000 e-N95 ezibhedlela ezisesifundeni sase-Hubei ngo-30 January. Inhlangano yokusizwa kwabantu i-Direct Relief, isebenzelana ne-FedEx, yathumela amamaski obuso angu-200,000 kanye nezinye izinto zokuvila umuntu siqu, okuhlanganisa amagilavu nezingubo, ngokundizisa kwesimo esiphuthumayo okuya e-Wuhan Union Hospital ngo-30 January.
"Ngo-5 February, u-Bill no-Melinda Gates bamemezela umnikelo wezigidi ezingu-$100 ku-WHO ukuze uxhase ukucwaningela ikhambi nemisebenzi yokulapha kanjalo nokuvikela ""inani labantu abasengozini e-Africa nase-South Asia""."
I-Interaksyon yabika ukuthi uhulumeni wase-China yanikela ngamamaski angu-200,000 kubantu base-Philippines ngo-6 February, ngemuva kokuthi u-Senator Richard Gordon ethumele amamaski ayizigidi ezingu-3.16 e-Wuhan.
Ngo-19 February, i-Singapore Red Cross yamemezela ukuthi izothumela usizo lwezigidi ezingu-$2.26 e-China.
I-Japan inikele ngamamaski ayisigidi esisodwa e-Wuhan, i-Turkey yahambisa izinto zezokwelapha, i-Russia yathumela e-Wuhan amathani angaphezulu kwezigidi ezingu-13 ezinto zezokwelapha, i-Malaysia imemezele umnikelo wamaglavu ezokwelapha ayizigidi ezingu-18 e-China, i-Germany ihambise izinhlobo ezihlukene zezinto zezokwelapha kuhlanganise u-10,000 wama-Hazmat suits, ne-United States inikele amathani angu-17.8 tons ezinto zezokwelapha e-China futhi yathembisa izigidi ezingu-$100 ngokwengeziwe wokusekela ngokwezimali kumazwe athintekile. Ngemuva kokubonakala kwezibonelo zase-China zibohla, izwe belithumela usizo emazweni ahlukene athintwe ubhubhane.
Ngo-March, i-China, i-Cuba ne-Russia yathumela izimpahla zezokwelapha futhi ilindele ukusiza i-Italy ibhekane nokuqubuka kwe-coronavirus yayo.
Usomabhizinisi u-Jack Ma wathumela izigidi ezingu-1.1 zamakhithi okuhlola, amamaski obuso ayizigidi ezingu-6, namasudi okuvikela angu-60,000 e-Addis Ababa, e-Ethiopia ukuze zabiwe yi-African Union.
Waphinda kamuva wathumela amakhithi okuhlola angu-5,000, amamaski obuso angu-100,000 kanye nama-ventilators angu-5 e-Panama.
U-Ma uphinde wanikela ngezimpahla zezokwelapha e-Canada. I-The Netherlands, i-Spain, i-Turkey, i-Georgia, ne-Czech Republic baveze ukukhathazeka ngamamaski enziwe e-China namakhithi okuhlola.
Ngokwesibonelo, i-Spain yakhipha amakhithi okuhlola enziwe e-China angu-58,000 anokunemba okungaba u-30% nje, ngesikhathi esifanayo, i-Netherlands yabizela emuva amamaski obuso ase-China angu-600,000 atholakala enenkinga defective.
I-Belgium yabizela emuva amamaski angasebenziseki angu-100,000, acabangelwa njengavele e-China, kanti eqinisweni ayevela e-Colombia.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, usizo lwase-China lwamukelwe ngezandla ezivulekile kwezinye izindawo zase-Latin America nase-Africa. Ngo-2 April, i-World Bank yaqalisa imisebenzi yokusekela isimo esiphuthumayo samazwe asathuthuka.
I-WHO income imizamo yamagunya ase-China yokunakekela nokuvalela umshayabhuqe.
"I-WHO iqaphele umahluko phakathi kokuqubuka kuka-2002–2004 kwe-SARS, lapho amagunya ase-China amangalelwa ngokwenza ngasese okwabangela ubunzima ekuvikeleni futhi kwalulaza imizamo yokuvalela, kanye nesimo samanje lapho uhulumeni oyinhloko ""ehlinzekele njalo ngizibuyekezo ukuze kugwenywe uvalo ngaphambi kwamaholidi e-Lunar New Year""."
"Ngo 23 January, isabela ekunqumeni kwamagunya ayinhloko ukuthi kumiswe umthetho ovala ezokuthutha e-Wuhan, omelela i-WHO u-Gauden Galea waphawula ukuthi noma lokhu ""kungesiso neze isikhuthazo se-WHO"", ngesikhathi esifanayo ""isinqumo esibaluleke kakhulu sokuzinikela ekuvaleleni umshayabhuqe endaweni lapho ugxile kakhulu khona"" futhi wasibiza ngokuthi ""esingakaze sibe khona ngaphambili emlandweni wezezempilo zomphakathi"". Ngo-30 January, kulandela ukuqiniseka kokudluliselana komuntu nomuntu ngaphandle kwase-China nokuphakama kwesibalo sezibonelo kwamanye amazwe, i-WHO yamemezela ukuqubuka ngokuthi i-Public Health Emergency of International Concern (PHEIC), i-PHEIC yesithupha kusukela isinyathelo saqala ukuncengelwa ngokuqubuka kuka-2009 kwe-swine flu."
"Umqondisi Omkhulu we-WHO u-Tedros Adhanom uthe i-PHEIC ibe ngenxa yesizathu ""sengozi yokusabalala kwembulunga, ikakhulukazi emazweni ezimali eziphansi nezimali eziphakathi angenayo inqubo yezezempilo enamandla."
"Esabela ekumisweni kwemikhawulo yokuhamba, u-Tedros ukhiphe elokuthi ""asikho isizathu sezinyathelo ezithinta ukuhamba nokuhwebelana kwamazwe ngaphandle kwesidingo"" nokuthi ""i-WHO ayikukhuthazi ukubeka umkhawulo kwezokuhweba nokunyakaza."""
"Ngo-5 February, i-WHO yanxusa izigidi engu-$675 kumphakathi wembulunga ukuze kuxhaswe isu lokulindelela lamazwe ezimali eziphansi, ilandisa ngokuphuthuma kokusekela lawo mazwe ""angenazo izindlela ezikhona zokuthola abantu abathole igciwane, noma kungathiwa liyavela""."
"U-Tedros waqhubeka nokulandisa ephakamisa ukuthi ""siqine kuphela ngezinga lalowo othambe kakhulu wethu"" futhi wancenga umphakathi wamazwe onke ukuthi ""utshale imali namhlanje noma uhlawule kakhulu ngokuzayo"". Ngo-11 February, i-WHO phakathi nengqungquthela yabezindaba yamisa i-COVID-19 yaba igama lesifo."
"Ngosuku olufanayo, u-Tedros washo ukuthi uNobhala Jikelele we-UN u-António Guterres ubesevumile ukuhlinzekela ""amandla enqubo yonke ye-UN ekusabeleni""."
"Iqembu Lokunakekela Inhlekelele le-UN liqalisiwe njengomphumela, kwavumela ukubambisana kokusabela kwayo yonke i-United Nations, okwenza i-WHO ithi lokhu kuzovumela yona ukuthi ""igxile ekusabeleni kwezezempilo lapho abanye abamelelayo beletha okwabo ubuhlakani ekubambeni ububanzi kwezokuhlala, kwezomnotho nezokuthuthukisa okuvezwa ukuqubuka""."
"Ngo 14 February, iqembu eliholwa i-WHO leNjongo Ehlangene ne-China laqaliswa ukuze lihlinzekele ochwepheshe bomhlaba ne-WHO endaweni ephansi e-China ukuze basize ekunakekelene ngaphakathi bese besinga isimo ""sobukhulu nokudluliseleka kwegciwane"" ngokuvula imihlangano yokufundisana hosting workshops nemihlangano nezikhungo zezinga lezwe elimqoka nokuqhuba uhlelo lokuvakashela amagceke ukuze kuhlolwe ""umphumela wemisebenzi yokusabela ngezinga lezifunda nezifundazwe, kuhlanganise izimo zasemadolobheni nezasemaphandleni"". Ngo-25 February, i-WHO yamisa ukuthi ""izwe kumele lenze okwengeziwe ukuzilungiselela okungase kube ubhubhane lwe-coronavirus,"" ibika ukuthi yize kusekuqaleni kakhulu ukuyibiza ngobhubhane, amazwe kumele kodwa abe ""sesigabeni sokulindela""."
"Isabela ekwandeni kokuqubuka e-Iran, i-WHO ithumele Eqembu Elihlangene Lomgomo khona ukuze lihlaziye isimo. Ngo-28 February, i-WHO ikhiphe elokuthi ukuhlaziya ingozi ye-coronavirus ezingeni lomhlaba kuzophakamiswa kusuke ""kokuphakeme"" kuye ""kokuphakeme kakhulu"", okuyibanga eliphakeme kakhulu lesixwayiso nokuhlaziya ingozi."
"U-Mike Ryan, ongumqondisi ophethe wohlelo lezokuphuthumayo kwezempilo ze-WHO, uxwayisile ngamazwi athi ""Lokhu kuyinkathi yokusanguluka kuwo wonke uhulumeni emhlabeni: Vukani."
"Leli gciwane kungenzeka lisendleleni yayo futhi kudingeka ukulindela,"" ukuncenga ukuthi izinyathelo zokusabela okuhle kungasiza umhlaba ugweme ""okubi kakhulu kwalo""."
"U-Ryan uphinde wathi idatha yamanje ayizange ibizele ukuthi izisebenzi zezempilo zomphakathi zimemezele ubhubhane wezwe lonke, ethi ukukhipha isimemezelo esinjalo kungasho ukuthi ""samukela ukuthi wonke umuntu emhlabeni uzochayeka kulelo gciwane."""
Ngo-11 March, i-WHO yamemezela ukuqubuka kwe-coronavirus ubhubhane.
"Umqondisi Jikelele uthe i-WHO ""ikhathazeke kakhulu ngakho kokubili ukuthusa kwamazinga okubhebhetheka nobunzima, kanye namazinga athusayo okungenzi lutho"". I-WHO ibhekane nokugxekwa ngokubonakala kungukuphatha okungagculisi kobhubhane, kuhlanganise ukwephuza kokumemezela isimo esiphuthumayo sezempilo yomphakathi nokuqoka igciwane njengobhubhane."
Imbibizane ihlanganise isicelo somphakathi sokuthi Umqondisi Jikelele we-WHO u-Tedros Adhanom afake incwadi yakhe yokushiya umsebenzi, yasayinwa ngabantu abangu-733,000 ngo-6 April.
Ngo-26 March 2020, inqwaba yochwepheshe be-UN bamalungelo abantu bagcizelela ukuhlonishwa kwamalungelo abo bonke abantu njengoba kuqhubeka ubhubhane lwe-COVID-19.
Iqembu lochwepheshe laphakamisa ukuthi wonke umuntu unelungelo kukho konke ukungenela kokusindisa impilo nokuthi uhulumeni unomthwalo wemfanelo kulokhu.
Iqembu lagcizelela ukuthi ukuntulela kwamandla noma kwemishwalense yezezempilo akumele neze kusebenze njengesizathu sokubandlulula iqembu elithile.
Ochwepheshe bagxile ekutheni wonke umuntu unelungelo lokufinyelela ezezempilo, okuhlanganisa abantu abakhubazekile, abavela kumaqembu amancane, abantu abakhulile, abantu abangababaleli bangaphakathi, abangenamakhaya, labo abaphila ngaphansi kwezimo zobumpofu obunzima, abantu ababoshiwe, kanjalo abangababaleki namanye amaqembu angacacisiwe adinga usizo lukahulumeni.
Izinhlangano zohulumeni bamazwe zinakekela imiphumela yezomnotho nezokuhlala zenhlekelele ye-COVID-19.
I-The Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development iqalise ilungiselelo lokuhlinzekela ngolwazi olufika ngesikhathi noluphelele endleli yokusabela emthethweni ngamazwe emhlabeni jikelele, kanjalo nemibono nezeluleko.
Kusukela emithethweni yokuqinisa inqubo yezezempilo nezomnotho zomhlaba kuye ekunakekeleni imiphumela yokuvala phansi nokukhawula ukuhamba, ihabhu yedijithali ihlanganisa i-Country Policy Tracker, futhi ihlose ukusiza amazwe afunde kwelinye nelinye nokungenela ekuvumelaniseni ukusabela kwembulunga kulenselele ye-coronavirus.
Uhulumeni wase-China ugxekwe kakhulu yi-United States, i-UK Minister ye-Cabinet Office u-Michael Gove, no-Eduardo Bolsonaro indodana kaMongameli wase-Brazil u-Jair Bolsonaro ngendlela abaphathe ngayo ubhubhane, olwaqala e-Hubei eyizifundazwe sase-China.
Isibalo sabasingathi bezinga lesifundazwe be-Communist Party of China (CPC) baxoshwa ngesizathu sendlela abaphatha ngayo imizamo yokuvalelwa e-Central China, uphawu lokunganeliseki endleleni yokusabela kwegatsha lepolitiki ekuqubukeni kulezo zindawo.
Abanye abahlaziyi bakholelwa ukuthi lesi sinyathelo besihloselwe ukuvikela unobhala jikelele we-Chinese Communist Party u-Xi Jinping olakeni lomphakathi endabeni yokuqubuka kwe-coronavirus.
Abanye abasebenzi base-China, isib. u-Zhao Lijian wala ekuqaleni ukwamukela ukuqubuka kwe-coronavirus okuqala e-Wuhan, ekhetha imibono yozungu mayelana ne-COVID-19 njengeqhamuka e-U.S. noma e-Italy.
"I-U.S. administration ka-Donald Trump ike yabiza i-coronavirus ngokuthi ""i-Chinese virus"" nokuthi ""i-Wuhan virus"" bethi inqubo ye-China ""yokwenza ngokufihla kuphe amandla igciwane manje eseliphenduke ubhubhane lomhlaba"", okuphenduke kwagxekwa ngabanye abagxeki njengokucwasa ""nokuphazam[isa] ekuhlulekeni kwe-administration yakhe yokuvalela isifo""."
"I-The Daily Beast yafinyelela ukwaziswa kwahulimeni we-U.S. eveza kabanzi isu lokukhulumisana okusobala ukuthi kuvela ku-National Security Council, isu licashunwe ngokuthi ""Yonke into imayelana ne-China."
"Siyatshelwa ukuthi sizame ukukhipha lomyalezo nganoma iyindlela engenzeka, kuhlanganise izingqungquthela zabezindaba nokuvela kuma-TV. ""Abasakazi abanjenge-Politico, i-Foreign Policy, ne-Bloomberg balandise ukuthi imizamo ye-China yokuthumela usizo emazweni ahlaselwe igciwane kuyingxenye yenkulumo-ze lokufinyelela ukwazi ukuthonya imbulunga."
"Isikhulu senqubomgomo yangaphandle se-EU u-Josep Borrell waxwayisa ukuthi kukhona ""inhlansi yepolitiki yendawo ehlanganisa umshikashika wokuba nethonya ngokusonta izinto ne-'politiki yokuba nesandla esivulekile'""."
"U-Borrell uphinde wathi ""i-China iphusha ngamandla umlayezo wokuthi, ngokungafani ne-US, yona ingumlingani onesibopho nothembekile."""
I-China iphinde yakhulumela ukuthi i-US iphakamise umnswinyo wayo e-Syria, e-Venezuela nase-Iran, yize kubikwa ukuthi ithumela usizo kulamazwe amabili okugcina.
Umnikelo ka-Jack Ma wamamaski angu-100,000 aya e-Cuba wavinjwa unswinyo lwase-US ngo-3 April.
Amagunya ase-US aphinde amangalelwa ngokuphambukisa usizo olumiselwe ezinye izizwe ukuthi luye ezweni awo.
Futhi kube nemibiko yokubangwa kwamamaski phakathi kwamanye amazwe, anjengeJalimane, i-Austria ne-Switzerland, kanye ne-Czech Republic ne-Italy.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, i-Turkey yaqhwaga amakhulu ama-ventilator abelibangise e-Spain.
Ekuqaleni kuka-Mashi, uhulumeni wase-Italy ugxeke i-European Union ngokuntula ubunye ne-Italy ibe ihlaselwe i-coronavirus.
"uMaurizio Massari, inxusa le-Italy kwi-EU, uthe ""i-China kuphela esabele ngokuthe nqgo."
