Ukuhlolwa kama-antibody kubonisa ukuthi bangaki abantu asebeke baba naso isifo kuhlanganise nalabo izimpawu zabo zazincane kakhulu ukuthi zazingabikwa noma abangenazo nhlobo izimpawu.
Isibalo esinembile sezinga lokufa kwabantu ngalesifo kanye nezinga lokungatheleleki kweningi emphakathini kungatholakala emphumelweni yalolu vivinyo.
Ngenxa yokulinganiselwa kwamanani okuhlolwa, ngesikhathi sika-March 2020, awekho amazwe abenezibalo ezingathenjwa mayelana nesibalo sokusabalala kwe-virus emphakathini wawo.
Ngo-23 March, alikho izwe ebeselihlole ngaphezu kuka-3 % wabantu abasemazweni awo futhi kukhona ukuhluka okukhulu kwenani lezibalo zokuhlolwa osekwenziwe emazweni ahlukahlukene.
Loku kuhluka kungenzeka ukuthi kuthinta kakhulu amanani okufa kwabantu abikiwe okungenzeka zeqe ngehaba kwamazwe athile.
Ngokusetshenziswa kwe-real-time reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction, i-rRt-PCR, lokuhlola kungenziwa kuma-respiratory samples atholwe ngezindlela ezihlukahlukene, kuhlanganise ne-nasopharyngeal swab noma i-sputum sample.
Imiphumela ngokuvamile itholakala phakathi namahora amabili kuya ezinsukwini ezingu-2.
Ukuhlola okubizwa nge-RT-PCR okwenziwa ngama-swab omphimbo kungaba nokuthenjelwa esontweni lokuqala kuphela kokophathwa yisifo.
Ngokuzayo, i-virus inganyamalala emphinjeni kodwa ibe iqhubeka yanda emaphaphini.
Kubantu abenegciwane abahlolwe ngesonto lesibili, okunye i-sample material ingakhishwa ekujuleni kwemizila yokuhogela nge-suction catheter noma ngokukhwehlela i-material, sputum, ingasebenziswa.
Ezinye zezindlela zokuhlola zokuqala ze-PCR zathuthukiswa e-Charite e-Berlin ngo-January 2020 kusebenziswa i-real-time reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction ,irRT-PCR, okwenza isisekelo sokusakazwa kwama khithi angu-250,000 yi-World Health Organization, WHO.
I-United Kingdom nayo yayisithuthukise indlela yokuhlola ngo-23 January 2020. Inkampany yase-South Korea i-Kogenebiotech yathuthukisa iPCR-based SARSCoV-2 kit yokuhlola esezingeni lokusebenza emtholampilo ngo-28 January 2020.
