Ukuhlanza izandla (noma ukuwash'izandla), okaziwa futhi ngokuthi inhlanzeko yezandla, isenzo sokuzicoca izandla ngenhloso yokususa inhlabathi, ugrisi, izinto ezincane, noma izitaputapu ezingafuneki.
Ukuhlanza izandla ngensipho ngokungalibali kulezo "zikhathi ezibucayi" phakathi nosuku kuvikela ukusabalala kwezifo eziningi, ngokwesibonelo uhudo nekholera, okuthelelana ngenqubo yendle–yomlomo.
Abantu bangaphinde batheleleke ngezifo zokuphefumula njengomkhuhlane noma amakhaza avamile, ngokwesibonelo, uma bengahlanzi izandla zabo ngaphambi kokuzithinta amehlo, ikhala, noma umlomo (okungukuthi, izici ezisamafinyila).
Izinkathi ezibucayi ezinhlanu phakathi nosuku lapho ukuhlanza izandla ngensipho kubalulekile kuhlanganisa: ngaphambili nangemuva kokuzikhulula, ngemuva kokuhlanza izinqa zosana noma ukushintsha amanephi, ngaphambi kokufunza usana, ngaphambi kokudla nangaphambi nangemuva kokulungisa ukudla noma ukuphatha inyama engaphekiwe, inhlanzi, noma izinyoni ezifuywayo.
Uma amanzi nensipho kungatholakali, izandla zingahlanzwa ngomlotha. I-World Health Organization ikhuthaza ukuhlanzwa kwezandla:
Ngaphambi, phakathi, nangemuva kokulungisa ukudla.
Ngaphambi nangemuva kokunakekela umuntu ogulayo.
Ngemuva kokushintsha amanephi noma kokuhlanza ingane ebisebenzisa indlu yangasese.
Ngemuva kokufinya, ukukhwehlela noma ukuthimula.
Ngemuva kokuthinta isilwane, ukudla kwesilwane, noma ukungcolisa kwesilwane.
Inhlanzeko yezandla yezokwelapha ibhekisela ezindleleni zenhlanzeko ezihlobene nenqubo yezokwelapha.
Ukuhlanza izandla ngaphambi kokunikeza umuthi noma usizo lokwelapha lungavikela noma kunciphise ukusabalala kwesifo.
Injongo eyinhloko yezokwelapha yokuhlanza izandla ukukhuculula ngokucoca izandla ama-pathogens (ama-bacteria, ama-viruses, noma amanye ama-microorganisms angabangela izifo) namakhemikhali angabangela ukulimala noma izifo.
Lokhu kubaluleke kakhulu kubantu abaphatha ukudla noma abasebenza kumkhakha wezokwelapha, kodwa kuyinqubo ebalulekile ngisho nakumphakathi ovamile.
Ukuhlanza izandla kunezinzuzo zempilo eziningi, kuhlanganisa ukunciphisa ukusabalala komkhuhlane, i-coronavirus, nezinye izifo ezithelelayo; ekuvikeleni izimbangela ezithelelanayo zohudo; ukunciphisa izifo zokuphefumula;
nokunciphisa izinga lokufa kwezinsana ekubeletheleni ekhaya.
Ucwaningo lango-2013 lwabonisa ukuthi inqubo yokuhlanza izandla ethuthukile ingase iholele ezingeni elincane lokuthuthuka ebudeni bokukhula kwezingane ezingaphansi kweminyaka eyisihlanu.
Emazweni asathuthuka, izinga lokufa kwabasha oluhlobene nezifo zokuphefumula nohudo lingancishiswa ngokuqalisa ushintsho lokuziphatha olulula, njengokuhlanza izandla ngensipho.
Isenzo esilula singanciphisa izinga lokufa ngalezizifo cishe ngo-50%.
Izindlela zokungenela ezikhuthaza ukuhlanza izandla ngensipho zinganciphisa iziqephu zohudo ngezinxenye ezintathu, futhi lokhu kungaqhathaniswa nokuhlinzekela amanzi ahlanzekile ezindaweni ezintulayo ngokwezimali.
Ukuncipha kweziqephu zohudo ngo-48% kungahlotshaniswa nokuhlanza izandla ngensipho. Ukuhlanza izandla ngensipho indlela eyodwa esebenza kahle futhi eyindleko encane ukuze kuvikelwe uhudo nama-acute respiratory infections (ARI), njengenqubo yokuziphatha ezenzekalelayo eyenzeka emakhaya, ezikoleni, nasemiphakathini emhlabeni wonke.
Inyumoniya, eyi-ARI enkulu, ihola yodwa njengembangela yokufa kwezinsana ezingaphansi kweminyaka eyisihlanu, ichitha izimpilo zezingane ezilinganiselwa ku-1.8 wezigidi ngonyaka.
Uhudo nenyumoniya kokubili kunesandla ekufeni kwezinsana eziyizigidi cishe ezingu-3.5 ngonyaka.
Ngokusho kwe-UNICEF, ukuguqula ukuhlamba izandla ngensipho ngaphambi kokudla futhi nangemuva kokusebenzisa indlu yangasese ukuthi kube umkhuba ogxilile kungasindisa izimpilo ezengeziwe kunanoma iliphi ikhambi elilodwa noma ukungenela kwezokwelapha, kunquma ukufa ngenxa yesizathu sohudo cishe ngengxenye nokufa ngezifo zokuphefumula ngengxenye eyodwa.
Ukuhlanza izandla ngokuvamile kuhlanganiswe ndawonye nokunye ukungenela kokuthutha udoti njengenxenye yamanzi, izinhlelo zokuthutha udoti nenhlanzeko (i-WASH).
Ukuhlanza izandla kuphinde kuvikele kusifo se-impetigo esidluliselana ngokuthintana okuqondile.
Ingozi encane eba khona njengomphumela wokuhlanza izandla njalo ukulimala kwesikhumba okubangelwa ukoma kwesikhumba.
Ucwaningo lwama-Danish lango-2012 lathola ukuthi ukuhlanza izandla ngokweqile kungaba nomphumela wokuluma, nesimo sesikhumba esinoqweqwe esaziwa ngokuthi i-hand eczema noma i-hand dermatitis, okuyinto evame kakhulu kubantu abangabasebenzi bokunakekela impilo.
Ukuhlanza izandla kaningi kuphinde kubonakale njengenye yezimpawu ze-obsessive-compulsive disorder (OCD).
Kunezikhathi ezibucayi ezinhlanu phakathi nosuku lapho ukuhlanza izandla ngensipho kubaluleke khona ukunciphisa ukudlulisela isifo ngenqubo yendle-ngomlomo: ngemuva kokusebenzisa indlu yangasese (ukuchama, ukuzikhulula), ngemuva kokuhlanza izinqa zosana (ukushintsha amanephi), ngamphambi kokufunza usana, ngaphambi kokudla noma ngaphambi/ngemuva kokulungisa ukudla noma kokuphatha inyama engaphekiwe, inhlanzi, noma izinyoni ezifuywayo.
Ezinye izikhathi lapho inqubo efanele yokuhlanza izandla kufanele ilandelwe ukuze kugwenywe ukudlulisela kwesifo kuhlanganisa ngaphambi nangemuva kokunakekela ukusikeka noma ukukulimala; ngemuva kokuthimula, ukukhwehlela, noma ukufinya; ngemuva kokuthinta uthuvi besilwane noma ukuphatha izilwane; nangemuva kokuthinta udoti.
Emazweni amaningi, kunezinga eliphansi lokuhlanza izandla ngensipho.
Ucwaningo lokuhlanza izandla emazweni angu-54 ngo-2015 lathola ukuthi ngokwesilinganiso, u-38.7% wemikhaya ulandela inqubo yokuhlanza izandla ngensipho. Ucwaningo lango-2014 labonisa ukuthi i-Saudi Arabia yayinezinga eliphakeme kakhululu lamaphesenti angu-97; i-United States eduze naphakathi ngamaphesenti angu-77; ne-China ngezinga eliphansi kakhulu lamaphesenti angu-23. Izinqubo ezimbalwa zemikhuba sezikhona manje ekukhuphuleni ukwamukela umkhuba wokuhlanza izandla ngensipho ngezikhathi ezibucayi. Ukuhlanza izandla njengeqembu kwezingane zesikole ngezikhathi ezimisiwe zosuku enye yazo emazweni asathuthuka ukuze kugxiliswe ukuhlanza izandla emikhubeni yezingane.
I-"Essential Health Care Program" eyaqaliswa i-Department of Education e-Philippines iyisibonelo sesenzo sesibalo sokukhuthaza ezempilo zezingane nezemfundo.
Ukukhipha izikelemu kabili ngonyaka, kuhambisane nokuhlanza izandla njalo ngensipho, ukuxubha nsuku zonke nge-fluoride, kuyinsika yohlelo lwezwe.
Iqaliswe ngempumelelo futhi nase-Indonesia.
Ukususa ama-microorganism esikhumbeni kuba nakangcono ngokufakwa kwensipho noma okokuhlanza emanzini.
Umsebenzi oyinhloko wensipho nokokuhlanza ukunciphisa izinto ezivimba isixazululo, futhi zikhuphule i-solubility.
Amanzi wodwa awanele ekuhlanzeni isikhumba ngoba amafutha namaphrotheyini, ayizakhiwo zenhlabathi, awancibiliki kalula emanzini.
Kodwa ukuhlanza kusizwa amanzi agelezayo ngokwezinga..
Insipho eyiqhuzu, ngoba iyakwazi ukuphinde isebenze, ingase igcine igciwane elisele ekusebenzeni kwangaphambili.
Isibalo esincane socwaningo olubheke ukudluliselwa kwegciwane elisuka ensiphweni eyiqhuzu ethole ukungcola siphethe ngokuthi akunakwenzeka njengoba amagciwane ehlambululeka kanye negwebu.
I-CDC isaqhubeka nokuthi "insipho ewuketshezi nokulawula ngaphandle kwezandla kungcono".
Izinsipho eziqeda amagciwane zikhangiswe kakhulu amalungu omphakathi okhathalela ezempilo.
Kuze kube namuhla, abukho ubufakazi bokuthi ukusebenzisa ama-antiseptics noma ama-disinfectants asikiselwayo kukhetha ama-antibiotic-resistant organisms emvelo.
Nokho, izinsipho ezi-antibacterial zinezimeleli ezivamile zama-antibacterial njenge-triclosan, enohlu elude lwama-resistant strains ama-organism.
Ngakho, ngisho noma ama-antibiotic resistant strains engakhethiwe insipho e-antibacterial, kungenzeka ingakwazi ukusebenza kahle ngendlela edayiselwa yona.
Ngaphandle kwalokho i-surfactant nesimeleli esivikela isikhumba, izakhiwo eziyinkimbinkimbi zingase zibe nama-acid (i-acetic acid, i-ascorbic acid, i-lactic acid) njengesilawuli se-pH, i-antimicrobially active benzoic acid nezinye izinakekeli zesikhumba (i-aloe vera, ama-vitamin, i-menthol, ama-plant extracts). Ukuhlolisisa okubanzi okuvela e-University of Oregon School of Public Health kwabonisa ukuthi izinsipho ezingenalutho zisebenza ngempumelelo ngendlela efanayo nama-consumer-grade anti-bacterial soaps ane-triclosan ekuvikeleni ukugula nokususa amagciwane ezadleni.
Amanzi ashisayo ongakwazi ukuhlanza ngawo izandla awashisi ngezinga elifanele ukuze kufe amagciwane.
Amagciwane akhula kakhulu lapho ukushisa komziba kungu-(37 °C).
Kodwa, amanzi afudumele, anensipho asebenza kangcono kunamanzi abandayo, anensipho ekususeni amafutha emvelo abamba inhlabathi namagciwane.
Ngokuhlukile kokukholelwa inqwaba kodwa, ucwaningo lososayensi lubonisile ukuthi ukusebenzisa amanzi afudumele akunamthelela ekunciphiseni i-microbial load ezandleni.
I-hand sanitizer noma i-hand antiseptic iyisimeleli senhlanzeko yezandla esingenziwe ngamanzi.
Ekupheleni kwawo-1990 nasekuqaleni kwengxenye lekhulu yekhulu leminyaka lama-21, izimeleli zenhlanzeko yezandla ezingenziwe ngamanzi zokuhlikihla nge-alcohol (zibuye zaziwe ngokuthi ama-alcohol-based hand rubs, ama-antiseptic hand rubs, noma ama-hand sanitizers) aqala ukuthola ukuduma.
Amaningi asekelwe ku-isopropyl alcohol noma i-ethanol eyakhuwe yahlanganiswa ngesimeleli esishubisayo njenge-Carbomer (i-polymer of acrylic acid) yenze kube ijeli, noma i-humectant njenge-glycerin ibe uketshezi, noma igwebu ukuze kube lula ukusebenzisa nokunciphisa isimo sokoma se-alcohol.
Ukufaka i-hydrogen-peroxide efakwe uketshezi iphakamisa umsebenzi we-antimicrobial nakakhulu. Ama-hand sanitizer ane-alcohol engu-60 to 95% abulala amagciwane ngempumelelo.
Ama-alcohol rub sanitizer abulala amagciwane, ama-multi-drug resistant bacteria (i-MRSA ne-VRE), i-tuberculosis, namanye amagciwane (kuhlanganise i-HIV, ama-herpe, i-RSV, i-rhinovirus, i-vaccinia, i-influenza, ne-hepatitis) ne-fungi.
Ama-alcohol rub sanitizers ane-70% ye-alcohol abulala u-99.97% (u-3.5 log ngokuncipha, ngokufanayo no-35 decibel ngokuncipha) wamagciwane ezandleni ngemizuzwana engu-30 ngemuva kokugcoba no-99.99% kuye ku-99.999% (4 kuya ku-5 log ngokuncipha) kwamagciwane ezandleni umzuzu ongu-1 ngemuva kokugcoba. Ama-hand sanitizers asebenza kahle kumagciwane futhi asebenze kancane kumagciwane athile.
Ama-hand sanitizer enziwe nge-alcohol acishe angasebenzi nhlobo ku-norovirus (noma i-Norwalk) uhlobo lwamagciwane, imbangela eyinhloko ye-gastroenteritis ethelelanayo. I-hand antiseptic eyanele noma i-alcohol rub kumele isebenziswe ukuthi ithambise ngokuphelele noma imboze zombili izandla.
Ingaphambili nengemuva lazo zombili izandla nangaphakathi nasekugcineni kweminwe kuyahlikihlwa cishe imizuzwana engu-30 kuze kube yilapho uketshezi, igwebu noma ijeli isiyomile.
Izingcina zeminwe kumele zihlanzwe nazo, zihlikihlwe ezintendeni zombili. I-The US Center for Disease Control and Prevention ikhuthaza ukuhlanza izandla kunokuhlikihla ngama-hand sanitizer, ikhakhulukazi lapho kusobala ukuthi izandla zingclolile.
Ukuphakama ekusebenziseni lezi zimeleli kungenxa yokusenza kwazo okulula namandla okushesha ukubulala ama-micro-organisms; kodwa, okufanele zisetshenziswe ukuze zithathe indawo yokuhlanza izandla efanele ngaphandle kwalapho insipho namanzi kungatholakali.
Ukusebenzisa ama-hand sanitizer asekelwe ku-alcohol njalo kungabangela isikhumba esomile ngaphandle kwalapho uma kufakwe ama-emollient kanye/noma iziswakamisi zesikhumba ekuhlanganiseni.
Inqubo yokoma kwe-alcohol ingancishiswa noma kuqedwe ngokufaka i-glycerin kanye/noma ama-emollients ekuhlanganiseni.
Ekuhloleni kokwelapha, ama-hand sanitizers asekelwe ku-alcohol anama-emollients enza ukulunyelwa kwesikhumba okwehle kakhulu nokoma kunensipho noma izihlanzi ezine-antimicrobial.
I-Allergic contact dermatitis, i-contact urticaria syndrome noma i- hypersensitivity to alcohol noma ama-additives akhona kuma-alcohol hand rubs awavamile ukuba khona.
Isimo esiphansi sokubangela i-irritant contact dermatitis sibe okukhangayo uma siqhathaniswa nokuhlanza izandla ngensipho namanzi.
Kungakhathaliseki ukusebenza kwazo, izimeleli ezingenamanzi azikwazi ukuhlanza izandla ezintweni zemvelo, kodwa zibulala amagciwane nje.
Kungalesi sizathu ukuthi ama-hand sanitizers awasebenzi kahle njengensipho namanzi ekuvikeleni ukusabalala kwama-pathogens amaningi, njengoba ama-pathogens eqhubeka esezandleni.
Ukuphumelela kwama-hand sanitizer angenayo i-alcohol kuncike kakhulu ezithakweni nokuhlanganiswa, futhi ngokomlando asebenza ngokuphoxayo kune-alcohol nama-alcohol rubs.
Muva nje, ukuhlanganisa okusebenzisa i-benzalkonium chloride kubonise ukuphikelela nokwanda komsebenzi we-antimicrobial ngemuva kokugcoba, ngokungafani ne-alcohol, esibonisiwe ukuthi yehlisa izinga lokusebenza ngemva kokusebenza ngokuphindwa, kungenzeka ingesizathu sokusabela okuqhubekayo kwesikhumba.
Abantu abaningi emiphakathini entulayo kwezezimali abakwazi ukuthenga insipho futhi basebenzisa umlotha noma inhlabathi esikhundleni.
Umlotha noma inhlabathi ingase isebenze kangcono kunamanzi kuphela, kodwa isebenze kancane kunensipho.
Okukodwa okukhathazayo ukuthi uma inhlabathi noma umlotha uthole ukungcola kwama-micro-organisms kungase kuphakamise ukusabalala kwesifo kunokusinciphisa.
Njengensipho, umlotha nawo uyisimeleli esiqeda igciwane ngoba lapho uhlanganiswa namanzi, kudaleka ingxube ye-alkaline.
I-WHO ikhuthaza umlotha noma isihlabathi esikhundleni sensipho uma insipho ingatholakali.
Inqubo efanele yokuhlanza izandla ekhuthazwa i-US Centers for Disease Control for prevention of transmission of disease ihlanganisa lezi zinyathelo:
Matisa izandla ngamanzi ahambayo afudumele noma abandayo.
Amanzi ahambayo ayakhuthazwa ngoba obheseni abamile kungenzeka babe nokungcola, kanti isimo sokubanda noma sokushisa samanzi asibonisi senza umehluko.
Gcoba izandla ngokuzihlikihla ngensipho eyanele kahle, kuhlanganise ingemuva lezandla, phakathi neminwe, nangaphansi kwezinzipho.
Insipho iphakamisa amagciwane esikhumbeni, futhi ucwaningo lubonisa ukuthi abantu bavame ukuhlanza izandla zabo kakhle uma insipho ikhona kunalapho besebenzisa amanzi kuphela.
Huhla okungenani imizuzwana engu-20.
Ukuhuhla kubangela ukushisa, okusizayo ekususeni amagciwane esikhumbeni, futhi ukuhuhla isikhathi esinde kususa amagciwane engeziwe.
Hlambulula kahle ngaphansi kwamanzi ahambayo.
Ukuhlambulula kubheseni kungase kuzingcolise izandla
Omisa ngethawula elihlanzekile noma uvumele zome ngomoya.
Izandla ezimanzi neziswakeme zikuthatha kalula ukungcola. Izindawo ezilibaleka kalula isithupha, isihlakalo, izindawo eziphakathi neminwe, nangaphansi kwezinzipho.
Izinzipho zokufakelwa ne-nail polish edlekile kungafukamela ama-microorganism.
Iloshini eswakamisayo ivamile ukukhuthazwa ukuze ugcine izandla zingomile; isikhumba esomile singaholela ekulimaleni kwesikhumba okungaphakamisa ukuchayeka kokudluliselwa isifo.
Izinhlelo ezihlukile ezingabizi zingenziwa ukuze kuhlangabezanwe nokuhlanza izandla lapho amanzi empompi kanye/noma insipho kungatholakali isib. ukuthela amanzi ngokulengisa isitsha noma isigubhu esinezimbobo ezifanele kanye/noma usebenzise umlotha uma kudingeka emazweni asathuthuka. Ezimweni ezinamanzi alinganiselwe (njengezikole noma izindawo zasemaphandleni emazweni asathuthuka), kunezinqubo eziyisixazulo zokonga amanzi, njengama-"tippy-taps" nezinye izinhlobo zokonga imali.
I-tippy-tap ubuchwepheshe obulula bokusebenzisa isigubhu esiboshwe ngentambo, nesigwedlo esisebenza ngonyawo esithela amanzi amancane ezandleni neqhuzu lensipho.
Ukomisa okusebenzayo kwezandla kuyingxenye ebalulekile yenqubo yenhlanzeko yezandla, kodwa kunokuphikisana mayelana nendlela esebenza ngcono yokomisa ezindaweni zokuhlanza zomphakathi.
Izinga elandayo locwaningo lusikisela ukuthi amathawula ephepha angcono ngokuhlanzeka kunezomisi zomoya zikagesi ezitholakala ezindaweni zokuhlanza.
Ngo-2008, ucwaningo olwaluqondiswa i-University of Westminster, London, futhi elalixhaswe imboni yamathawula ephepha i-European Tissue Symposium, ukuthi iqhathanise amazinga enhlanzeko atholakala kumathawula ephepha, izomisi zezandla zomoya oshisayo nezomisi zezandla zamuva zomoya osheshayo.
Ngemuva kokuhlanza nokomisa izandla ngesomisi somoya oshisayo, ingqikithi yesibalo samagciwane satholakala siphakama ngesilinganiso kumaphedi eminwe ngo-194% futhi ematheni esandla ngo-254%.
Ukomisa ngesomisi somoya osheshayo kwaphumelela ekuphakameni ngesilinganiso sengqikithi yesibalo samagciwane kumaphedi eminwe ngo-42% futhi ematheni esandla ngo-15%.
Ngemuva kokuhlanza nokomisa izandla ngethawula lephepha, ingqikithi yesibalo segciwane yehla ngesilinganiso kumaphedi eminwe ngo-76% futhi ematheni esandla ngokufika ku-77%. Ososayensi baphinda bathatha ukuhlola okungaveza uma belikhona ithuba lokuthelelana kwabasenzisi bezindawo zokuhlanza nendawo yokuhlanza njengomphumela wendlela ngayinye yokomisa.
Isomisi somoya osheshayo, esiphephetha umoya ovela kuso ngesivinini esibekiwe sika-180 m/s (650 km/h; 400 mph), saphumelela ukuphephetha ama-micro-organisms esandleni nakuso nokucishe sithelele abanye abasebenzisi nendawo yokuhlanza ibanga elingaba amamitha angu-2.
Ukusetshenziswa komoya oshisayo kusabalalise ama-micro-organisms kuze kube amamitha angu-0.25 kusuka kwisomisi.
Amathawula ephepha awabonisanga kusabalala okuqaphelekayo kwama-micro-organisms. Ngo-2005, ucwaningo olwaqondiswa i-TÜV Produkt und Umwelt, izindlela zokomisa izandla ezihlukile zahlolwa.
Ushintsho olulandelayo esibalweni samagciwane ngemuva kokomisa izandla kwaqaphelwa:
Baningi abakhiqizi bezomisi zezandla abakhona, futhi izimisi zezandla zike zaqhathaniswa nokomisa ngama-paper towels.
Ukuhlanza izandla usebenzisa ama-hand sanitizing asulayo kungenye indlela lapho usohambweni ingenkho insipho namanzi.
I-hand sanitizer eyakhiwe nge-alcohol kumele ibe ne-alcohol ngu-60% okungenani.
Ukuhlanza izandla kwezokwelapha kwaphoqelelwa isikhathi eside ngemuva kokuthi udokotela wase-Hungary u-Ignaz Semmelweis ethole ukusebenza kwakho (ngo-1846) ekuvikeleni isifo endaweni yasesibhedlela.
Kunamadivayisi asebenza ngogesi ahlinzekela ngokuphawula okukhumbuza izisebenzi zasesibhedlela ukuthi zihlanze izandla lapho zikhohlwa.
Ucwaningo olulodwa luthole ukuncipha kwamazinga ezifo ngokusebenza kwawo.
Ukuhlanza izandla kwezokwelapha kuba imizuzwana engu-15, usebenzisa insipho eningi namanzi noma ijeli ukuze ugcobe noma uhlikihle ingxenye ngayinye yezandla.
Izandla kumelwe zihlikihlwe ndawonye ngokugaxelanisa iminwe.
Uma kunokungcola ngaphansi kwezinzipho, i-bristle brush ingasebenziswa ukuze ikususe.
Njengoba amagciwane engahlala emanzini asezandleni, kubalulekile ukuhlambulula kahle bese usula kome ngethawula elihlanzekile.
Ngemuva kokomisa, ithawula lephepha kumele litshenziselwe ukuvala amanzi (nokuvula noma isiphi isicabha sokuphuma uma kwenzeka).
Lokhu kugwema ukuphinde ungcolise izandla ngalezo zindawo.
Inhloso yokuhlanza izandla esimweni sokwezokunakekela ukususa ama-pathogenic microorganisms ("germs") bese ugwema ukuwadlulisela.
I-The New England Journal of Medicine ibika ukuthi ukuyekelela ukuhlanza izandla kuqhubeka ngamazinga angemukeleki ezindaweni eziningi zezokwelapha, isibalo esikhulu sodokotela nabahlengikazi beqhubeka bekhohlwa ukuhlanza izandla zabo ngaphambi kokuthinta iziguli, kanjalo badlulisele ama-microorganisms.
Ucwaningo olulodwa lwabonisa ukuthi ukuhlanza izandla ngendlela nezinye izinqubo ezilula kungehlisa izinga le-catheter-related bloodstream infections ngo-66 percent. I-World Health Organization inyathelise ishidi elibonisa isimiso sokuhlanza izandla nokuhlikihla izandla emkhakheni wokunakekela kwezempilo.
Iziqondiso zenhlangano ezisalungiswa zenhlanzeko yezandla zingatholakala kuwebusayithi yayo ukuze umphakathi uphawule.
Ukubuyekeza okufanele kwaqondiswa i-Whitby et al.
Amadivayisi ezitolo angakwazi ukulinganisa nokuqinisekisa inhlanzeko yezandla, uma ukubonisa nokuvumelana nomthetho kufuneka.
I-World Health Organization "inezikhathi eziyisihlanu" zokuhlanza izandla:
ngemuva kokuchayeka egazini/kuketshezi lwegazi
ngaphambi komsebenzi we-aseptic, kanye
nangemuva kokunakekela isiguli. Ukufaka amakhemikhali anqandayo ensiphweni ("enomuthi" noma izinsipho "ezinqanda ama-microbes") kunika amandla okubulala kulokho kokuhlanza izandla.
Lawo mandla okubulala angase adingeke ngaphambi komsebenzi wokuhlinza noma ezimweni lapho ama-antibiotic-resistant organisms emaningi khona. 'Ukuhuhla' izandla kothile ngenjongo yomsebenzi wokuhlinza, kuyadingeka ukuba nempompi engavulwa futhi uvalwe ngaphandle kokuthintwa ngezandla, i-chlorhexidine noma i-iodine wash, ama-sterile towels okomisa izandla ngemuva kokuhlanza, ne-sterile brush yokuhuhla kanye nenye i-sterile instrument yokuhlanza ngaphansi kwezinzipho.
Konke okokuhloba kumele kukhunyulwe.
Lenqubo idinga ukuhlanzwa kwezandla nezingalo kufike endololwaneni, ngokuvamile imizuzu engu-2-6.
Izikhathi ezinde zokuhuhla (imizuzu engu-10) azisona isidingo.
Lapho uyakaza, amanzi asezingalweni kumele avinjwe angagijimeli emuva ezandleni.
Ngemuva kokuphetha ukuhlanza izandla, izandla zomiswa ngendwangu e-sterile noma ingubo yokuhlinza iyagqokwa.
Ukuze kwehliswe ukusabalala kwagciwane, kungcono ukuhlanza izandla noma ukusebenzisa isinqandamagciwane sezandla ngaphambili nangemuva kokunakekela umuntu ogulayo.
Ukuze kulawulwe izifo ze-staphylococcal ezibhedlela, kuye kwatholakala ukuthi inzuzo enkulu evela ezandleni ezicocekile ivela ku-20% wokuqala wokuhlanza, nokuthi incane kakhulu izuzo eyengeziwe etholakalayo lapho ukuhlanza izandla ngokuphindelela kukhushulwe ngaphezulu kuka-35%.
Ukuhlanza ngensipho engenalutho kuba nomphumela wezinga elengezwe kathathu lesifo segciwane elithathelanayo ekudleni uma kuqhathaniswa nokuhlanza ngensipho enqanda amagciwane. Ukuqhathanisa i-hand-rubbing nge-alcohol-based solution ne-hand washing with antibacterial soap for a median time of 30 seconds each showed that the alcohol hand-rubbing reduced bacterial contamination 26% more than the antibacterial soap.
Kodwa insipho namanzi kusebenza kangcono kunama-alcohol-based hand rubs ekunciphiseni i-H1N1 influenza A virus ne-Clostridium difficile spores ezandleni. Ukungenela ukuze kuthuthukiswe inhlanzeko yezandla ezimweni zokunakekela impilo kungahlanganisa ukufundisa izisebenzi ngokuhlanza izandla, ukuphakamisa ukutholakala kwe-alcohol-based hand rub, nezikhumbuzo ezibhaliwe nezishiwoyo kubasebenzi.
Kunesidingo socwaningo olwengeziwe oluphenya ukuthi iyiphi kulezindlela zokungenela esebenza kangcono ezimweni zokunakekela impilo ezingafani.
Emazweni asathuthuka, ukuhlanza izandla ngensipho kuqashelwa njengendlela eyongayo, ithuluzi elibalulekile lokufinyelela impilo enhle, ngisho nokondleka ngokomzimba.
Kodwa, ukuntuleka kokuphakelwa amanzi okunokuthenjelwa, insipho noma izindawo zokuhlanza izandla emakhaya abantu, ezikoleni nasezindaweni zokusebenza zenza kube inselele ukufinyelela imikhuba yokuhlanza izandla yomhlaba.
Ngokwesibonelo, emaphandleni amaningi e-Africa izimpompi yokuhlanza izandla eseduze nezindlu zangasese zomuntu noma zomphakhathi iyantuleka, yize zikhona izindlela ezingaduli zokwakha izindawo zokuhlanza izandla.
Kodwa, amazinga aphansi okuhlanza izandla kungenzeka ayisizathu semikhuba egxilile kunaleso sokuntuleka kwensipho noma kwamanzi.
Ukukhangisa nokumelela ukuhlanza izandla ngensipho kungaba nomthelela ekwenzeni iziqumo zomthetho, kuphakamise ukuqapha ngezinzuzo zokuhlanza izandla futhi kuholele ekushintsheni kwemikhuba ehlalayo yomphakathi.
Ukuze lokhu kusebenze kahle, ukuqapha nokulandelela kubalulekile.
Ukubuyekeza okuhleliwe kocwaningo olungu-70 kuthole ukuthi izindlela ezincika emphakathini ziyasebenza ekuphakamiseni ukuhlanza izandla kuma-LMIC, kuyilapho imikhankaso yokukukhangisa ngokwezenhlalo kusebenza kancane. Isibonelo esisodwa sokukhangisa ukuhlanza izandla ezikoleni "Indlela Yezinkanyezi Ezintathu" ye-UNICEF ekhuthaza izikole ukuthi zithathe izinyathelo ezilula , ezongayo ukuze kuqinisekwe ukuthi abafundi bahlanza izandla zabo ngensipho, phakathi nezinye izimfuneko zenhlanzeko.
Lapho amazinga amancane efinyelelwa, izikole zingasuka kwesinye futhi ekugcineni ziye kwezintathu izinkanyezi.
Ukwakha izindawo zokuhlanza izandla kungaba yingxenye yemikhankaso yokukhangisa ukuhlanza izandla eyenziwayo ukuze kuncishiswe izifo nokufa kwezinsana.
Usuku Lomhlaba lokuhlanza Izandla ngenye yezibonelo zemikhankaso ephakamisa ukuqapha ezama ukufinyelela ukushintsha kwemikhuba. Njengomphumela wobhubhane lwe-2019-20 coronavirus, i-UNICEF yakhangisa ukusebenziswa kabanzi kwe-emoji yokuhlanz'izandla.
Ucwaningo olumbalwa luye lacabangela izindleko zonkana zokusebenza kokuhlanza izandla emazweni asathuthuka nobudlelwano nokuvimba kwe-DALYs.
Kodwa, ukubuyekeza okukodwa kuphakamisa ukuthi ukukhangisa ukuhlanza izandla ngensipho konga izindleko kakhulu kunokunye ukungenelela ngamanzi nokukhuculula.
Ukubaluleka kokuhlanza izandla kwezempilo yomuntu – ikakhulukazi kubantu abangaphansi kwezimo ezibuthaka njengomame abasanda kubeletha noma amasosha alimele ezibhedlela – kwaqaphelwa okokuqala phakathi lekhulu leminyaka lika-19 ngamavulandlela amabili enhlanzeko yezandla: Udokotela wase-Hungary u-Ignaz Semmelweis owayesebenza e-Vienna, e-Austria no-Florence Nightingale, Ingisi "elasungula ubuhlengikazi besimanje".
Ngaleso sikhathi abantu abaningi babesakholelwa ukuthi izifo zibangwa amaphunga amabi ayebizwa ngama-miasmas.
Ngawo-1980, ukuqubuka okuvela ekudleni nezifo ezihlobene nezokwelapha kwaholela i-United States Centers for Disease Control and Prevention ukuthi ikhangise ngokwengeziwe ukuhlanza izandla njengendlela ebalulekile yokuvikela ukusabalala kwesifo.
Ukuqubuka kwe-swine flu ngo-2009 kanye nobhubhane lwe-COVID-19 ngo-2020 kuholele ekuqapheni okuphakeme emazweni amaningi mayelana nokubaluleka kokuhlanza izandla ngensipho ukuze umuntu azivikele kulolu hlobo lwezifo ezithathelanayo.
Ngokwesibonelo, amaphosta anombhalo othi "inqubo efanele yokuhlanza izandla" aphanyekwa phezulu eduze kukasinki wokuhlanza izandla ezindlini zangasese zomphakathi nasezindlini zangasese kumabhilidi amahhovisi nasezikhumulweni zezindiza e-Germany.
Isisho esithi "ukuhlanza izandla zakho" kokuthile, kusho ukucacisa ungafuni kothile ukuthatha umthwalo wemfanelo kokuthile noma ukuhileleka kuyo.
Umsuka wayo yingxenye yeBhayibheli ekuMathewu lapho uPontiyu Pilatu ezihlanza izandla ekwenzeni isinqumo sokubethela uJesu Krestu, kodwa sesiphenduke isisho esisebenza kabanzi kweminye imiphakathi yamaNgisi.
Ku-Macbeth ka-Shakespeare, Intokazi u-Macbeth iqala sakuphoqa ngokuzihlanza izandla izama ukuzicoca ukungcola okucabangwayo, okumelela unembeza onecala ngokuphathelene namacala ayewenzile futhi wanxenxela umyeni wakhe ukuba awenze.
Kuphinde kwatholakala ukuthi abantu, ngemuva kokukhumbula noma kokucabanga ngezenzo ezingafanele, bavamile ukuhlanza izandla zobo izikhathi eziningana kunabanye, futhi bavamile ukwazisa ukubaluleka kwezinto zokuhlanza izandla kakhudlwana.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, lapho abavunyelwe ukuhlanza izandla zabo ngemuva kwalokho aba mancane amathuba abo okuhlanganyela kokuzisola ezenzweni "zokuhlanza", njengokuvoluntiya.
Inkolo ikhuthaza ukuhlanza izandla ngakho kokubili injongo yenhlanzeko nomfuziselo. Umfuziselo ekuhlanzeni izandla, usebenzisa amanzi kodwa ngaphandle kwensipho ukuze uhlanze izandla, kuyingxenye yenqubo yokuhlanza izandla ekhona kweziningi izinkolo, kuhlanganise i-Bahá'í Faith, i-Hinduism, i-tevilah ne-netilat yadayim ku-Judaism, i-Lavabo ku-Christianity, ne-Wudhu ku-Islam. Izinkolo ziphinde zikhuthaze ukuhlanza izandla, ikakhulukazi ngemuva kwezenzo ezithile.
I-Hinduism, i-Judaism ne-Islam iphoqa ukuhlanzwa kwezandla ngemuva kokusebenzisa indlu yangasese.
Futhi, i-Hinduism, i-Buddhism, i-Sikhism, i-Judaism ne-Islam iphoqa ukuhlanza izandla ngaphambi nangemuva kokudla.
Izilawuli zendowo yomsebenzi zengozi ye-COVID-19
Izilawuli zengozi endaweni yomsebenzi ze-COVID-19 ukusebenziswa kwezinqubo zokulawula izingozi ze-occupational safety and health ekuvikeleni isifoe se-coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Izilawuli ezifanele zengozi endaweni yomsebenzi zincike endaweni yokusebenza nohlobo lomsebenzi, ngokusekela ekuhloleni ubungozi bemithombo yokuchayeka, ubunzima besifo emphakathini, nezinto eziyingozi kubasebenzi ngabanye okungenzeka babuthaka ekunqandeni i-COVID-19.
Ngokusho kwe-U.S. Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA), imisebenzi enokuchayeka okuphansi kwengozi inezinga eliphansi lokuthintana nomphakathi nezinye izisebenzi, okuthi izinyathelo ezilula zokuvikela ziyakhuthazwa, kuhlanganisa ukuhlanza izandla, ukukhuthaza izisebenzi ukuthi zihlale emakhaya uma zigula, imikhuba emihle yokuphefumula, nokugcina inqubo yokuhlanza nokubulala amagciwane endaweni yokusebenza.
Imisebenzi enokuchayeka engozini okuphakathi ihlanganisa leyo efuna ukuthinta njalo futhi okuseduze nabantu abangaziwa noma abasolwa ukuba ne-COVID-19, kodwa bangase babe negciwane ngenxa yokudluliselana okuqhubekayo emphakathini noma ukuvakashela emazweni angaphandle.
Lokhu kuhlanganisa izisebenzi ezinokuthintana nomphakathi ovamile njengezikole, izindawe zokusebenza ezigcwala abantu abaminyene, kanye nezimo zokuthengisa ezinabaningi.
Izilawuli zengozi kuleli qembu, ngaphezu kwezinyathelo zokuvikela igciwane ezilula, zihlanganisa i-ventilation esebenzisa i-high-efficiency air filters, ama-sneeze guards, kanye nokuba ne-personal protective equipment etholakalayo ezimweni lapho kutholakala umuntu one- COVID-19.
I-OSHA ibheka abasebenzi bezempilo nabasemakhazeni abachayeka kubantu abaziwayo noma abasolwa ngokuba ne-COVID-19 njengabasengozini ephakeme yokuchayeka, okuphakamela engozini ephakeme kakhulu yokuchayeka uma izisebenzi zenza ama-aerosol-generating procedures, noma zilanda noma ziphatha ama-specimens asuka kubantu abaziwayo noma abasolwa ngokuba ne-COVID-19.
Izilawuli zengozi ezifanelekayo kulezi sebenzi kuhlanganisa izilawuli zokwakha njengama-negative pressure ventilation rooms, ne- personal protective equipment efanele emsebenzini.
ukuqubuka kwe*COVID-19 kungaba nemiphumela enzima ngaphakathi endaweni yomsebenzi.
Izisebenzi zingase zingabibikho emsebenzini ngenxa yokugula, isidingo sokunakekela abanye, noma ngenxa yokusaba ithuba lokuchayeka.
Imikhuba youthengisa ingase ishintshe, kukho kokubili uhlobo lwezimpahla ezifunekayo, anezindlela zokukuzithola lezi zimpahla (njengokuthenga ngezikhathi ezingekho matasa noma ngokulethelwa noma nemisebenzi yokudlula ngokushayela).
Okokugcina, ukuthunyelwa kwezinto ezisuka ezindaweni ezithintwe kanzima i-COVID-19 kungase kuphazamiseke. Ukulungela isifo esithelelanayo nohlelo lokusabela kungasibenziswa ukuze kuqondise izenzo ezivikelayo.
Izinhlelo zibheka amazinga engozi ahilelekile ezindaweni ezingafani zokusebenza nohlobo lomsebenzi, zihlanganisa uhlobo lokuchayeka, izinto eziyingozi eziphakama ekhaya noma ezimweni zomphakathi, nezinto eziyingozi zabasebenzi ngabanye njengiminyaka ephakeme noma izimo zezifo ezingomahlalakhona.
Ziphinde zicacise ukulawula okufanele ukuze kuhlangabezwe lezo zingozi, futhi izinhlelo ezilandelayo zezimo ezingaphakama njengomphumela wokuqubuka.
Ukulungela isifo esithelelanayo nezinhlelo zokusabela zingase zincike kokukhuthazwa umthetho wezwe noma wezifundazwe.
Izinjongo zokusabela esimweni sokuqubuka zihlanganisa ukunciphisa ukudliliselana phakathi nabasebenzi, ukuvikela abantu abasengozini ephakeme yezinkinga ezinzima zempilo, ukugcina imisebenzi yebhizinisi, nokunciphisa imiphumela enzima kwamanye amabhizinisi nabaphakeli bokuthenga.
Ubunzima besifo emphakathini ibhizinisi elikuwo kuthinta izinyathelo zokusabela ezithathwayo.
Izitebhisi zokulawula izingozi ifremuwekhi esebenziswa kabanzi ku-occupational safety and health ekuhlanganiseni izilawuli zengozi ngemiphumela.
Lapho izingozi ze-COVID-19 zingasuseki, ukulawula okusebenza kangcono ukulawula kokwakha, kulandelwa ukulawu kokuphatha, futhi ekugcineni izinto zokuvikela umuntu siqu.
Izilawuli zokwakha zihilela ukuhlukanisa abasebenzi ezingozini ezihlobene nomsebenzi ngaphandle kokuthembela emkhubeni wesisebenzi, futhi zingaba isinyathelo esonga izindleko kakhulu lapho sifakwa.
Izilawuli zokuphatha izinguquko emthethweni womsebenzi noma izinqubo odinga isinyathelo sesisebenzi noma somqashi
Personal protective equipment (PPE) icatshangela iphumelela ngezinga eliphansi kunokulawula kokwakha nokulawula kokuphatha, kodwa kungasiza ekugwemeni ukuchayeka okuthile.
Zonke izinhlobo ze-PPE kumele zikhethwe ngokusekelwe engozini yesesebenzi, igqokwe ngendlela efanele njengokufanelekile (isib., amarespiretha), kugqokwe njalo futhi ngendlela, ihlolwe njalo, igcinwe, futhi ishintshwe, ngokwesidingo, futhi isuswe ngendlela efanele, ihlanzwe, futhi igcinwe noma or ilahlwe kugwenywe ukungcola.
Ngokusho kwe-U.S. Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA), imisebenzi enokuchayeka okuphansi inokuthintana okuncane nomphakathi nezinye izisebenti ezingontanga.
Izinyathelo ezilula zokuvikela igciwane ezikhuthaziwe kuzo zonke izindawo zokusebenza zihlanganisa ukuhlanza izandla kaningi futhi ngokwenzisisa, ukukhuthaza izisebenzi ukuthi zihlale ekhaya uma zigula, imikhuba yokuziphatha emihle yokuphefumula ehlanganisa ukumboza ukukhwehlela nokuthimula, ukuhlinzekela ngamathishu nezithako zomgqomo, ukulungiselela ukusebenzela ekhaya noma amashifu ashiyanayo kuye ngesidingo, khuthaza izisebenzi ukuthi zigweme ukusebenzisa amathuluzi abanye nezinto zokusebenza, futhi ziqhubeke zigcine inqubo yokuhlanza nokubulala amagciwane endaweni yomsebenzi.
Ukutholakala okusheshayo nokuhlukaniswa kwabantu okungenzeka banegciwane isinyathelo esibalulekile ekuvikeleni izisebenzi, amakhasimende, izibakashi, nabanye endaweni yomsebenzi.
I-U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) ikhuthaza ukuthi izisebenzi ezinezimpawu ze-acute respiratory illness kumele zihlale emakhaya kuze kube yilapho zingasenakho ukushisa, nezinye izimpawu okungenani amahora angu-24 ngaphandle kokusebenzisa imithi eyehlisa ukushisa noma eguqula izimpawu, nokuthi imithetho yezinsuku zokugula ibe egobekayo, vumela izisebenzi ukuthi zihlale ekhaya ukuze zinakekele ilungu lomndeni eligulayo, nokuthi abasebenzi bayazi lemithetho.
Ngokusho kwe-OSHA, imisebenzi enokuchayeka okuphakathi ihlanganisa leyo misebenzi edinga ukuthintana njalo noma eduze ngamagxathi ayisithupha (1.8 m) nabantu abangaziwanoma abacatshangelwa ukuba iziguli ze-COVID-19, babe negciwane le-SARS-CoV-2 ngenxa yokudluluselana okuqhubekayo emphakathini oseduzane nendawo yokusebenza, noma ngesizathu sokuthi othile usanda kubuya ezweni langaphandle eliyindawo enokusabalala kokudluliselana nge-COVID-19.
Laba bahlanganisa izisebenzi ezinokuthintana nomphakathi ovamile njengezikole, izindawo zokusebenza ezigcwala kakhulu abantu, nezimo zokudayisa zesimo esiphakeme. Ukwakha izilawuli zala maqembu engozi ephakeme kuhlanganisa ukufaka ama-air filters ezinga eliphakeme lokusebenza, ukuphakamisa izinga le-ventilation, ukufaka imingcele njengeziqaphi zokuthimula zepulastiki, nokufaka iwindi lokudlula ngokushayela lesevisi yamakhasimende. Ukulawula kokuphatha kuleli qembu lemisebenzi enokuchayeka okuphakeme kuhlanganisa ukukhuthaza izisebenzi ezigulayo ukuthi zihlale emakhaya, ukufaka indlela yokuxhumana ngenqubo ye-virtual ukuthi ithathe indawo yemihlangano yobuso-nobuso, ukuqalisa amashifu ashiyanayo, ukumisa uhambo olungabalulekile oluya ezindaweni ezinokuqubuka kwe-COVID-19, ukwakha izinhlelo zokuxhumana kwesimo esiphuthumay okuhlanganisa i-forum yokuphendula izinkathazo zabasebenzi, ukuhlinzekela abasebenzi ngemfundo nokuqeqeshwa kwakamuva mayelana nezinto eziyingozi nge-COVID-19 nemikhuba yokuzivikela, ukuqeqesha abasebenzi abadinga ukusebenzisa izingubo ezivikelayo nendlela yokuzisebenzisa, ukuhlinzekela ngezinsizi nendawo yokusebenza ekhuthaza inhlanzeko yomuntu siqu, efuna ukuhlanzwa kwezandla njalo, ukubeka umkhawulo wamakhasimende nomphakathi wokufinyelela indawo yomsebenzi, nokuposa izimpawu mayelana nokuhlanza izandla izinyathelo zokuvikela i-COVID-19. Kuye ngokuncika emsebenzini, abasebenzi abachayeka ngezinga eliphakathi bangase badinge ukugqoka izinto zokuzivikela ezihlanganisa inhlanganisela yamagilavu, ingubo, isembozo sobuso noma imaski yobuso, noma izibuko.
Izisebenzi ezikuleli qembu lokuchayeka azivamile ukudinga ukusebenzisa amarespiretha.
Uma umuntu eqala ukugula ebhanoyini, izinhlelo ezifanele zokulawula zokuvukela abasebenzi nabanye abagibeli zihlanganisa ukuhlukanisa umuntu ogulayo nabanye ngebanga lamagxathi angu-6, ukubeka ilungu elilodwa le-crew ukuthi linakekele umuntu ogulayo, nokunikeza imaski yobuso kumuntu ogulayo noma ukubuza umuntu ogulayo ukuthi amboze umlomo wakhe nekhala ngamathishu lapho ekhwehlela noma ethimula.
Ikhru yekhebhini kumele igqoke amagilavu lapho inakekela umgibeli ogulayo noma ithinta ukutshezi lomzimba noma izindawo okungenzeka zingcolile, futhi kungenzeka ukuthi izinto ezengeziwe zokuzivikela uma ogulayo enokushisa, ukukhwehlela okungaphezi, nalapho kunzima ukuphefumula.
Amagilavu nezinye izinto ezilahlekayo kufanele zilahlwe ngesikhwama se-biohazard, futhi izindawo ezithole ukungcola kufanele zihlanzwe futhi zifakwe isibulala magciwane kamuva. Ngokuphathelene nemikhumbi yezimakethe, kuhlanganisa imikhumbi yokuvakasha neminye yokuthutha abagibeli, ukulawula ingoza kuhlanganisa ukuhlehlisa uhambo lapho ugula, nokuzihlukanisa futhi wazise isikhungo sokwelapha ngaphakathi ngokushesha uma othile eqala ukushisa noma ezinye izimpawu lapho esagibele.
Uma kungenzeka, ukulandelela kwezokulapha kumele kwenzakale kukhebhin yomuntu ozihlukanisile. Ezindaweni zezikole nenkulisa, i-CDC ikhuthaza ukuvala isikhashana ngenjongo yokuhlanza nokubulala amagciwane uma umuntu onegciwane eke waba ngaphakathi kwesakhiwo sesikole kungakhathaliseki ukusabalala.
Uma kunokutheleleka okuncane kuya kokuphakathi emphakathi, amasu okuhlukanisa ngokuhlala kungenzeka aqaliswe njengokukhansela ama-field trip, imihlangano, neminye imibuthano emikhulu njengemfundo yezemvelo, amaklasi ekwaya noma ukudla emakhafethira, ukwandisa isikhala phakathi kwamadeski, ukufika ngezigamu nezikhathi zokugoduka, ukukhawula izivakashi ezingabalulekile, nokusebenzisa indawo yehhovisi lempilo elihlukile lezingane ezinezimpawu ezifana nomkhuhlane.
Lapho igciwane lisakazeka ngendlela ephawulekayo emphakathini, naphezu kwemizamo yokuqhelelana kwabantu, kungase kucatshangelwe ukuvalwa kwezikole okweluliwe. Ezisebenzini zezomthetho ezenza imisebenzi yansuku zonke, ingozi yempilo ngaleso sikhathi ibhekwa njengephansi yi-CDC.
Izisebenzi zezomthetho okumelwe zithintane nabantu abaqinisekisiwe noma okusolwa ukuthi bane-COVID-19 kukhuthazwa ukuba zilandele iziqondiso ezifanayo nezezisebenzi zezimo eziphuthumayo zezempilo, kuhlanganise nezinto ezifanele zomuntu zokuzivikela.
Uma kwenzeka kuba nokusondelana kakhulu lapho umuntu etholakala, izisebenzi kufanele zihlanze futhi zisuse amagciwane emabhandeni azo omsebenzi nezinto ezizigqokile ngaphambi kokuba ziphinde zizisebenzise ngesifutho noma indwangu yokuhlanza yasendlini, futhi balandele izinqubo ezivamile zokuvimbela ukusakazeka kwegciwane nokulahlwa kwe-PPE esetshenzisiwe nangokugcina nokuwasha izingubo.
I-OSHA icabangela ukuthi izisebenzi ezithile zezokwelapha nezasemakhazeni zisengozini enkulu noma enkulu kakhulu yokuchayeka esifweni.
Imisebenzi yabachayeke engozini enkulu ihlanganisa abathumela izinto zokwelapha, izinto zokusiza, abasemalabhorethri, nezisebenzi ezithutha izinto zokwelapha ezichayeke ezigulini ezaziwayo noma okunezinsolo zokuthi zine-COVID-19.
Lezi ziba izingozi ezinkulu kakhulu zokuchayeka esifweni uma izisebenzi zenza izinqubo ezisungula i-aerosol, noma eziqongelela noma zisingathe amasampula, avela ezigulini ezaziwayo noma okunezinsolo zokuthi zine-COVID-19.
Izinqubo ezisungula i-aerosol zihlanganisa ukufakwa kweshubhu emzimbeni, izinqubo ezibangela ukukhwehlela, i-bronchoscopies, izinqubo nokuhlola okuthile kwamazinyo, noma ukuqoqwa kwamasampula omzimba.
Imisebenzi yasemakhazeni yokuchayeka esifweni enobungozi kakhulu ihlanganisa izisebenzi ezihileleke ekulungiseleleni izidumbu zabantu abanezigameko ezaziwayo noma okunezinsolo zokuthi bane-COVID-19 lapho befa; lezi ziba ubungozi obukhulu kakhulu uma zihlola izidumbu. Izilawuli ezengeziwe zonjiniyela zala maqembu obungozi zihlanganisa amagumbi okuhlaliswa wedwa eziguli ezaziwayo noma okunezinsolo zokuthi zine-COVID-19, okuhlanganisa lapho kwenziwa izinqubo zokusungulwa kwe-aerosol.
Ukungena komoya okukhethekile ngomfutho onegathivu kungafaneleka kwamanye amasethingi ezokwelashwa nawasemakhazeni.
Amasampula kufanele asingathwe ngeziqondiso zokuphepha ze-Biosafety Level 3.
I-World Health Organization (WHO) ikhuthaza ukuba iziguli ezifikayo zihlukaniswe zifakwe ezindaweni zokulinda ezihlukile kuye ngokuthi kunezinsolo yini zokuthi zine-COVID-19. Ngaphezu kwenye i-PPE, i-OSHA ikhuthaza ama-respirator kulabo abasebenza beqhelelene ngamafithi angu-6 neziguli ezaziwayo, noma okunezinsolo, zokuthi zinegciwane le-SARS-CoV-2, nalabo abenza izinqubo ezisungula i-aerosol.
E-United States, ama-respirator ayisembozo sobuso esihlungayo e-N95 agunyazwe yi-NIOSH noma angcono kunawo kumelwe asetshenziswe njengendlela yohlelo lokuzivikela ngama-respirator olubhaliwe oluphelele, olubandakanya ukuhlolwa kokuba umqemane, ukuzivocavoca, nokuhlolwa kwezokwelashwa.
Ezinye izinhlobo zama-respirator zingavikela kakhudlwana futhi zithuthukise ukuphatheka kahle kwesisebenzi. I-WHO ayiwakhuthazi ama-coveralls, ngoba i-COVID-19 iyisifo esingena ngokuhogelwa hhayi ngokudluliselwa ngoketshezi olusemzimbeni.
I-WHO ikhuthaza kuphela imaski yokuhlinza ezisebenzini ezihlungayo ezindaweni okungenwa kuzo.
Kulabo abaqongelela amasampula okuhogela, abanakekela, noma abahambisa iziguli ze-COVID-19 ngaphandle kwezinqubo zokusungula i-aerosol, i-WHO ikhuthaza imaski yokuhlinza, izibuko, noma i-face shield, igawuni, namagilavu.
Uma kwenziwa inqubo yokusungula i-aerosol, kufakwa i-N95 noma i-respirator ye-FFP2 esikhundleni semaski yokuhlinza.
Ngenxa yokuthi i-PPE ayitholakali ngokwanele emhlabeni, i-WHO ikhuthaza ukunciphisa isidingo se-PPE ngokuxhumana neziguli ngocingo, izivimbeli ezingokoqobo njengamafasitela abonisa ngale, okuvumela kuphela labo abahileleke ngokuqondile ekwelapheni ukuba bangene egunjini elinesiguli esine-COVID-19, basebenzise kuphela i-PPE edingekayo emsebenzini othile, baqhubeke besebenzisa i-respirator efanayo ngaphandle kokuyikhipha kuyilapho benakekela iziguli eziningi ezinesifo esifanayo, beqapha futhi belawula ukutholakala kwe-PPE, futhi benqabela ukusetshenziswa kwamamaski kubantu abangenazimpawu zesifo.
