Sizithola sisesimweni esiphawulekayo kule nyanga.
Umqedazwe we-COVID-19 uyinto eyenza icace indlela abantu emhlabeni abaxhumene ngayo nomthwalo esinawo komunye nomunye.
Asikaze sibhekane nezinselele ezifuze lena, kodwa siyazi ukuthi indlela esisabela ngayo ixhomeke ohlotsheni lokuzwelana emhlabeni, ukusebenzelana kahle, nokwakhiwa komphakathi okungumgogodla wale nhlangano.
Ukubambisana nokunakekelana esikubonile kuzo zonke izisebenzi zethu ngama-imeyili, izingcingo, nezingxoxo kuyisiqinisekiso esiphawulekayo sokuthi sinabantu abahle esinenhlanhla yokusebenza nabo.
Ngiyajabula ngempela futhi ngiyaziqhenya ngokusebenza kanye nani.
Ngeviki elidlule, othile wangitshela awazisa ngayo umsebenzi wethu.
Wangikhumbuza indlela okunengqondo ngayo ngomhlaba ukuba ukwazi ukuvula i-Wikipedia njengamanje, futhi lolu uphawu olunamandla ngalo mthombo osemqoka ukuba uhlale utholakala ku-inthanethi futhi utholakala kuwo wonke umuntu.
Umsebenzi wenu wenza lokhu kwenzeke, kungakhathaliseki ukuthi nigcina amasayithi evulekile noma izisebenzi zethu zikhokhelwe noma imiphakathi yethu ivikelekile.
Umhlaba uyaludinga ulwazi olutholakala ku-Wikipedia, manje kunanini ngaphambili.
Lesi yisikhathi lapho kungekhona kuphela lokho esikwenzayo, kodwa nendlela esikwenza ngayo, okuzoba negalelo elinamandla emhlabeni.
Ngenxa yokubaluleka kwalo msebenzi nendima yenu kuwo, sizokwenza izinguquko ezinkulu endleleni esisebenzelana ngayo, kusukela evikini elizayo.
Izinguquko emsebenzini wethu namashejuli
Njengoba uRobyn eshilo ngaphambilini, ithimba-c liye lahlangana izolo kusihlwa laxoxa ngendlela esizosebenza ngayo neshejuli yethu yezinsuku nezinyanga ezizayo.
Kuleyo ngxoxo, siye sacabangela lokho esibe nomuzwa wokuthi kuzoba ukusabela kahle kulokho esibhekene nakho nendlela engcono kakhulu yokugcina inhlangano iqhubeka phakathi nalesi sikhathi.
Singalindele besifuna ukususa ukucindezeleka futhi sisekele umgomo wethu wenkathi ende.
Uma kudingeka uphinde usishayele, kulungile.
Kuzo zonke izisebenzi, izinkampane zenkontileka, nezisebenzi zenkontileka:
umsebenzi wethu olindelekile wansuku zonke uzoba amahora angaba ngu-4 ngosuku, noma amahora angu-20 ngeviki kuze kumenyezelwe ushintsho.
Asimemezeli iholidi - uma ukwazi ukusebenza amahora avamile engeziwe, inkampane ingakusebenzisa.
Nokho, izinto aziqinisekile emhlabeni manje, futhi kungakhathaliseki ukuthi kudingeka unakekele abantu obathandayo, uthenge ukudla, noma uye kwadokotela, impilo yakho iza kuqala kithi.
Ngeke sisilandelele isikhathi osisebenzayo.
Uma ugula, ungasebenzi.
Asikho ngempela isidingo sokukusho lokhu, kodwa sizokusho.
Akudingeki ufake izinsuku zokugula noma i-PTO - uzomane utshele imenenja yakho futhi usize ithimba osebenza nalo ukuba lihlele kabusha amakhalenda namashejuli ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuthi izingxenye ezisemqoka zomsebenzi ziyafezwa.
(Uma kutholakala ukuthi unegciwane le-COVID-19, sicela utshele uBryan phakathi kwama-T&C Ops ukuze i-T&C ikwazi ukusiza ngokusekela futhi iqinisekise ukuthi isimo sakho sinakekelwa abaphathi ngendlela efanele).
Izisebenzi ezisebenza ngamahora zizokhokhelwa ngokugcwele.
Kakade sishilo, futhi siyazijuba ukuba sifeze izibopho zethu ezisebenzini zethu zenkontileka nalezo ezisebenza ngamahora.
Wonke umuntu uzokhokhelwa ngokwamahora akhe avamile abewasebenza ezimweni ezivamile.
Lokhu kuhlanganisa nalapho ugula futhi ungakwazi ukusebenza.
Uma ufuna ukusebenza, siyakusekela.
Abantu abaningi basebenzisa umsebenzi njengendlela yokwenza ukucindezeleka kwabo kuhambisane nezinto ezisizungezile.
Esikwenzayo kungaba nomvuzo oyingqayizivele, ikakhulukazi ezikhathini ezinjengalesi.
Siyaphinda futhi, kubalulekile ukuba uzinakekele.
Sikucela ukuba uxhumane nemenenja yakho, ukuze sazi lokho esingakulindela futhi sihlele ngokuvumelana nakho.
Omunye umsebenzi ubhekwa njengosemqoka.
Kunezinto okumelwe siqhubeke sizenza.
Amathimba e-SRE, e-HR Ops, e-Trust & Safety, nawe-Fundraising (phakathi kwamanye) enza umsebenzi obucayi ongase udinge ukusekelwa okwengeziwe.
Sizoqala inqubo nayo yonke iminyango ukuze sihlole imigomo yamanje futhi sigudluzele ukugxila kwethu ekusekeleni lokho okubalulekile emgomweni wethu.
Kuningi sonke okufanele sikwenze, sizomane sigxile sonke kumaphrojekthi asemqoka kakhulu.
Ukunciphisa ijubane manje ngeke kusilimaze kamuva.
Asihleli “ukusebenza ngokuphindiwe ukuze sibambe ishejuli” lapho umqedazwe usudlulile.
Ngeke kulindeleke ukuba usebenze amahora engeziwe ukuze uqede umsebenzi ngesikhathi esingavamile kwamanje.
Siyakwamukela ukuthi izimo zishintshile, futhi sizosebenzela ekubekeni imigomo nezikhathi ezintsha lapho kufaneleka khona.
Kwenzekani nge-APP (i-Annual Planning)?
Ukuze ushintshele ezimweni zethu ezintsha nasemahoreni omsebenzi esiwalindele nsuku zonke, sihlose ukushintsha inkathi yokuthunyelwa kwe-Annual Plan yethu ka-2020-2021.
Inhloso yethu iwukusikisela ukwelulwa kohlelo lwethu lwango-2019-2020 oluvumela isikhathi esengeziwe sokwenza ibhajethi yokuvumela izisebenzi ukuba zenze imisebenzi ebucayi kuqala, zizinakekele zona, futhi zinakekele abantu ezibathandayo kuyilapho zisiza nalabo abadinga noma abafisa ukusebenza ishejuli encishisiwe emavikini ambalwa azayo.
Lokhu kwelulwa kwenkathi yokusebenza inciphisa kakhulu umsebenzi ohlelelwe manje nengcindezi ekuyo yonke inhlangano.
Sizokwethula lokho esikuhlongozayo kuBhodi ngeviki elizayo futhi sibuyekeze abameleli namathimba ezinyathelweni ezilandelayo ngokushesha nje lapho sesinesiqinisekiso.
Siyalibonga ithimba le-APP ngokuhola kulokhu.
Isimo sehhovisi, ukuchayeka, nokuhlanza
Ngeviki elidlule, sifunde ukuthi esinye isisebenzi sethu esiyi-SF kungenzeka sichayeke egciwaneni le-COVID-19.
Nokho, ngenxa yokukhathazeka okukhulu, sithumele iqembu elihlanza ngokususa amagciwane ukuba lisuse amagciwane kuzo zonke izindawo zehhovisi lase-San Francisco.
Lisebenzise insipho yasezibhedlela eyisibulali-magciwane ukuze lisuse amagciwane yonke indawo, kanye nasendaweni yokwamukela izivakashi nasezindaweni zama-elevator ezingenela endaweni esikuyo.
Isakhiwo sisebenzisa iphrothokholi yaso yokunakekelwa ngokusebenzisa imikhiqizo esekela ukuphepha kwamathenenti aso.
Sizizwa sikhululekile ukuthi ihhovisi lizobe selilungile lapho sesinquma ukuphindela kulo.
Ihhovisi lethu le-DC lise-WeWork, elabelene nathi iphrothokholi yalo ye-COVID-19 kanye nazo zonke izisebenzi ezise-DC.
Kusukela ngeviki elidlule, ihhovisi lethu le-DC lithuthele endaweni eqhelile esethwe ngokuphelele ngokuvumelana nesiqondiso esinikezwe i-San Francisco.
Njengoba ezinye izisebenzi zethu zase-NYC zazi, besilokhu sixoxa ngokuqasha indawo e-Brooklyn.
Lezi zingxoxo ziyaqhubeka kodwa zingase zithathe isikhathi.
Ezinye izisebenzi zethu zisebenzela kude okokuqala ngqa.
Izisebenzi zethu ezinesikhathi eside zisebenzela kude ziyazi ukuthi kungaba ushintsho olukhulu, futhi zifuna ukuninika icebiso:
Nciphisani ubude bemihlangano ibe okungenani yihora elilodwa noma amabili.
Uma kudingeka imihlangano emide, cabangelani indlela eningayihlukanisa ngayo phakathi nezinsuku eziningana.
Chazani ngokucacile ukuthi umhlangano umayelana nani, yibani ne-agenda, futhi nithumele izinto okufanele zifundwe kusenesikhathi.
Wenzeni njalo ngevidiyo, ngamathuluzi anjenge-Google Docs ne-Zoom ukuze nisebenze futhi nixhumane bukhoma.
Yibani nomuntu ozohola ukuze ahlele yonke imihlangano, othile ozobheka imibuzo ezingxoxweni futhi alandelele uhlu lwabazokhuluma, nothile ozosiza ekubhaleni amanothi (noma nibhale amanothi ninonke).
Thumelani i-imeyili kwabasekela ngezobuchwepheshe uma nidinga ihedisethi ekahle.
Sebenzisani imali yenu yenhlalakahle ekuthengeni okuhlafunwayo.
Joyinani ishaneli ethi #remoties ku-Slack ukuze nixoxe nozakwenu ngomsebenzi othunyelwayo
Ithimba le-HR Operations lifuna isiqondiso kumasemina e-inthanethi ngezindlela eziphumelelayo zokusebenza ukuze kusekelwe ukwanda emsebenzini othunyelwayo kuyo yonke Inkampane.
Kuleli viki elidlule sicele bonke abamukela imali yeqolo emphakathini ukuba bakhansele izenzakalo zomphakathi ezixhaswa yi-Wikimedia, njengama-editathons, i-WHO ize imemezele ukuthi lo mqedazwe usuphelile.
Sizobatshela ukuthi siye saqonda ukuthi isicelo sethu sokukhansela neminye imingcele ingenza kungenzeki ukuqedela imisebenzi yabo yemali yeqolo okuvunyelenwe ngayo nokuthi akekho ozohlawuliswa ngokwephuza noma ukushintsha leyo migomo.
