I-b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) yi-enzyme ehlezi ngaphandle (kulwelwesi lweseli) kwamaseli emaphashini, imithambo, inhliziyo, izinso, namathumbu.
I-ACE2 ilwa nokusebenza kwe-angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) ngokunciphisa inani le-angiotensin-II nokukhuphula i-Ang(1-7) iyenze ibe umuthi othembisayo wokwelapha izifo zenhliziyo negazi. I-ACE2 iphinde isebenze njengendawo yokungena kumaseli kuma-coronavirus athile.
Uhlobo lomuntu lwe-enzyme kuvame ukubhekiselwa kulo ngokuthi yi-hACE2.
I-angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 iyi-metalloenzyme ene-zinc etholakala ebusweni be-endothelial namanye amaseli.
Iphrotheni le-ACE2 liqukethe idomeyini ye-N-terminal peptidase M2 kanye nedomeyini ye-C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter.
I-ACE2 iyiphrotheni yolwelwesi ewuhlobo I olunomzila owodwa, enedomeyini yayo esebenza ngama-enzyme echayeke ebusweni bamaseli emaphashini nakwezinye izicubu.
Idomeyini yangaphandle kweseli ye-ACE2 ihlukaniswa ukusuka kudomeyini ye-transmembrane nge-enzyme eyaziwa ngokuthi yi-sheddase, futhi iphrotheni encibilikayo eba khona ikhishelwa egazini futhi ekugcineni iphumela emchamweni.
I-ACE2 ikhona ezakhini zomzimba eziningi: i-ACE2 ihlangene nolwelwesi lweseli ikakhulu lwamaseli ohlobo II e-alveolar, ama-enterocytes amathumbu amancane, amaseli e-arterial nawe-venous endothelial namaseli ezicubu abushelelezi e-arterial ezakhini zomzimba eziningi.
I-ACE2 mRNA itholakala naku-cerebral cortex, ku-striatum, ku-hypothalamus, naku-brainstem.
Umsebenzi oyinhloko we-ACE2 uwukusebenza njengebhalansi ye-ACE.
I-ACE ihlukanisa ihomoni ye-angiotensin I ibe yi-vasoconstricting  angiotensin II.
I-ACE2 ihlukanisa i-carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine ukusuka ku-angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) bese uyihlukanisa ibe yi-vasodilator angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ingaphinde ihlukanise amanye ama-peptides amaningana okubandakanya i-[des-Arg9]-bradykinin, i-apelin, i-neurotensin, i-dynorphin A, ne-ghrelin.
I-ACE2 iphinde ilawule ukuhamba kolwelwesi lwe-neutral amino acid transporter SLC6A19 futhi luhlanganisiwe esifweni sika-Hartnup.
Njengephrotheni eliyi-transmembrane, i-ACE2 isebenza njengendawo yokungena eyinhloko kumaseli ama-coronavirus athile, okubandakanya i-HCoV-NL63; i-SARS-CoV (igciwane elibangela i-SARS); ne-SARS-CoV-2 (igciwane elibangela i-COVID-19).
Ngokuqondile, ukuhlangana kwephrotheni le-spike S1 ye-SARS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV2 kudomeyini eyi-enzyme ye-ACE2 ebusweni bamaseli kuphumela ku-endocytosis nakuhambeni kwakho kokubili igciwane ne-enzyme kuye ku-endosomes ephakathi kwamaseli.
Le nqubo yokungena iphinde idinge ukwenza i-S protein lenziwe lisebenze yi-serine protease TMPRSS2, isivimbeli esingaphansi kophenyo lwamanje njengesingaba yikhambi lesifo. Lokhu kuye kwaholela abathile ukuba baphethe ngokuthi ukunciphisa amaleveli e-ACE2, kumaseli, kungasiza ekulweni negciwane.
Nokho, izinhlangano eziningi eziphambili nezindikimba ezisebenzayo zikhuthaze ukuqhubeka ngesivimbeli esivamile se-ACE nokwelapha nge-ARB.
"Ukubuyekeza okuhleliwe nokuhlaziya okushicilelwe ngo-July 11, 2012, kuthole ukuthi ""ukusebenzisa izivimbeli ze-ACE kwakuhlobene nokuncipha okukhulu okungu-34% engozini ye-pneumonia uma kuqhathaniswa nezilawuli."""
"Ngaphezu kwalokho, ""ingozi ye-pneumonia iye yancishiswa ezigulini ezelashwa ngezivimbeli ze-ACE ebezisengozini enkulu ye-pneumonia, ikakhulu lezo ezisifo sikanhlangothi nenhliziyo."
"Ukusetshenziswa kwezivimbeli ze-ACE kuye kwaphinde kwahlotshaniswa nokuncipha kweziguli ezibulawa yi-pneumonia, nakuba imiphumela ibingemibi kangako kunomonakalo ongadalwa yi-pneumonia."""
Isakhi esiyinhlanganisela somuntu i-ACE2 (rhACE2) kucatshangelwa ukuthi siyindlela yokwelapha entsha yokulimala kwephaphu okubi kakhulu, futhi kubonakala kuthuthukisa i-pulmonary hemodynamics ukuphuma komoya-mpilo ezingulubeni ezine-lipopolysaccharide-induced acute respiratory distress syndrome.
Uhhafu we-rhACE2 kubantu uthatha amahora angu-10 ukusebenza futhi uqala ukusebenza ngemva kwemizuzu engu-30 ngaphezu kwesikhathi osisebenzayo (inkathi) engamahora angu-24.
Ucwaningo oluthile lubonisa ukuthi i-rhACE2 lungaba umuthi ofanele walabo abangakwazi ukuphuza ama-renin-angiotensin system inhibitors (RAS inhibitors) avamile noma ezifweni lapho i-angiotensin II ejikezelayo isidlondlobele. Ukugcwaliswa kwe-rhACE2 kuye kwahlolwa ocwaningweni lwezokwelapha ekwelapheni i-acute respiratory distress syndrome.
"Ama-app e-b'COVID-19 ayizinhlelo zesofthiwe yeselula eziklanyelwe ukusiza uthole izinombolo ngokuqondene nomqedazwe wango-2019-20 we-coronavirus, njengenqubo yokuthola abantu (""abathintwayo"") okungenzeka baye bathintana nomuntu onegciwane."
Kuye kwasungulwa noma kwacatshangelwa izinhlelo eziningana, ngokusekela komthetho kahulumeni kwezinye izindawo.
Kuye kwasungulwa amafremuwekhi okwakha ama-app okuthungatha othintwayo.
Kuye kwavezwa ukukhathazeka kobumfihlo, ikakhulukazi mayelana namasistimu asekelwe ekulandeleleni indawo abasebenzisi be-app abakuyo.
Ezinye izindlela ezingadingi ulwazi oluyimfihlo zibandakanya ukusetshenziswa kwamasignali eBluetooth ukuze kufakwe indawo umsebenzisi akuyo kwamanye amaselula.
Ngomhla ka-10 April 2020, i-Google ne-Apple zamemezela ukuthi zizokwakha indlela ukuze zisekele ama-app anjalo eBluetooth ngokuqondile kuma-OS e-Android ne-iOS.
EChina, uhulumeni waseChina, usebenzelana ne-Alipay, usungule i-app evumela izakhamuzi ukuba zihlole ukuthi ziye zathintana yini nabantu abane-COVID-19.
Isetshenziswa emadolobheni angaphezu kuka-200 eChina. ESingapore, kusetshenziswa i-app ebizwa ngokuthi yi-TraceTogether.
"Le app yasungulwa izisebenzi ze-IT zasendaweni, yakhishwa njengewuthombo ovulekile futhi izonikezwa uhulumeni. ENyakatho Macedonia kwakhishwa i-""StopKorona!"", i-app esebenza ngeBluetooth ukuze kulandelelwe ukuchayeka kubantu okungenzeka banegciwane futhi kunikezwe ukusabela okusheshayo eziphathimandleni zezempilo."
Le app yasungulwa uMnyango Wezokuxhumana Nezobuchwepheshe noMnyango Wezempilo.
Kusukela ngomhla ka-14 April 2020, le app yayilindele ukugunyazwa yi-Google Play Store ne-Apple App Store.
"Ngomhla ka-12 April, uhulumeni wathi i-app yokuthungatha umuntu yayisezingeni elithuthukile lokusungulwa, futhi yayizotholakalela ukukhishwa emavikini ambalwa. Kulungiselelwa i-app efanayo e-Ireland, naseFrance (""StopCovid"")."
Kokubili i-Australia neNew Zealand zicabangela ama-app asekelwe ku-app yaseSingapore i-TraceTogether nephrothokholi ye-BlueTrace. IRussia ihlose ukusungula i-app ebonisayo lapho umuntu eqa imingcele ayibekelwe yeziguli ezitholwe zine-COVID-19 ezihlala eMoscow, eklanyelwe ukuqinisekisa ukuthi abaphumi emakhaya.
URoss Anderson, uprofesa ongunjiniyela kwezokuvikeleka eCambridge University, ubale izinto eziningana ezingaba yinkinga ngamasistimu e-app, okubandakanya izixwayiso ezidukisayo namathuba okungasitholi isixwayiso uma amandla e-app elinganiselwe enanini elincane kuphela labantu.
"Ukuze ixazulule izinkinga ezimayelana nokubhebhetheka kwama-app ""e-coronavirus"" adukisayo noma ayingozi, i-Apple ibeke imingcele ezinhlotsheni zezinhlangano ezingafaka ama-app e-coronavirus ku-App Store yayo, yathi kuzoba yilawo ""asemthethweni"" kuphela noma izinhlangano ezethenjwayo."
I-Google ne-Amazon zisungule imingcele efanayo.
Amaqabane alwela ubumfihlo aveze ukukhathazeka kwawo ngokuqondene nezinkinga zokuthungatha uquqaba lwabantu kusetshenziswa ama-app e-coronavirus, ngokukhethekile mayelana nokuthi uhlelo lokuthungatha olusungulelwe ukusingatha umqedazwe we-coronavirus luzoqaqwa lapho lolu songo seludlulile.
I-Amnesty International nezinye izinhlangano ezingaphezu kuka-100 zikhiphe isitatimende esibeka imingcele kulolu hlobo lokuthungatha.
Lezi zinhlangano zimise imibandela eyisishiyagalolunye kumaphrojekthi kahulumeni:
"ukuthungatha kufanele kube ""semthethweni, okudingekile futhi kufaneleke"";"
ukwelulwa kwenkathi yokuqapha nokuthungatha kufanele kube nemibandela yokushona kwelanga;
ukusetshenziswa kwedatha kuzofanele kulinganiselwe ezinjongweni ze-COVID-19;
ukuvikeleka kwedatha nokungaziwa kwamagama kuzodingeka kuvikelwe futhi kuboniswe njengokuvikelwe ngokusekelwe ebufakazini;
ukuhlolwa okuyidijithali kuzofanele kugweme ukwehlisa ububi bobandlululo nokunciphisa ukubaluleka kwezinto;
noma ikuphi ukwabelana ngedatha nabanye abantu kuzofanelwe kuchazwe ngokomthetho;
kuzofanele kube nokuqapha ngokumelene nokusetshenziswa kabi kanye namalungelo ezakhamuzi okusabela ekusetshenzisweni kabi;
"ukuhlanganyela ngendlela ewusizo yibo bonke ""abaneqhaza"" kuzodingeka, okubandakanya ochwepheshe bezempilo bomphakathi namaqembu amancane. I-German Chaos Computer Club (CCC) ne-Reporters Without Borders (Reporter ohne Grenzen) (RSF) nazo zikhiphe izinhlu zokuhlola."
Uhlelo oluhlongozwayo lwe-Google/Apple luhlose ukulungisa inkinga yokulandelelwa njalo ngokukhipha umsebenzi wokuthungatha kuma-OS edivayisi lapho ungasadingeki.
Amanye amazwe abesebenzisa ukuthungatha indawo ngokusekelwe kunethiwekhi kunama-app, okuqeda kokubili isidingo sokudawuniloda i-app nokugwema ukulandelelwa.
E-Israel, ukulandelela okusekelwe kunethiwekhi kwagunyazwa.
Izixazululo ezisekelwe kunethiwekhi ezinokufinyelela kudatha yendawo engahlungiwe zingaba nezinkinga ezinkulu zobumfihlo.
Nokho, akuwona wonke amasistimu anamaseva amakhulu okudingeka athole ukufinyelela kudatha yendawo yomuntu; inani lamasistimu avikela ubumfihlo liye lakhiwa asebenzisa amaseva amakhulu ukuze axhumane kuphela (bheka isigaba esingezansi).
ENingizimu Korea, isistimu engasekelwe ku-app yasetshenziswa ukuze kulandelelwe umuntu.
Esikhundleni sokusebenzisa i-app eqokiwe, isistimu iqongelela ulwazi lokuthungatha emithonjeni ehlukahlukene okubandakanya idatha yokulandelela idivayisi eyiselula nedatha yokuthenga ngekhadi, futhi ihlanganise lokhu ukuze ithumele izaziso ngemiyalezo yombhalo kubantu okungenzeka banegciwane.
Ngaphezu kokusebenzisa lolu lwazi ukuze kuxwayiswe abantu okungenzeka bathole igciwane, uhulumeni iphinde yenza ulwazi lwendawo lwatholakalela umphakathi, okuyinto evunyelwe ngenxa yezinguquko eziningi emithethweni yobumfihlo ngemva kokuqubuka kwe-MERS kulelo zwe.
Lolu lwazi lutholakalela umphakathi ngama-app namawebusayithi. Amazwe abandakanya iGermany acabangele ukusebenzisa kokubili amasistimu amakhulu nalawo avikela ubumfihlo.
Kusukela ngomhla ka-6 April 2020, imininingwane ayikakhishwa.
Ukulandelela okuvikela ubumfihlo buyindlela eklanywe kahle, enezincwadi zocwaningo eziningi ezisukela emuva okungenani ngo-2013. Kusukela ngomhla ka-7 April 2020, amaqembu ochwepheshe angaphezu kuka-12 abefuna izisombululo ezikwamukelayo ubumfihlo, njengokusebenzisa i-Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) ukuze usondelanise umsebenzisi namanye amaselula.
Nokho, i-PEPP-PT ingumzamo wokuxhumanisa oqukethe kokubili izindlela ezinkulu nezihlukahlukene, futhi ayiyona iphrothokholi eyodwa. Amaphrothokholi ahlukahlukene abandakanya i-Decentralized Privacy-Preserving Proximity Tracing (DP-PPT/DP-3T), i-Temporary Contact Numbers (i-TCN, i-fka Contact Event Numbers, i-CEN), i-Privacy Sensitive Protocols ne-Mechanisms for Mobile Contact Tracing (PACT) namanye.
Kulawa maphrothokholi, idatha yomuntu ebonakalayo ayilokothi ishiye idivayisi, futhi konke ukumatanisa kwenzeka kudivayisi.
I-Privacy Group e-MIT Media Lab ibilokhu isungula i-SafePaths, ipulatifomu yokusebenzisa amasu okuvikela ubumfihlo lapho iqongelela futhi isebenzisa indawo noma idatha engumzila oyisinqamuleli ukuze kulandelelwe ukubhebhetheka kwe-COVID-19.
"Kusekelwe ocwaningweni oluvela ephepheni elimhlophe i-""Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic"" elakhishwa ngoMarch 2020. Omunye umzamo ofanayo yipulatifomu ye-SafeTrace ye-Enigma MPC, inkampane esungula ubuchwepheshe bobumfihlo eyasungulwa okokuqala e-MIT Media Lab."
I-SafeTrace isebenzisa ubuchwepheshe behadiwe obuvikelekile ukuze ivumele abasebenzisi ukuba babelane ngedatha ebucayi yendawo nempilo nabanye abasebenzisi nabezomthetho, ngaphandle kokubeka ubumfihlo baleyo datha engozini.
Ngomhla ka-5 April 2020, i-TCN Coalition yomhlaba wonke yasungulwa amaqembu abehlanganiswe yilokho obekuyindlela efanayo namaphrothokholi ashiyana kakhulu, ngomgomo wokunciphisa ukuhlukana, futhi kuvunyelwe ukusebenziseka emhlabeni wonke kwama-app okuthungatha nokuxwayisa, isici esibalulekile ekwamukelweni kabanzi.
Ngomhla ka-9 April 2020, uhulumeni waseSingapore wamemezela ukuthi wenza isimemo sephrothokholi ye-BlueTrace esetshenziswa yi-app wayo kahulumeni esemthethweni.
Ngomhla ka-10 April 2020, i-Google ne-Apple, izinkampane ezilawula amapulatifomu eselula ye-Android ne-iOS, zamemezela indlela yokuthungatha abantu, futhi zagomela ngokuthi izobuvikela ubumfihlo, ngokusekelwe enhlanganiseleni yobuchwepheshe be-Bluetooth Low Energy ne-cryptography evikela ubumfihlo.
Ziphinde zashicilela izici zobuchwepheshe obusetshenziswe kusistimu.
Ngokuvumelana ne-Apple ne-Google, isistimu kuhloswe ukuba ikhishwe ngezigaba ezintathu:
ukukhishwa kwamathuluzi ukuze kuvunyelwe ohulumeni ukuba bakhe ama-app asemthethweni athungatha i-coronavirus avikela ubumfihlo
ukufakwa kwalesi sici ngokuqondile ohlelweni lwe-iOS ne-AndroidGoogle ne-Apple ukuze kulungiswe izinkinga zokuqalisa nokuqapha okuqhubekayo ngokuthumela kuqala isistimu ngezibuyekezo ze-OS, futhi kamuva ukusikhipha ngendlela efanayo lapho usongo seludlulile.
I-b'Drug repositioning (ephinde yaziwe ngokuthi ukusetshenziswa kabusha komuthi, i-re-profiling, i-re-tasking noma i-therapeutic switching) iwukusebenzisa kabusha umuthi ogunyaziwe ukuze kwelashwe esinye isifo noma isimo sezempilo esihlukile kuleso eyayakhelwe sona.
