Ezinye iziqondiso zocwaningo zibandakanya ukusungulwa komgomo we-COVID-19 nokumpontshelwa i-convalescent plasma. I-SARS-CoV-2 inamaphrotheni angaba ngu-66 akwazi ukusebenzisa umuthi, ngayinye inamasayithi amaningi okuhlangana kuwo amamolekhuli.
Ukuhlaziya lawo masayithi okuhlanganwa kuwo kwakha iphrojekthi enengqondo yokusungula umuthi olwa negciwane ngokumelene namaphrotheni e-COVID-19.
Kumaphrotheni abhekiwe abaluleke kakhulu e-SARS-CoV-2 yi-protease enjenge-papain, i-RNA polymerase esekelwe ku-RNA, i-helicase, i-S protein, ne-ADP ribophosphatase.
