Umphathi-sifundazwe waseNew York u-Andrew Cuomo wamemezela ukuthi ucwaningo lweSifunda saseNew York lwe-chloroquine ne-hydroxychloroquine luzoqala ngomhla ka-24 March. Ngomhla ka-28 March, i-FDA yagunyaza ukusetshenziswa kwe-hydroxychloroquine sulfate ne-chloroquine phosphate ngaphansi kwe-Emergency Use Authorization (EUA).
Lokhu kwelashwa akukagunyazwa yinqubo yocwaningo yezokwelapha ye-FDA futhi igunyazwa ngaphansi kwe-EUA kuphela njengendlela yokwelapha ecwaningwayo ezosetshenziselwa izimo eziphuthumayo ezigulini ezilaliswa esibhedlela kodwa ezingakwazi ukwamukela ukwelashwa ocwaningweni lwezokwelapha.
