Umgomo we-b'A COVID-19 ungumgomo ocatshangwayo ngokumelene nesifo se-coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Nakuba ungekho umgomo osuqedile ucwaningo lwezokwelapha, kunemizamo eminingi eqhubekayo yokwakha umgomo onjalo.
Ngasekupheleni kuka-February 2020, i-World Health Organization (WHO) yathi ibingalindele ukuthi umgomo we-SARS-CoV-2, igciwane eliyimbangela, ukuba litholakale ngaphansi kwezinyanga ezingu-18.
Amakhendidethi okugoma amahlanu abeseSigabeni I socwaningo lokuphepha ngo-April.
I-COVID-19 yatholwa ngo-December 2019.
Ukuqubuka okukhulu kwabhebhetheka emhlabeni wonke ngo-2020, kwaholela emsebenzini omkhulu wokutholwa kwezimali nocwaningo ukuze kusungulwe umgomo.
Izinhlangano eziningi zisebenzisa izakhi zofuzo ukuze zisungule imigomo engenziwa ye-SARS-CoV-2.
Kusukela ngo-April, izinto ezisemqoka zomsebenzi we-CEPI wokusungula umgomo ziyashesha, ziyagungulwa, ziyakhiqizwa, futhi ziyafinyeleleka emhlabeni.
Ngo-April, ososayensi be-CEPI babike ukuthi amapulatifomu obuchwepheshe ahlukahlukene angu-10 aye acwaningwa futhi asungulwa ngasekuqaleni kuka-2020 ukuze kwakhiwe umgomo osebenzayo ngokumelene ne-COVID-19.
Imisebenzi yepulatifomu emikhulu eyathuthukela ocwaningweni lokuphepha lweSigaba I ihlanganisa:
i-nucleic acid (i-DNA ne-RNA) (umsunguli weSigaba I nekhendidethi yomgomo: i-Moderna, i-mRNA-1273)
i-viral vector (umsunguli weSigaba I nekhendidethi lomgomo: i-CanSino Biologics, i-adenovirus type 5 vector)
