Ngokwesibonelo, lapho isibhedlela sase-Italy sidinga ngokuphuthumayo i-ventilator valve, futhi umhlinzeki engakwazi ukuyithumela ngesikhathi ebifuneka ngaso, inkampane yendawo yasebenzisa imishini yayo futhi yaphrinta ama-valve abedingeka angu-100 ngobusuku obubodwa.
Ngemva kokuqubuka kokuqala kwegciwane le-COVID-19, izindaba ezicatshangelwayo, izindaba ezingamanga nezidukisayo kwavela ngokuqondene nemvelaphi, ukubhebhetheka, ukuvinjelwa, ukwelashwa nezinye izici zesifo futhi kwasakazeka masinyane ku-inthanethi.
Abantu kubonakala bekwazi ukubhebhethekisa igciwane kwezinye izilwane.
Ucwaningo luhlulekile ukuthola ubufakazi bokutheleleka kwezingulube, amadada, nezinkukhu ngegciwane.
Ayikho imithi noma umgomo ogunyaziwe wokwelapha lesi sifo.
Ucwaningo lwamazwe ngamazwe lomgomo nemithi ye-COVID-19 luqhutshwa izinhlangano zohulumeni, amaqembu ezikole nabacwaningi bezimboni.
"Ngo-March, i-World Health Organization yaqala ""Ucwaningo OLUHLANGANISIWE"" ukuze kuhlolwe imiphumela yokwelashwa yemithi emine elwa negciwane esikhona okunamathemba amakhulu okuthi izosebenza."
Awukho umuthi wokugoma osukhona, kodwa ama-ejensi ahlukahlukene asebenzela ukusungula imithi yokugoma.
Umsebenzi owedlule we-SARS-CoV uyasetshenziswa ngoba i-SARS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV-2 kokubili zisebenzisa i-ACE2 receptor ukuze zingene kumaseli omuntu.
Kucwaningwa izindlela ezintathu zokugoma.
Okokuqala, abacwaningi bahlose ukwakha umuthi wokugomela igciwane.
Inhloso yokusetshenziswa kwegciwane elinjengaleli, lingasebenzi noma lifile, iwukusungula ukusabela komzimba okulwa negciwane elisha le-COVID-19.
Indlela yesibili, ama-subunit vaccines, ihlose ukusungula umgomo owenza amasosha omzimba asabele ezicini ezithile zegciwane.
Uma kuyi-SARS-CoV-2, ucwaningo olunjalo lugxila kuphrotheni eyi-S-spike esiza igciwane lingene ku-ACE2 enzyme receptor.
Indlela yesithathu yimigomo ye-nucleic acid (imigomo ye-DNA noma i-RNA, indlela entsha yokwakha umgomo).
Imigomo ecwaningwa nganoma iyiphi kulezi zindlela kuzofanele ihlolelwe ukuphepha nokusebenza. Ngomhla ka-16 March 2020, ucwaningo lokuqala lwezokwelashwa lomgomo lwaqala ngamavolontiya amane eSeattle.
Umgomo uqukethe ikhodi yezakhi zofuzo engenalusongo ekopishwa egciwaneni elibangela isifo. Ukuthuthukiswa okusekelwe ezakhini zesifo kuye kwasikiselwa njengenselele yokusungulwa komgomo we-SARS-COV-2, kodwa lokhu akuqinisekisiwe.
Kunocwaningo lwezokwelashwa olungaphezu kuka-300 oluqhubekayo kusukela ngo-April 2020.
Ucwaningo oluyisikhombisa beluhlola ukwelashwa osekugunyaziwe kakade kukamalaleveva, okubandakanya ucwaningo olune lwe-hydroxychloroquine noma i-chloroquine.
Imithi esetshenziswa kabusha elwa negciwane yakha ingxenye enkulu yocwaningo eChina, kanti ucwaningo oluyisishiyagalolunye lwesigaba III lwe-remdesivir emazweni amaningana luzothumela umbiko ngasekupheleni kuka-April.
Ukubuyekezwa okunamandla kokusungulwa ngabezokwelapha komgomo we-COVID-19 nemithi engasetshenziswa ekwelapheni kwase kuqalile, ngo-April 2020. Imithi eminingana etholakalayo elwa negciwane iyacwaningwa ekwelapheni i-COVID-19, okubandakanya i-remdesivir, i-chloroquine ne-hydroxychloroquine, i-lopinavir/ritonavir ne-lopinavir/ritonavir ixutshwe ne-interferon beta.
Kube nobufakazi obuphathekayo bokusebenza kwe-remdesivir, ngo-March 2020.
Kubonakale intuthuko ekwelashweni kweziguli okubonakele ekusetshenzisweni ngokwanele kwe-remdesivir.
Ucwaningo lwezokwelapha lweSigaba III luyaqhutshwa e-US, eChina nase-Italy. I-chloroquine, eyayisetshenziswa ngaphambilini ekwelapheni umalaleveva, yacwaningwa eChina ngo-February 2020, kwavela imiphumela engakagunyazwa.
Nokho, kuhlongozwa ukuba kuhlolwe imiphumela yocwaningo.
Iziphathimandla Zezempilo zaseKorea naseChina zikhuthaza ukuba i-chloroquine isetshenziswe.
Nokho, i-Wuhan Institute of Virology, nakuba ikhuthaza umthamo wansuku zonke oyigremu elilodwa, uphawula ukuthi kabili lowo mthamo uphakeme kakhulu futhi ungabulala.
Ngomhla ka-28 March 2020, i-FDA yakhipha imvume yokusetshenziswa ezimweni eziphuthumayo kwe-hydroxychloroquine ne-chloroquine ngokubona kodokotela abelapha abantu abane-COVID-19. Iziqondiso zohlelo 7 zaseChina zabandakanya i-interferon, i-ribavirin noma i-umifenovir ekwelapheni i-COVID-19.
Idatha engakagunyazwa ibonisa ukuthi imithamo ephakeme ye-ribavirin iyadingeka ekuvimbeleni i-SARS-CoV-2 ku-in vitro.
I-Nitazoxanide iye yasikiselwa ocwaningweni oluqhubekayo lwe-vivo ngemva kokubonisa ukuvinjelwa okungenamandla kwe-SARS-CoV-2. Ucwaningo lubonisa ukuthi ukwenyuka kokuqala kwe-protein priming nge-transmembrane protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) kusemqoka ekungeneni kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ngokuthintana nesivimbeli se-ACE2.
Ucwaningo lwe-chloroquine ne-hydroxychloroquine ikanye ne-azithromycin noma ngaphandle kwayo lunemingcele emikhulu evimbele umphakathi wezokwelashwa ekutholeni lokhu kwelashwa ngaphandle kocwaningo oluqhubekayo. I-Oseltamivir ayiyivimbeli i-SARS-CoV-2 ku-vitro futhi inendima engaziwa ekwelapheni i-COVID-19.
I-Cytokine storm ingaba inkinga ezigabeni zakamuva ze-COVID-19 embi kakhulu.
Kunobufakazi bokuthi i-hydroxychloroquine ingaba nezici ze-anti-cytokine storm. I-Tocilizumab iye yanezelwa eziqondisweni zokwelapha yi-National Health Commission yaseChina ngemva kokuphothulwa kocwaningo oluncane.
Kwenziwa ucwaningo lwesigaba 2 okungelona olungahleliwe esigabeni sikazwelonke e-Italy ngemva kokubonisa imiphumela ephozithivu kubantu abanesifo esinamandla.
Ihlanganiswe nokuhlolwa kwegazi kwe-serum ferritin ukuze kutholwe ama-cytokine storms, ihloselwe ukuvimbela ukwenzeka kwalokhu, okucatshangelwa ukuthi kuyimbangela yokufa kwabantu abathile abathintekile.
I-interleukin-6 receptor antagonist yagunyazwa yi-FDA ngokusekelwe ocwaningweni lwesikhathi esidlule ekwelapheni i-steroid refractory cytokine release syndrome ebangelwa yizinto ezihlukene, ukwelashwa ngeseli kwe-CAR T, ngo-2017.
Kuze kube manje, abukho ubufakazi obungahleliwe, obulawulwayo bokuthi i-tocilizumab iwukwelashwa okuphumelelayo kwe-CRS.
Ukudluliswa kwezakhi zesifo ezihlanziwe nezinamandla ezikhiqizwa amasosha omzimba alabo abalulamayo ku-COVID-19 kubantu abawadingayo kuyaphenywa njengendlela engadingi ukugoma kokuvikelwa okungatheni.
Le ndlela yazanywa ku-SARS futhi imiphumela ayaziwa.
I-viral neutralisation iyindlela elindelekile esetshenziswayo lapho ukwelashwa ngezakhi zesifo okungatheni kungadala ukuvikeleka ngokumelene ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Nokho ezinye izindlela, njenge-cellular cytotoxicity esekelwe ezakhini zesifo kanye/noma ne-phagocytosis, zingenzeka.
Ezinye izindlela zokwelapha ngezakhi zesifo, ngokwesibonelo, kusetshenziswa izakhi zesifo ezinamaseli afanayo, ziyasungulwa.
Ukukhiqizwa kwe-convalescent serum, equkethe ingxenye ewuketshezi yegazi elivela ezigulini eziluleme futhi enezakhi zesifo ezihlobene naleli gciwane, kungakhushulwa ukuze isheshe isetshenziswe.
Izifo ze-coronavirus, iqembu lezifo ezihlobene ngokuseduze
U-Li Wenliang, udokotela e-Central Hospital yaseWuhan, kamuva owaba negciwane futhi wafa ngenxa ye-COVID-19 ngemva kokusiza ekuqwashiseni ngokubhebhetheka kwegciwane.
